        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:03:28.987000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. To start us off, when when you need an answer online, like looking something up quickly, what's the very first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "10de113785d542f7ba7847453",
