        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:04:05.307000Z",
        "message": "Basically, I just I guess, figure out what I'm wanting to look up, and I type it in or go to Google, type type it in, and hit search button, and then I generally click on the first 1 that grabs my attention, I guess."
      },
      {
        "callId": "10de113785d542f7ba7847453",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:04:20.437000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. When you're looking at those first results, what usually makes you pick 1 link over another?"
