      {
        "callId": "f8d3229c11cd4952956e6adb0",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:03:25.223000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f8d3229c11cd4952956e6adb0",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:03:33.422000Z",
        "message": "Good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f8d3229c11cd4952956e6adb0",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:03:35.773000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. To get started, when you need answers online, what's the what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f8d3229c11cd4952956e6adb0",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:03:43.023000Z",
        "message": "Ask Siri."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f8d3229c11cd4952956e6adb0",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:03:46.343000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. Can you walk me through your typical process? When you ask Siri for something? What kinds of questions do you usually ask? And what happens next?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f8d3229c11cd4952956e6adb0",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:03:59.583000Z",
        "message": "I ask for information. She either gives it to me or says, can she use chat GBT? That's it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f8d3229c11cd4952956e6adb0",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:04:24.632000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Thinking of the last time you used Siri, what were you hoping to find out? Can you tell me the whole story? From what you needed to what Siri did and how it ended up?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f8d3229c11cd4952956e6adb0",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:04:39.893000Z",
        "message": "I asked her about Charlie Kirk. And she went to chat GBT. And chat GBT answered my question."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f8d3229c11cd4952956e6adb0",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:04:51.453000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. What was the the answer experience like once Siri handed your question over to ChatGPT, did it feel any different from when Siri gives you an answer herself?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f8d3229c11cd4952956e6adb0",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:05:03.262000Z",
        "message": "No."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f8d3229c11cd4952956e6adb0",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:05:07.013000Z",
        "message": "Alright. What part of that experience felt most helpful to you? And was there anything about it that you found annoying or frustrating?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f8d3229c11cd4952956e6adb0",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:05:17.373000Z",
        "message": "The answer was most help and sometimes it's hard to communicate with Siri. Period."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f8d3229c11cd4952956e6adb0",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:05:37.163000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like getting a clear answer is what you value most, but, uh, communicating with Siri can be a bit tricky. Can you tell me more about what makes it hard to communicate with Siri? Are there certain moments or types of questions where things get stuck?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f8d3229c11cd4952956e6adb0",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:05:52.742000Z",
        "message": "Some words get confused. Words as sound the same"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f8d3229c11cd4952956e6adb0",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:06:01.882000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. That happens, when Siri misunderstands a word, what do you usually do next? Do you try again? Switch to another tool or something else? Are you still there? Are you still there?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f8d3229c11cd4952956e6adb0",
