        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:07:15.793000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for letting me know. Sometimes I can't tell on my end, so I appreciate the confirmation. So when Siri misinterprets your words and mixes things up, do you usually repeat the question? Rephrase it, or reach for something else? Like typing it into Google or another engine, what's your go to move in that moment?"
