        "callId": "f8d3229c11cd4952956e6adb0",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:07:45.383000Z",
        "message": "Got it. When you end up using ChatGPT through Siri, does it feel just like getting a regular Siri answer, or do you notice any differences maybe in how detailed, conversational, or, uh, trustworthy the answer feels."
