        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:08:13.093000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. When you get a more detailed answer, from ChatGPT, how does that make you feel about using it for questions? Compared to Siri or Google? Does it affect which 1 you trust? Or prefer?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f8d3229c11cd4952956e6adb0",
