    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "c697c50c893f4f45b70c28589",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:00:50.024000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c697c50c893f4f45b70c28589",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:00:58.034000Z",
        "message": "Good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "c697c50c893f4f45b70c28589",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:00.764000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. When you wanna find an answer online, maybe a random fact, help with a task, what's the very first thing you typically do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c697c50c893f4f45b70c28589",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:11.054000Z",
        "message": "Search on Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "c697c50c893f4f45b70c28589",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:14.873000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Walk me through what happens Let's say you have a specific question in mind. What's your usual process after you type it into Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c697c50c893f4f45b70c28589",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:25.334000Z",
        "message": "Search the most logical answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "c697c50c893f4f45b70c28589",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:29.184000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Uh, can you share a recent example of a question you looked up on Google? Start from what you wanted to know just describe each step you took, even if it seems routine."
      },
      {
        "callId": "c697c50c893f4f45b70c28589",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:40.153000Z",
        "message": "I wanted to know how many days were in the month of June."
      },
      {
        "callId": "c697c50c893f4f45b70c28589",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:44.454000Z",
        "message": "That's a classic 1. So starting from that moment, what were the exact words you typed in Google? And after you saw the search results, what did you do next?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c697c50c893f4f45b70c28589",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:54.863000Z",
        "message": "How many days are in June? And after I saw the results, I got the answer."
