        "callId": "c697c50c893f4f45b70c28589",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:02:42.114000Z",
        "message": "Great. Can you tell me about a recent time you used ChatGPT instead of Google? What did you need, and what made you choose ChatGPT for that moment?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c697c50c893f4f45b70c28589",
        "index": 15,
