        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:04:30.044000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate you sharing that. Thinking about those 2, uh, Google and ChatGP are there certain situations where you'd pick 1 over the other What kinds of questions make you"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c697c50c893f4f45b70c28589",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
