        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:05:56.244000Z",
        "message": "That's a useful detail. So these days, when Google leaves you hanging, you're likely to turn to ChatGPT instead. Would you say you trust ChatGPT's answers more now for certain things"
