        "callId": "c697c50c893f4f45b70c28589",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:06:17.444000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate that. Now shifting gears a bit, I'm curious. If you imagine Google, ChatGPT, and maybe Perplexity or Gemini, as people at a party, how would you describe each one's personality or vibe?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c697c50c893f4f45b70c28589",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:06:33.174000Z",
