        "callId": "c697c50c893f4f45b70c28589",
        "index": 45,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:07:54.254000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. I do feel like it's confidence, but also that it's got a lot of information And don't really have anything else further to say about that."
      },
