        "callId": "c697c50c893f4f45b70c28589",
        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:08:09.163000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. When you share an answer with someone else, maybe a friend or a classmate, which engine's answer do you feel most comfortable quoting or or forwarding to them? Any particular reason?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c697c50c893f4f45b70c28589",
