        "index": 48,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:08:28.134000Z",
        "message": "That's straightforward. Looking back over the past year or so, has anything changed in how you search for answers online? Any moment stand out when you started using ChatGPT more or shifted away from Google as your first stop."
      },
      {
        "callId": "c697c50c893f4f45b70c28589",
        "index": 49,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:08:44.064000Z",
        "message": "Yes. When I first heard about CHAT GPT, I didn't really know what it was, and I wasn't familiar. But when I was going through a certification exam and I was able to ask those specific questions and get those specific answers, I knew I could ask it anything else I wanted to in my life."
      },
      {
