        "index": 54,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:09:16.184000Z",
        "message": "sorry. I meant that moment with your certification exam was the turning point for you in discovering how useful ChatGPT could be. Since then, have your friends or classmates ever recommended AI engines like ChatGPT to you, or have you found yourself recommending it to them? Can you remember a time that happened?"
