  {
    "id": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
    "responseId": "636973abfa2346cc9855eea2c",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:00:18.250000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:00:27.020000Z",
        "message": "Good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:00:29.600000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. To get us warmed up, uh, let's talk about your typical habits. When you need an answer online. Maybe quick facts or more detailed info, what's what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:00:41.599000Z",
        "message": "Search on Bing."
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:00:45.410000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So Bing is your starting point. Can you walk me through what that process usually looks like for you step by step?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:00:54.640000Z",
        "message": "Just opened the app and search for what I'm looking for. Do have any questions about anything?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:02.750000Z",
        "message": "Absolutely. Thanks for laying out your process. When you use Bing for answers, makes it your go to? Is there something about the experience, results, or maybe just habit?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:15.350000Z",
        "message": "It's just my my my basic web search engine that I use."
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:22.940000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. Um, it sounds like Bing is sort of your default. Thinking back to the last time you used Bing, can you walk me through the full story? What were you searching for? And what happened at each step?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:37.630000Z",
        "message": "I was just searching for movies. At the movie theater, what movies are showing."
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:44.370000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. So you wanted to know what movies were playing at your local theater? Can you talk me through exactly how that went? For example, what did you type in? What came up? And how did you use the results?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:58.150000Z",
        "message": "I just went to the movie theaters website and looked at the for the movie times and showings,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:02:09.600000Z",
        "message": "So after searching in Bing, you clicked into the theater's own website. To get the actual info. What made you decide to go straight to the site instead of, say, relying on Bing's own answer or summary?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:02:27.710000Z",
        "message": "being had the movie theater listed on the search engine that I could just go to the site easily."
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:02:35.470000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So Bing helps surface the theater's official site right at the top, making it quick to jump in. When you're using Bing this way, what parts of the experience feel most helpful to you? Anything that ever annoys you or slows you down?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:02:50.510000Z",
        "message": "No. I don't have any problems with it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:02:54.750000Z",
        "message": "Sounds straightforward then thinking about other answer engines. Like ChatGPT, Perplexity, Yo, Perplexity, Google's AI summaries, Gemini. Do you ever use any of those for looking things up? Or is it pretty much Bing all the way?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:03:13.219000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. Pretty much. I don't use much AI."
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:03:19.420000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So for you, most of your searching isn't through AI driven answer engines. What makes you stick with Bing instead of trying something like ChatGPT or Google's AI summaries?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:03:32.720000Z",
        "message": "I've tried chat g d g but I just don't need it. I don't have no much much use for it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:03:42.380000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. When you tried ChatGPT, you remember what you used it for and how that experience compared to just searching with Bing?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:03:54.440000Z",
        "message": "I just had a question about an actor. Or about which actor was in a certain movie. And it answered it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:04:04.560000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate that. When ChatGPT gave you the answer about the actor, did anything stand out to you? Maybe the way it presented info, the level of detail, or anything else compared to Bing. Or did it just feel about the same?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:04:17.780000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. It felt the same. There was no difference."
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:04:22.260000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So no real difference for you between ChatGPT's answer and Bing's search results. If you imagine lining up Bing and ChatGPT side by side, just thinking about how they help you, would either 1 feel more trustworthy, or reliable to quote to a friend, or are they equal in your mind?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:04:41.020000Z",
        "message": "They're equal."
      },
      {
        "callId": "c10bf1339c2b4078a03c71324",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:04:44.260000Z",
        "message": "Alright. That's clear. If you think about Bing or ChatGPT as personalities, say, if each were a person at the party, who do you picture them as? What are they like?"
      },
      {
