        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:03.133000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Thinking about those those 2, um, Google and social media, do you tend to reach for 1 first, or does it depend on what you're searching for?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "068023239ca74ae895fca55c9",
