        "callId": "068023239ca74ae895fca55c9",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:16.323000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful. Um, can you me about a situation when you chose social media over Google, What were you looking for, and what made you pick social media that time?"
