      {
        "callId": "068023239ca74ae895fca55c9",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:25.352000Z",
        "message": "If I was looking for social media, say, news reports,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "068023239ca74ae895fca55c9",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:33.032000Z",
        "message": "Gotcha. So if you're searching for news reports, might go to social media first. Tell me about the last time you did that. What was the topic, and how did you actually go about finding the information?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "068023239ca74ae895fca55c9",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:44.013000Z",
        "message": "The topic was about the present presidential debates."
      },
      {
        "callId": "068023239ca74ae895fca55c9",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:01:49.063000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. Um, you were looking for information on the recent presidential debates. Can you walk me through exactly what you did? For example, which social media platform did you use? And how did you serve"
