        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:02:07.643000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. When you search the stories on, um, Facebook about the debates, what did you find most helpful? And was there anything that frustrated or annoyed you during that process?"
