        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:02:25.623000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like it gave you exactly what you needed. When you're not looking for something news related or social media focused, say, general answers or facts, do you usually go straight to Google? Or do you ever use other answer engines like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Gemini?"
      },
      {
