        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:02:47.083000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for clarifying. Thinking about the last time you used ChatGPT, can you tell me the whole story what you needed, how you used it, what stood out about that experience?"
