        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:03:40.523000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like ChatGPT covered the basics just like Google. If you had to compare the 2, is there anything about ChatGPT's experience, maybe the way it presents information or how you interact with it that feels different or or stands"
