        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:04:01.973000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. So you noticed ChatGPT presents information in a different way. And seems to pull from a lot of sources to give you the right details. Can you describe you how that makes you feel when you're using it?"
