        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:10:41.313000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. I do use it a lot more than I did before. It's just as I I think for me, it's the the time the time that I save and checking with Gemini and getting the answers from them is, you know, I mean, if I'm doing a project and I have asked for research, I get, you know, in a matter of minutes. You know, I get pages of information which would take me you know, quite some time to amass on my own. So I do rely on it a lot more now."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc3d117b394c4959a44d5b1d4",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T01:11:17.494000Z",
        "message": "That's a pretty clear shift. Now you're leaning on Gemini more, because it gets you answers fast and saves a big chunk of time. Especially with research. Was there a moment you first realized you were defaulting to"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc3d117b394c4959a44d5b1d4",
