        "time": "2025-09-14T01:11:35.644000Z",
        "message": "Again, as I said, it was all those exercises I did in the test group. You know? I realized that I mean, I even have a, um, an outline of how to market some surfaces that I have that Gemini gave me. Very detailed. Yeah. It was going through"
      },
