        "time": "2025-09-14T00:54:26.147000Z",
        "message": "It's it's been really interesting. I have to say that the the only thing that tips me off that you are an AI versus a real person is your ability to quickly form thoughts and sentences and answers and not have the typical human filler of, um, and, you know, and, you know, those space fillers that people tend to, uh, stick into their syntax. So um, but, uh, overall, it's this has been an interesting experience."
