        "time": "2025-09-14T00:39:32.699000Z",
        "message": "Got it. You usually head to Google first. Can you walk me through what you do"
      },
      {
        "callId": "44cf136b9a31490583f0069e7",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:39:35.139000Z",
