        "callId": "44cf136b9a31490583f0069e7",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:39:41.099000Z",
        "message": "Oh, I tried to troubleshoot it and see where the the I tried to figure out the problem, and then see if I could find it through Google. If not, use AI services."
      },
      {
        "callId": "44cf136b9a31490583f0069e7",
