        "time": "2025-09-14T00:39:54.439000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that flow. So you start by trying to figure out the problem, then search on Google first. If you don't find what you need there,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "44cf136b9a31490583f0069e7",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:40:02.279000Z",
        "message": "Yeah."
      },
      {
        "callId": "44cf136b9a31490583f0069e7",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:40:03.769000Z",
        "message": "you'll turn to AI services. Can you tell me about the most recent time you did this? What was the issue you were solving? And how did the process go from Google to to any AI tools?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "44cf136b9a31490583f0069e7",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:40:17.059000Z",
        "message": "I had to research, um, a few documents, but was very time consuming, and then I had to use the AI to kill a lot of the time."
