      {
        "callId": "44cf136b9a31490583f0069e7",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:40:28.099000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like you were dealing with some document research that started to eat up a lot of time. When you say you used AI to kill a lot of the time, can you walk me through exactly what you did? Which AI tool did you choose, and how did you use it to help with the research?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "44cf136b9a31490583f0069e7",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:40:45.629000Z",
        "message": "I used and I asked ChatGPT to help help me with my brainstorm approach because I couldn't find research for human resource onboarding for new employees."
      },
      {
        "callId": "44cf136b9a31490583f0069e7",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:02.629000Z",
        "message": "That's really clear. So Google wasn't giving you the info you needed about HR onboarding. And you switched to ChatGPT to help guide your brainstorming. Can you tell me more about that ChatGPT interaction? What did you ask? What kind of answer did you get? And how did it feel compared to your Google experience?"
