        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:20.499000Z",
        "message": "I asked Chad GBT if to verify. If certain services work for, um, human onboarding human resource onboarding. And they and they ended up working. So it was good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "44cf136b9a31490583f0069e7",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:32.789000Z",
        "message": "So you used ChatGPT to verify if certain services would work for HR onboarding, and it gave you answers that ended up being helpful. Sounds like it got you what you needed. Thinking about that,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "44cf136b9a31490583f0069e7",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:41.129000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. Yeah."
      },
      {
        "callId": "44cf136b9a31490583f0069e7",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:44.389000Z",
        "message": "that experience, what part of using ChatGPT felt most helpful? And was there anything about it that"
      },
      {
        "callId": "44cf136b9a31490583f0069e7",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:48.159000Z",
        "message": "Everything"
      },
      {
        "callId": "44cf136b9a31490583f0069e7",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:53.478000Z",
        "message": "sounds like you had a"
      },
      {
        "callId": "44cf136b9a31490583f0069e7",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:53.719000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. Everything what?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "44cf136b9a31490583f0069e7",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:55.928000Z",
