  {
    "id": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
    "responseId": "29324f51d9354919b6f97782f",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:38:00.646000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:38:08.746000Z",
        "message": "My day is pretty pretty good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:38:13.696000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. When you need to find answers, online, like, let's say, you're trying to settle a debate or just curious about something. What's the the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:38:25.286000Z",
        "message": "I generally go to Google and type in my question."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:38:31.675000Z",
        "message": "Walk me through what usually happens after you type your question. Into Google. What do you look for on that results page, and how do you decide which answer or link to check out first?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:38:44.236000Z",
        "message": "Well, generally, the first one's the best 1. And I may look at the next couple down, but, the first one's the best 1."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:38:55.346000Z",
        "message": "Tell me about a specific time you did this you did this recently. Maybe the last time you looked something up on Google. Was the question or topic, and what did you do step by step?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:39:07.156000Z",
        "message": "Let's see."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:39:09.826000Z",
        "message": "Take your time. No rush. Whenever something comes to mind, just walk me through, uh, what you searched for, what popped up, and what you did next."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:39:21.226000Z",
        "message": "Actually, I was looking up a recipe today. For"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:39:25.716000Z",
        "message": "Nice."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:39:26.806000Z",
        "message": "for pizza sauce. And, actually, I picked the very first 1, and I made it I had all the ingredients I needed, and I made it, and I had pizza."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:39:37.795000Z",
        "message": "Love that. So when you click the first result, what made you trust it enough to use that recipe? Was it something specific about the result, like the source reviews, how it was presented or or or just have it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:39:52.816000Z",
        "message": "The most important thing was I had all the ingredients. So that"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:39:57.036000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So have got it. The ingredient list matched what you already had on hand. Was there anything about how the search result looked or who posted it that caught your attention, or was it really just about practicality in that moment?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:40:14.206000Z",
        "message": "It was about practicality in that moment. I just needed a a good recipe And since I had everything, it worked out well."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:40:24.715000Z",
        "message": "After you found that recipe, did you feel any need to, uh, double check its details? Like comparing with another site or or looking for reviews, or did you just go with it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:40:35.666000Z",
        "message": "I kinda go went with it, but I did watch her little video that she made."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:40:43.166000Z",
        "message": "That's a cool detail. So you checked out the creator's video for the recipe. What was it about the video that made you want to watch? And did watching it change how you felt about recipe at all?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:40:56.406000Z",
        "message": "It didn't change how I felt about the recipe, and the reason I watched it just to make sure I was doing correctly."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:06.915000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Helpful to see it in action. You think about that whole experience, was there anything about using Google for your recipe search that felt annoying or gotten your way at all?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:19.246000Z",
        "message": "No. Nothing."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:21.736000Z",
        "message": "Alright. You mentioned Google's your default. Have you ever used something like ChatGPT, Perplexity, Citi, Gemini, or 1 of those new AI answer engines? To look up a recipe"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:34.066000Z",
        "message": "I yeah. I've used chat g GPT, and, actually, in my Google searches, it looks like they're they're integrating a ChatGPT in the Google search now or I'm sorry, AI into the Google searches now as well."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:50.596000Z",
        "message": "Interesting catch. When you've used ChatGPT before, maybe for recipes or something else, how did that experience compare to just straight up Googling? Felt similar or different?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:42:02.596000Z",
        "message": "Well, what felt different was you weren't getting the variety of of of other people's input. It just seemed like AI was answering your question, period. That was it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:42:16.366000Z",
        "message": "That's a great observation. So with ChatGPT, it's more like 1 answer straight up versus Google where there's crowd of opinions, reviews, sources. Does that difference matter to you, uh, when you're deciding which engine to use for a search?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:42:31.116000Z",
        "message": "I kinda like having a choice."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:42:35.056000Z",
        "message": "Totally fair. When you see a bunch of options on on Google, what makes you decide which 1 to actually click? Is it the title, the website name, ratings, or do you just go by gut feeling?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:42:47.276000Z",
        "message": "the graphics that they have, the colors, whatever."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:42:52.656000Z",
        "message": "So visuals grab your attention. Can you think of a time when you saw an answer from ChatGPT or"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:42:55.076000Z",
        "message": "Sure."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:42:58.025000Z",
        "message": "another AI engine and thought, I wish I could see more options. Or compare sides. Anything like that? I don't know somebody like that come to mind."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:43:07.576000Z",
        "message": "Well, yeah, I I think I like to have that. The other options where just a straight up answer is good if you just need a straight up answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:43:17.656000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. So if you're in a hurry, a single straight answer from something like ChatGPT works. But for stuff like recipes, choices matter more."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:43:25.136000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:43:27.376000Z",
        "message": "Thinking about all the engines you've used, Google, ChatGPT, and maybe any others, If you line them up from most to least helpful for you personally, how would you rank them? And what's your main reason for putting each 1 where you did?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:43:42.396000Z",
        "message": "You know, I've I've used Google for so long. It's just worked for me. Like, Edge seems like it's more like a sales. They're it's more like sale oriented where they're trying to sell you something. And then chat GPT, I didn't really see any advertising on that that I heard my call. So that was okay."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:44:10.136000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate that rundown. When you think about Google ChatGPT and Edge, do any particular emotions or traits come to mind for each? Like, if you had to describe their personality, what pops up for each?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:44:27.586000Z",
        "message": "Google is more friendly, and I think Jet GP is more technical."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:44:33.666000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. Google feels friendly. ChatGPT feels technical. What about Edge? Um, any vibe or personality pop into your mind for that 1?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:44:44.995000Z",
        "message": "I just don't use Edge very much. Probably because I don't I don't feel like I get as good as search out of it as I do Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:44:57.136000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you just naturally drift away from edge, thinking about trust, when when you share an answer or a recipe you found, Is there 1 tool's result you'd feel most comfortable quoting to someone else? Or does it not really matter you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 43,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:45:11.136000Z",
        "message": "I usually if someone asks me something, I always tell them, Google it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:45:17.886000Z",
        "message": "That's classic. So looking back over the past year or so, has anything changed in the way you search for answers online? Like, are you using any new tools or maybe noticing AI popping up where it wasn't before?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 45,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:45:31.356000Z",
        "message": "Oh, definitely seeing AI popping up where I it wasn't before. Just like I said, even within Google, I'm seeing that if you scroll down a little bit farther, you get an AI answer. To integrate it into that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:45:48.676000Z",
        "message": "When you spot those AI answers in Google, does it change how you use the results? Like, do you ever pick the AI summary instead of the regular links? Or do you still usually click through?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 47,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:46:02.846000Z",
        "message": "I think I generally go back to the links. Because I kinda like peruse, I guess."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 48,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:46:14.096000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful to know. Has anyone in your circle, friends, family, coworkers, ever recommended a different answer engine to you lately? Maybe suggested you try something other than Google for certain searches."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 49,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:46:28.126000Z",
        "message": "No. I can't think of anybody referee referring me to any other."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
        "index": 50,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:46:34.486000Z",
        "message": "Alright. That covers my main questions for today. Thanks for sharing your stories and being so thoughtful. Just out of curiosity, how is this AI interview experience for you? And whenever you're ready, you can end the call."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f5ca04014ca840c899944ecf2",
