  {
    "id": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
    "responseId": "bb0b2930240b4acb94c2d4486",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:59.991000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:08.051000Z",
        "message": "That's all good. Thank you."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:11.111000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. Let's get started. When you need an answer online, say you're curious about something, or want to solve a problem, what's, like, the very first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:24.151000Z",
        "message": "What do you mean?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:26.500000Z",
        "message": "Sure. Let me break that down. Imagine you're sitting at your computer or holding your phone, and you suddenly need to find out something. Maybe it's what time a store closes. How to fix something, or just settling a random argument. Your usual move? Do you open a certain app?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:41.991000Z",
        "message": "Oh, I yeah, I while I open Google or Bing, and search on there."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:50.821000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So Google or Bing are your usual starting points. Can you walk me through, you know, what happens next step by step? After you open Google or Bing?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:37:02.151000Z",
        "message": "I open it. I type in whatever I'm looking for, whether it's like you said, a time or place that something opens or closes or if I'm searching certain food or a restaurant that's near me. I type in my question. I press search, and I look at the list of everything that's available to me or closest to me, and I go from there."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:37:23.151000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for that rundown. So when you're sifting through those options, helps you pick which result to click? Are you scanning for something specific like ratings, distance, maybe how the title looks? Tell me about that decision moment."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:37:37.161000Z",
        "message": "Usually distance. How close it is to me. If I'm in the mood for something specific, then I'll look at the closest place that has that option available."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:37:48.201000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. Proximity is the top factor. Thinking back, when was the last time you did a search like this? Can you walk me through what you needed and how the search played out? Step by step?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:38:01.051000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. That was actually today. I was looking for the cheapest I wanted tacos, so I was looking for the cheapest sour cream. Near me, and I got the Safeway that was right up the street. So that's the 1 I went to."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:38:20.121000Z",
        "message": "Perfect example. So from start to finish with that search, looking for the cheapest sour cream, wanting tacos, ending up at Safeway. What part of the experience felt most helpful or satisfying? And was there anything kind of annoying or frustrating about it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:38:36.311000Z",
        "message": "Nothing was really annoying or fresh frustrating. The the most satisfying was finding out that the distance I didn't have to go far. I lived 2 minutes from that Safeway. So that's all I had to do was drive 2 minutes over around this down the corner and I had exactly what I needed."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:38:55.041000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like super smooth sailing, quick search, closed store, easy decision. If you hadn't used Google or Bing for that, what would you have done instead to find your answer?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:39:07.290000Z",
        "message": "I probably would have just drove to the course closest grocery store and looked in the aisle for the sour cream and took whatever was was there."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:39:22.231000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful. Um, so the search saved you time. And, uh, maybe a bit of guesswork. Um, out of curiosity, do you ever use other tools besides Google or Bing for answers? Things like ChatGPT, perplexity, or any AI summaries, or do you mostly stick with search engines?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:39:38.021000Z",
        "message": "I mostly stick with search engines."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:39:42.971000Z",
        "message": "Right. You're mostly a search engine person. Can you think of any situations where you'd consider trying something like ChatGPT or another AI powered tool to get an answer? Instead of Google or Bing. Or does it not really cross your mind?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:39:55.411000Z",
        "message": "Absolutely. No. It's definitely crossed my mind. I just don't have a lot of experience with it, so I haven't really gravitated towards it. But if I definitely, um, had experience with it, I I would use it a lot more."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:40:11.841000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. When you do think about tools like ChatGPT, what comes to mind for you? Any impressions, feelings, or words you associate it even if you haven't used it much yet?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:40:24.141000Z",
        "message": "As as as far as I know, I I I think it's a good tool. I mean, so far, even though I haven't used it, I've heard great things about it. I've heard that you can search on there and find just about anything just like you can with Google or any other search engine. So I would definitely use it if I if I had more experience with it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:40:45.141000Z",
        "message": "That's a clear endorsement from what you've heard. Out of curiosity, if you picture Google, Bing, and ChatGPT as people at a party, what kind of personalities do you imagine each of them would have?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:40:59.860000Z",
        "message": "I think of Google and maybe Bing being more of a spontaneous personality because that it's a search engine. Really, you could type there's certain things on there and get it answered to something you didn't even ask. Weird, strange things pop up. But I'm thinking more of, chat GBT is probably more laid back gives you the exact answer that you need with the with the specific question that you're looking for. If that makes sense."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:36.111000Z",
        "message": "That does make sense. So Google and Bing feel a bit unpredictable or spontaneous, while ChatGPT comes across as"
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:42.121000Z",
        "message": "Exactly. Exactly."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:47.791000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate that. Thinking about trust for a moment. You share answers with other people, say friends or family, which engine's results would you feel most confident quoting? Why is that?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:42:03.291000Z",
        "message": "Probably more I would probably lean towards more chat GBT because it is more strict, like I said. Google can give off very spontaneous answers to things that I'm not even asking specifically. So if I were to tell them to use something, I would tell them to use Jet. Chat GBT just because if you ask a certain question or need to know a certain thing, gonna give you an answer specific to that to what you ask. Not just something out of the blue and strange that's gonna pop up."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:42:34.761000Z",
        "message": "That's clear. Specificity and directness feel more reliable to you. Looking back over the past year, have you noticed any changes in how you look things up"
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:42:39.371000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:42:43.101000Z",
        "message": "online? Maybe you tried an AI tool once or your habits shifted even if only a little. Tell me about any moment that that stands out."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:42:53.011000Z",
        "message": "Not none. Not really. I've I've always gravitated the same Google or Bing. Engine searches. I haven't really changed any of that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:43:04.321000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Your habits have stayed pretty steady with Google or Bing."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:43:07.031000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. Correct."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:43:08.531000Z",
        "message": "Has thanks. That's super clear. Just to wrap up, how was the experience talking through your search habits with an AI today? Anything feel unusual or interesting?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:43:20.610000Z",
        "message": "No. Actually, you sound like a person. You don't even sound like an AI. Your voice is is is responding to me exactly how a person would. It's kind of it's cool."
      },
      {
        "callId": "738878d284fd4b7f95643d5f1",
        "index": 36,
