  {
    "id": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
    "responseId": "faeb6ac944d74e2c9afe442f7",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:58.640000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:06.890000Z",
        "message": "Wonderful. Can you hear me?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:09.980000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. When you need to I can hear you just fine. Thanks for checking. Just to clarify, I can only respond to your messages here, but I'm ready to go whenever you are. When you need an answer online, what's typically your very first move?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:20.300000Z",
        "message": "Okay. Okay. Let's go. Hello?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:31.709000Z",
        "message": "Sounds good. So imagine you"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:32.470000Z",
        "message": "Anybody?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:35.329000Z",
        "message": "I'm here. You're coming through loud and clear. So let's start simple. When something pops into your head and you want to look it up online, walk me through what you do first."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:48.100000Z",
        "message": "Speak into the microphone."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:50.950000Z",
        "message": "I get where you're coming from. Don't actually have a microphone or voice. I'm just text based here. So we'll chat by typing back and forth. So if you're ready, let's jump in. Let's say you have a random question and want an answer fast."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:37:04.749000Z",
        "message": "Okay. Alright."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:37:05.220000Z",
        "message": "What's your go to"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:37:07.970000Z",
        "message": "Alright. What is what's the SOP on the g Georgia Department of Corrections SOP on the timeline of a disciplinary report."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:37:31.060000Z",
        "message": "Let's unpack that together. When you have a specific question, like, what's the SOP on the Georgia Department of Corrections? Disciplinary report. Timeline, talk me through what you usually do. Step by step. You go straight to Google, use another search tool, or try something else first?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:37:51.870000Z",
        "message": "Go straight to Google. Type in what's what I'm looking for, and it pulls up what I need."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:38:00.570000Z",
        "message": "Helpful. So Google's your first stop for something official. Like that. Can you tell me about the last time you did this? What was the question? And how did the whole process go?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:38:05.589000Z",
        "message": "Yeah."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:38:09.460000Z",
        "message": "From typing to finding your answer?"
