        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:38:48.690000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So you kind of weigh what's most relevant and and helpful for your situation. When you're scrolling through do certain websites or sources feel more trustworthy to you than others? What signals make you trust or maybe doubt the answers you find?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
