        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:39:10.180000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. So it sounds like you look for research backed info to build trust in what you're reading. When the answer from Google doesn't seem fully clear or reliable, do you ever turn to other tools or or sites like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or or or Gemini to cross check or get more perspective?"
