        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:39:39Z",
        "message": "Great detail. Thinking about that last time, uh, you turned to Gemini. What made you choose it over Google in that moment? Was there something about the experience or the answer that felt different for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
