        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:40:12.080000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful. When you say Gemini feels easier for research, what's going on there? Is it how fast the answer shows up? How it's written? The way you can ask follow-up questions? Or something else that stands out."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
