        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:40:52.550000Z",
        "message": "So it sounds like you use both maybe even side by side. Can you tell me about a situation where you switched between Google and Gemini for the same question? What made you go back and forth?"
