        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:15.920000Z",
        "message": "That's super clear. So you use Gemini and Google together as a sort of double check referencing 1 against the other. When you get matching answers, how do you feel? And what happens if you see differences between their responses?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
