        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:32.230000Z",
        "message": "Research Brother."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:41:35.310000Z",
        "message": "Gotcha. Research is key for you, Confirming through multiple sources. When you notice differences or conflicting answers, do you dig even deeper? Maybe check a third source, or does it make you question the reliability of 1 engine over the other?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9c06e6eb9beb4db18e2221e6e",
