        "time": "2025-09-14T00:42:00.470000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Good question. Thanks for hanging in. We're just about done. Last quick 1. Has anything changed in the past year about which tools you use first when you're looking up answers, or is is your routine pretty much the same?"
