        "message": "Great. Was there any got it. Sounds like it was straightforward. You got the answer you needed. When you use Google like that, do you ever feel emotionally things like relief, confidence, or maybe something else when it delivers quickly? Or is it mostly just routine for you? Feel free to ask me any questions."
