        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:31.907000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. It sounds like the situation shifted from feeling temporary to something more lasting for you. When you realized it was becoming more permanent, did that change how you searched for answers or which tools you used you tell me a little bit about that shift?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:49.367000Z",
        "message": "I just just use try GPT automatically."
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:55.807000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful. So once it felt more permanent, reaching for ChatGPT became automatic. Can you tell me the full story of that last time? What did you need to know? And, uh, what steps did you take with ChatGPT from start to finish?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:34:10.806000Z",
        "message": "That's too personal."
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:34:14.497000Z",
        "message": "I appreciate you letting me know. We can keep things general. No need for specifics. Let's switch gears a bit. When you do use ChatGPT, what part of the experience feels most helpful to you? And is there anything about it that that ever annoys you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:34:28.927000Z",
        "message": "No. It does not."
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:34:31.856000Z",
        "message": "Good to know. Sounds like you haven't run into anything annoying with ChatGPT so far. What is it about the experience that feels most helpful when you use it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:34:43.147000Z",
        "message": "Make things more easier."
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:34:46.887000Z",
        "message": "Nice. Could you walk me through what making things easier looks like for you? When you use ChatGPT? For example, is it about quick answers? Feeling less stressed, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:14.437000Z",
        "message": "Bless blisterous."
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:17.466000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate the word choice. Bless Blistress. Can you tell me more about what that means to you in the context of using ChatGPT?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:27.477000Z",
        "message": "I can't."
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:30.847000Z",
        "message": "That's totally okay. We can move on. Um, have you used any other Answer tools besides ChatGPT, like Google, Perplexity, or or or Gemini? For getting info"
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:40.817000Z",
        "message": "No."
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:43.257000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for clarifying. Sounds like ChatGPT is your main go to. When you think of ChatGPT as a brand or a personality, what kind of vibe do you get? If it were a person at a party, who would it be and how would it act?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:58.737000Z",
        "message": "Easy, simple going, less stressful."
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:06.047000Z",
        "message": "That's a clear vibe. Easy, simple going, less stressful. If you had to pick just a few words that come to mind when you think of ChatGPT, what would they be?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:15.617000Z",
        "message": "Can you repeat the question?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:18.417000Z",
        "message": "Sure thing. If you had to choose just a few words that come to mind, when you think about ChatGPT, what would those words be?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:26.847000Z",
        "message": "Easy, simple, complex at times."
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:31.437000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. Those are great descriptors. Easy, simple, complex at times. Last thing, thinking back to about a year ago. Has anything changed and how often or or how quickly you use ChatGPT to get answers? Or is it about the same?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:46.006000Z",
        "message": "The same."
      },
      {
        "callId": "28e76b4cea904913a2c076c26",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:48.587000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So your habits haven't really changed over the past year. For sharing all this. Before we wrap up, how was it talking to an AI for this interview?"
      },
