  {
    "id": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
    "responseId": "8eea57cb26ae46a081fae3fcc",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:47.166000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:55.445000Z",
        "message": "Doing good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:59.096000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear. Let's jump in. When you need quick answers online, say, you're curious about something or need help with a task, What's typically the first thing you do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:09.406000Z",
        "message": "The first thing that I do is I search I go to my search engine, and if not, I will dig deeper and go into ChatGPT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:22.135000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So your first stop is usually a search engine. Search engine do you tend to use most often for that first search?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:29.656000Z",
        "message": "Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:32.706000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing. Uh, thinking about your last time, uh, using Google, to look something up, can you walk me through step by step what you needed and everything you did to get your answer?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:44.446000Z",
        "message": "Uh, Yeah. I just went on my Safari. I saw, like, Google. And I searched up what I needed to search up. And the answer came up automatically. Pretty quickly, actually. And yeah. I figured out what I needed to figure out."
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:04.776000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for walking me through that. Thinking about that experience, what part felt most helpful to you? And was there anything that frustrated or annoyed you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:13.576000Z",
        "message": "So there wasn't anything that actually frustrated me. And really, that's just because, like, you know, I would say, you know, Google and all these, like, you know, modern day, uh, search engines, they're really advanced. So they were pretty quick to come up with the answer that I needed and it was all set."
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:39.846000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like speed and getting a clear answer are big positives for you. Thinking back to situations when you didn't get what you needed from Google, what do you usually do next? Can you share a specific example of a time that happened?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:52.556000Z",
        "message": "Uh, yes. I went on ChatGPT to do a numbers a mathematical number equation, um, for a investment that I have."
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:09.476000Z",
        "message": "Interesting switch. Can you walk me through that moment? What exactly were you trying to solve? And how did using ChatGPT feel different compared to Google for that task?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:20.816000Z",
        "message": "It was a mathematical numbers equation, uh, for a few real estate properties that I am a co owner of. And it was just it was just super quick. Everything was super steady. And yeah."
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:43.656000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for that. When you used ChatGPT for your real estate calculation, what part of its answer or process felt especially useful or different than what you get with Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:55.806000Z",
        "message": "Well, it was I would say it was about the same speed, um, when it came to searching it up. The only difference from the ChatGPT from the Google is that it acts actually in ChatGPT, uh, the answer was brought out, but it was more in-depth. So it was they explained more things that I needed to know than if I would have just searched it up on Google, it would have probably just came up with the answer, and that said no further explanation."
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:34:29.806000Z",
        "message": "That's really clear. So when you need a deeper explanation or extra details, it sounds like ChatGPT feels more thorough than Google. Has there ever been a time when even ChatGPT didn't quite hit the mark for you, or when you tried another tool like Perplexity or Gemini to compare? Could you tell me about that?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:34:49.886000Z",
        "message": "Honestly, I never I never used another platform, AI platform, aside from So ChatGPT itself is able to resolve anything for me."
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:05.236000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for explaining. So for now, Google is your first stop for speed and convenience, and ChatGPT is your backup for more depth. When you think about the strengths of Google versus ChatGPT, what words are feelings come to mind for each?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:21.296000Z",
        "message": "Uh, very well advanced."
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:25.606000Z",
        "message": "That's an interesting way to put it. When you imagine Google and ChatGPT as people at a party, what kind of personalities or vibes would each have What sort of roles would they play?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:34.126000Z",
        "message": "Okay. Nerds."
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:38.736000Z",
        "message": "Love that. If you had to describe, are they the same kind of nerd, or does Google show up 1 way? And ChatGPT another? Me a bit more about the differences, if any, in how you think about them."
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:50.766000Z",
        "message": "No. I think that I would view them the same because they're both extremely intelligent, um, and, you know, they're they're very mind advanced, I would say."
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:06.896000Z",
        "message": "That's a fun way to describe it. It sounds like they both bring brainpower to the table. Thinking about sharing answers with others is there 1 you'd feel more comfortable quoting to a friend, coworker, or someone you're helping, or does it not really matter which 1? Just checking. Would you feel any difference in trust or credibility when quoting Google versus ChatGPT to someone else? Or do you see them as about equal in that sense?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:35.996000Z",
        "message": "I say that they are equal."
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:40.256000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing your take on that. Looking back over the past year, has anything changed about how often you use Google versus ChatGP or which 1 you reach for first? Any recent"
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:36:49.746000Z",
        "message": "Uh, no. No. Nothing really changed. I still view both of them the same. So nothing negative to say about either."
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:37:00.576000Z",
        "message": "That's really helpful to know. Last quick question. Do you ever hear friends, uh, coworkers, or family talk about using different answer engines? Or recommend specific ones for certain situations? If so, can you share what comes up? If not, no worries."
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:37:18.476000Z",
        "message": "No. Everyone just really just tells me to stick to Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:37:24.916000Z",
        "message": "That's clear. Super interesting to hear. Well, that covers everything. I wanted to ask today. Before we wrap, how did it feel talking to an AI about your search habits? And you're welcome to end the call whenever you'd like."
      },
      {
        "callId": "72921f4bfb844d7c819c2ed9f",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:37:43.136000Z",
        "message": "Uh, Yeah. I I enjoyed talking to you. You actually are so advanced that it it feels like I'm actually talking an actual human being. Yeah. I have nothing negative to say about you. Um, you seem like a well well platform or good platform. So yeah."
      }
