        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:22.743000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you go straight to what's most accessible or right in front of you. Thinking about online searches specifically when you need answers fast, the very first thing you do or use?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "a96c1efa7e7c41878e899deaf",
