        "time": "2025-09-14T00:37:41.013000Z",
        "message": "So ChatGPT feels detailed and maybe even exciting, while Google is more straightforward but lacking in-depth. When you need to share an answer, say, with a friend or coworker, do you ever feel like 1 engine's answer is more credible or worth quoting than the others? Or does it depend on the situation?"
