        "time": "2025-09-14T00:38:39.033000Z",
        "message": "That's a helpful point. So within the last year, you've been reaching for ChatGPT more. Because its answers feel more precise. Meanwhile, Google sometimes sends you all over different websites that don't really get to the heart of of your question. Was there a specific moment or task that made you realize you wanted to try ChatGPT instead of sticking with Google, or did it just gradually happen?"
