        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:01.483000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like it might be 1 of those days. I'll keep things simple. Let's start here. When you need to look something up online, get an answer to a question, or figure something out, what's what's the very first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8c609ea8fd794009a0764d75e",
