        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:18.293000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So Google's your go to. Can you walk me through a recent time you needed an answer? Maybe the last thing you looked up? Start with what you needed and tell me every step you took from there."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8c609ea8fd794009a0764d75e",
