        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:41.073000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for laying that out. When you did that, what part of the experience stood out as especially helpful? Or maybe on the flip side, anything that felt annoying or not quite right about it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8c609ea8fd794009a0764d75e",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
