        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:17.143000Z",
        "message": "Understood. It sounds like Google is pretty locked in for you when it comes to answers. Just curious, have you ever tried using tools like Chat GPT, Perplexity, or Gemini for questions or info? If so, what led you to give them a shot? If not, what's kept you sticking with Google?"
