        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:45.173000Z",
        "message": "That's clear. If it's working, no need. To change. When you think about what makes Google pretty good for you, features or qualities come to mind? Maybe speed, accuracy, trust, or something else."
