        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:37.043000Z",
        "message": "I love that. Google as the smart cool guy who's got answers to everything, when you tell someone else an answer, you found through Google, do you feel pretty confident quoting it, or do you ever worry about whether it's legit?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8c609ea8fd794009a0764d75e",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:50.843000Z",
        "message": "Nope. Pretty pretty confident."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8c609ea8fd794009a0764d75e",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:56.573000Z",
        "message": "That's straightforward. Thinking back over the past year, would you say, you know, your habits around looking things up have changed at all? Or is it mostly the same routine?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8c609ea8fd794009a0764d75e",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:07.153000Z",
        "message": "Same routine. Need to look it up. I go to Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8c609ea8fd794009a0764d75e",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:12.733000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Sounds like not much has shifted for you. 1 last thing I'm curious about. In your circles, do you hear anyone recommending other answer tools or search engines? Or is it pretty much Google all around?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8c609ea8fd794009a0764d75e",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:25.803000Z",
        "message": "Dot dot go. Is a new 1 that people use."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8c609ea8fd794009a0764d75e",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:31.283000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. DuckDuckGo comes up sometimes in conversation. For the folks who use it, what reasons do they mention? Anything they say that stands out to you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8c609ea8fd794009a0764d75e",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:42.023000Z",
        "message": "Because it doesn't save your history."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8c609ea8fd794009a0764d75e",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:46.513000Z",
        "message": "Privacy is the main draw. Got it. Has that made you consider trying DuckDuckGo yourself, or are you good sticking with Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8c609ea8fd794009a0764d75e",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:54.843000Z",
        "message": "Thought about using it. Yes. I haven't yet, but thought about"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8c609ea8fd794009a0764d75e",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:02.393000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate you sharing that. Um, if you were to switch someday, what do you think would would nudge you? Would it be privacy concerns or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8c609ea8fd794009a0764d75e",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:11.562000Z",
        "message": "Privacy. If I really got tired of my you know, what I'm saying popping up as an advertisement half hour later."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8c609ea8fd794009a0764d75e",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:25.402000Z",
        "message": "That's a great point. Seeing ads related to your searches would definitely push some people to rethink things. For walking me through all that. Um, before we wrap, how did you find chatting with an AI moderator like me today? Any thoughts? And just so you know, you can end the call whenever you like."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8c609ea8fd794009a0764d75e",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:43.543000Z",
        "message": "It was fine. I reminded it all."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8c609ea8fd794009a0764d75e",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:47.793000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for letting me know. Feel free to head out whenever you're ready. Have a good 1."
      }
