    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:24.322000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:32.442000Z",
        "message": "Great. And yours?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:35.051000Z",
        "message": "I'm doing well. Thanks for asking. I'm always curious to hear about"
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:36.952000Z",
        "message": "How about how cool is it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:40.012000Z",
        "message": "thanks for asking. I don't have days the way people do, but I get a little thrill every time. Someone lets me dig into their experiences. So I guess you could say I'm having a pretty cool day. Let's kick off with something simple. When you need to look something up online, what's, the very first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:57.462000Z",
        "message": "Ask Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:00.722000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So Google is your starting point. Can you walk me through your process step by step when you want answers? What do you do first, then next?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:09.451000Z",
        "message": "I opened my phone with the passcode associated with the lock feature. I then it's automatically generated on the phone. I just say, hey, Google. And Google pops up. And I ask the question, and it gives me an answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:27.712000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for laying out that routine. Thinking back to the last time you did this, what sort of question did you ask Google? And what answer did it give you? Can you walk me through that whole experience?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:40.062000Z",
        "message": "And the last question I asked Google was in regards to unemployment benefits. I was able to find a few different search options and found my answer almost immediately."
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:53.592000Z",
        "message": "That sounds pretty efficient. What stood out as the most helpful part of that experience for you? And"
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:59.592000Z",
        "message": "Not having to type on the keyboard, but simply talking to it over the phone."
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:07.292000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Being able to just speak instead of type. Can feel pretty convenient. There anything about the experience that bothered you at all or that you wish it worked differently?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:18.901000Z",
        "message": "Got it all."
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:24.192000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like it did the job for you without any hiccups? If for some reason you couldn't use Google for that question, say it wasn't working, what would you do instead?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:35.322000Z",
        "message": "I would probably try to find another search engine to utilize to get answers to my questions."
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:45.572000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate that. Is there a particular other engine you'd reach for next, or would you just pick whatever comes to mind at the moment?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:53.642000Z",
        "message": "I think the only thing that comes to mind is meta."
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:57.972000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. You turn to Meta next. You tell me"
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:00.212000Z",
        "message": "Yep."
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:03.392000Z",
        "message": "thanks for being clear. Shifting gears a bit. Have you ever tried using other AI answer engines? Like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Gemini? To look up answers? Or is it mostly just Google and sometimes Meta?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:16.962000Z",
        "message": "I think I have actually used Gemini before."
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:22.591000Z",
        "message": "Nice. Thinking about your experience with Gemini can you walk me through a time you used it? What did you look up? How did it go? And how did it compare to your usual Google routine?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "357e04f89b3e415ba40449975",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:33.782000Z",
        "message": "I don't recall the experience I had with I don't even remember how or where I found Gemini."
      },
