        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:15.257000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:23.137000Z",
        "message": "It's going good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:25.887000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. When you need answers online, say, you're trying to figure something out, what's what's the very first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:34.767000Z",
        "message": "Google Gemini. Is what I use."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:40.937000Z",
        "message": "Got it. You reached for Google Gemini first. Can you walk me through"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:43.957000Z",
        "message": "Yep."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:47.357000Z",
        "message": "thinking back to the last time you used Gemini. What was going on? Can you walk me through what you needed and every step you took? Starting from the moment you realized you had a question?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:58.626000Z",
        "message": "Yes. I was building something, and I wanna know the exact radius of something. So I asked Google Gemini and they helped me out with it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:11.437000Z",
        "message": "That sounds like a pretty practical need. Can you tell me more about what you you typed into Gemini, what came back, how you decided if the answer was right for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:22.577000Z",
        "message": "It was a radius of a hundred and 20 degree circle."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:28.647000Z",
        "message": "So you typed in something like what's the radius of a 120 degree circle? When Gemini gave you an answer, what did you do next? Did you trust the answer? Or did you double check it somewhere else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:39.837000Z",
        "message": "I trusted the answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:43.567000Z",
        "message": "What about Gemini's response made you feel confident trusting it instead of double checking somewhere else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:50.346000Z",
        "message": "Google Gemini is very good. It's never let me down. In its later stages. In its early stages, it was not that good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:00.157000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like your trust in Gemini has grown over time. Can you remember anything specific that changed? Either in the tool itself or in your experience? That made you start relying on it more these days?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:13.297000Z",
        "message": "AI tools got a whole lot better. In my opinion, in the last few years. So I've been using I use Amazon Alexa and all Google Gemini all the time."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:28.826000Z",
        "message": "It's interesting that you brought up Alexa too. When you're working on something and need a quick answer, makes you reach for Gemini? Compared to Alexa or other tools for that matter?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:40.517000Z",
        "message": "It depends if I have my phone or not."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:44.617000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. It's partly about which device you have handy. When you do have your phone and"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:49.947000Z",
        "message": "Yep."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:53.917000Z",
        "message": "thinking about the experience, what part of using Gemini feels most helpful to you? And is there anything that ever feels annoying or gets in the way?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:03.987000Z",
        "message": "No. There's nothing annoying that gets underway. It's very practical. It tells you the answers. That you need to know when you ask a question to it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:14.837000Z",
        "message": "It sounds like simplicity and directness matter a lot to you. If you hadn't used Gemini in that moment, say, wasn't available, what would you have done instead?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:24.837000Z",
        "message": "I would've Google searched it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:27.887000Z",
        "message": "So if Gemini isn't available, regular Google search becomes your fallback. When you use Google Search instead,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:33.517000Z",
        "message": "Yep."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:36.936000Z",
        "message": "let's shift gears for a second. Have you ever switched between Gemini and something like ChatGPT or Perplexity for a question? If so, what made you change tools that time?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:46.857000Z",
        "message": "Yes. Yes. I did that because, um, I didn't trust the answer on 1 of the service So I tried it on another 1."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:59.897000Z",
        "message": "That's a useful workaround. When you switched, can you remember which engines you used and what the answer felt like? Were they different in any clear way?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:08.356000Z",
        "message": "Janet GTP was what I used. And it was the same answer over and over again. Everyone every I also use Perplexity too, and that was the same answer on that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:24.187000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like across ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Gemini, you got the same answer. Did anything about how those engines answered the tone, the detail, citations, speed stand out to you? Or did it mostly feel similar?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:38.487000Z",
        "message": "Yes. Google Gemini was faster than all of them."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:44.087000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. Speed really makes a difference for you. Besides being fast, is there anything about how Gemini responds that feels unique compared to ChatGPT or Perplexity? Or is speed the standout factor?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:58.047000Z",
        "message": "Speed is a standout factor in how accurate that it is."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:03.727000Z",
        "message": "Accuracy matters too. If you had to line up those engines, Gemini, ChatGPT, Perplexity, from most helpful to least for you, What's the order and and what's behind that ranking?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:15.017000Z",
        "message": "Gemini is the best because it gives you the best answers. And it's the fastest Repel XD is, uh, next besides beside Amazon Alexa and then comes chat GTP."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:31.467000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for breaking that down. Uh, you mentioned Amazon Alexa. Um, How does it fit into your ranking? Is there anything about Alexa that stands out compared to the others or is it mostly device convenience?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:43.926000Z",
        "message": "Device convenience."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:47.607000Z",
        "message": "Understood. Thinking about these engines, if each 1 were a person at a party, who would Gemini be? And how would you describe how it acts?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:59.217000Z",
        "message": "Gemini would be the know it all. Or Pepsi would be the sports commentator. And Chad GTP would be the barbecue chef."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:14.396000Z",
        "message": "I love those descriptions. What words or or feelings come to mind? When you think of Google Gemini? And if you compare that to you feel about Perplexity or ChatGPT, what's different?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:27.577000Z",
        "message": "It's fine to use. It's funny sometimes to use, and it's always right."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:36.307000Z",
        "message": "So with Gemini, you get reliability. A bit of humor, and you feel good using it. Does that sense of always right make you more likely to share its answers with others? Or do you usually check things before sharing?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 43,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:49.777000Z",
        "message": "I usually check things before share."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:55.547000Z",
        "message": "When you check, do you have a go to source for double checking? Or do you just pick a different engine For example, Perplexity or ChatGPT?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 45,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:34:04.867000Z",
        "message": "Yes. Just speak chat GTP."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:34:09.297000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful. Thinking back over the past year, has anything changed about how often you use Gemini or other engines? Any shifts in your habits or which ones you trust most?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 47,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:34:19.887000Z",
        "message": "No. Not at all."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 48,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:34:24.397000Z",
        "message": "Alright. Last question for me. Do friends or coworkers ever talk about which engine they use or recommend certain ones for specific tasks? If so, which ones come up most often?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 49,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:34:36.867000Z",
        "message": "Google Gemini and Perplexity and Apple Intelligence."
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 50,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:34:42.707000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing all that. Uh, before we wrap up, how did you find chatting with an AI about your habits today? Anything about this interview experience that stood out to you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "0bfb5ab4437e4055b9390819a",
        "index": 51,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:34:54.087000Z",
        "message": "Yes. It seems like I'm talking to another human."
      },
