  {
    "id": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
    "responseId": "9438fde0a86a4eb9a2ac5f282",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:47.054000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:55.464000Z",
        "message": "Going very well. Thank you."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:58.194000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. Let's start with something easy. When you need to find an answer online, maybe for a random fact or help with work, what's the very first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:08.844000Z",
        "message": "Go"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:13.403000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you usually go you mean you head straight to Google or something else? Walk me through what happens next after you decide you need an answer. Feel free to ask me any questions. Are you still there?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:43.564000Z",
        "message": "Yes. I'm here. Can you hear me?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:46.314000Z",
        "message": "I can definitely hear you. Thanks for checking. So picking up where we left off. When you need an answer and you go, do you mean you go straight to Google? Or is there a different tool or website you usually use first? What does your process look like?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:00.134000Z",
        "message": "No. I just I go straight for Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:05.494000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for clarifying. When you search on Google, can you tell me about the steps you take? For example, do you type exactly what comes to mind? Do you scan the results, or do you look for certain types of sources? How does it usually go for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:30.383000Z",
        "message": "I use the Google's AI search function."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:35.474000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. Thanks for sharing that. So when you use Google's AI search function, tell me the full story of the last time you remember using it. What did you need to find, and what did you do step by step?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:48.734000Z",
        "message": "I was looking up the news item, and I asked the Google AI to summarize a YouTube video about it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:59.324000Z",
        "message": "That's a cool example. Can you walk me through exactly what you did starting from realizing you wanted a summary to the steps you took in Google's AI? And what happened after."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:11.214000Z",
        "message": "Well, I I just went to Google, and I typed in in natural language what I wanted to find out. And once it suggested some YouTube videos, I asked it to summarize 1 of those videos."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:25.794000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for breaking that down. When Google's AI gave you the summary, what stood out about the experience? Was there anything that felt especially helpful or maybe annoying about how it handled your request?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:37.444000Z",
        "message": "No. It was pretty comprehensive, and it it helped me find what I the information I was looking for."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:43.564000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like it hit the mark for you. If you hadn't used Google's AI for that summary, what do you think you would have tried instead?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:53.094000Z",
        "message": "I'm not familiar with the other AIs yet, so I'd probably just scroll through YouTube videos until I found what I was looking for."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:06.813000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. Just relying on YouTube and searching manually. When you're using Google's AI, do you ever feel curious about other tools like ChatGPT or Perplexity, or has Google just become your comfortable default?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:20.854000Z",
        "message": "Google has become my comfortable default. I've messed around with chat GBT a couple times, but I like the Google interface better."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:28.774000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful to hear. When you say you like the Google interface better, about it makes you prefer it over something like ChatGPT?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:38.324000Z",
        "message": "Just the way just the natural language that it uses is is better than ChatGPT, I think. And the results that I've gotten Google have always been superior to ChatGPT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:53.014000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. When you think about superior results, what does that look like for you? Is it about accuracy, detail, speed, something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:02.853000Z",
        "message": "Basically, accuracy."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:05.704000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So when Google's AI gives you an answer, do you ever check other sources to make sure it's accurate, or do you tend to trust what it provides right away?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:14.704000Z",
        "message": "I've basically become I've I've come to trust Google. I I haven't put the put the different engine side by side. But Google has always been has always worked for me."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:31.304000Z",
        "message": "Understood. Thinking about the different engines for a moment, if Google's AI summary, ChatGPT, or another tool gave answers to the same question, which which one's answer would you feel most comfortable sharing with a friend or coworker? What makes you feel that way?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:46.244000Z",
        "message": "I'd say Google because most everybody knows how to use Google. And so people are a little put off by ChatGPT. And its interface. So I usually recommend just to use Google. Since pretty much everybody knows how to use it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:05.073000Z",
        "message": "That's really interesting. When you think about Google compared to other engines, are there any words or feelings that come to mind for each For example, if Google AI was a person at a party, how would it act? What about ChatGPT?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:21.284000Z",
        "message": "Google had a party."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:24.184000Z",
        "message": "Let's imagine Google"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:24.254000Z",
        "message": "Google would yep. Yeah. Google just has a more natural language I mean, as far as I as far I haven't checked chat GPT in a while, but Google has, a more natural language You know, it it sounds more like you're talking to a person than an AI."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:44.514000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. That's a good way to put it. So if you if you picture Google as as someone at a party, does it feel like Google blends in easily? Or stands out somehow? And thinking about Chachi"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:33:54.424000Z",
        "message": "No. Yeah. It blends in pretty well. Google blends pretty well in comparison to ChatGPT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:34:02.693000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So Google feels familiar, approachable, maybe almost like a regular guest. If you picture ChatGPT at that same party, how would it act? Any particular vibe come to mind?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:34:13.484000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. A little bit more awkward. I mean, you get the same most of the time, you get the same results. Between the 2 engines, but chat g 2 p t just has you you can tell that you're not speaking to a real person."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:34:29.654000Z",
        "message": "That's really helpful. Thinking back over the past year or so, has anything changed about how you look things up online? Any moments when you reach for Google's AI features instead of just using regular search or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:34:43.234000Z",
        "message": "No. I I use at this point, I I pretty much just default to use AI mode. And then go from go from there as far as the recommendations for what websites or information I might need"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:00.354000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for explaining that. Last question for you. If something changed and Google's AI didn't have the accuracy or natural language you expect, uh, what do you think would make you consider switching to another answer engine for your searches?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:15.804000Z",
        "message": "Um, if if the quality of the results started to wane, I I would consider using another engine. Probably chat ChatGPT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:26.163000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. That quality really drives your choice. Thanks for sharing all that. That's all I've got for you today. Before we wrap up, how was this AI interview experience for you? And you're welcome to end the the call whenever you'd like."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:42.354000Z",
        "message": "The AI the quality of the AI in this phone call was great, and, uh, I appreciate you asking me the questions."
      },
      {
        "callId": "003de5a295fd43eda1532b083",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:35:52.413000Z",
        "message": "Thank you for calling."
      }
