  {
    "id": "3d1dc974a24f46ca97f65c3d7",
    "responseId": "123f78f55df84714869b1c2af",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "3d1dc974a24f46ca97f65c3d7",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:12.508000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3d1dc974a24f46ca97f65c3d7",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:20.548000Z",
        "message": "Very well. How about yours?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3d1dc974a24f46ca97f65c3d7",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:24.128000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. I'm having a solid day myself. Always curious to hear what have to say about how they find answers online. So, uh, to get us started, when you're looking for an answer online, could be anything from a quick fact to something you're researching. What's what's the first thing you usually do? Walk me through your typical process."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3d1dc974a24f46ca97f65c3d7",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:44.188000Z",
        "message": "Well, first of all, I would probably ask Alexa But if I was on my phone, I would ask Siri."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3d1dc974a24f46ca97f65c3d7",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:52.658000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. You turn to voice assistance first. Can you tell me more about what usually prompts you to use"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3d1dc974a24f46ca97f65c3d7",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:55.628000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3d1dc974a24f46ca97f65c3d7",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:59.568000Z",
        "message": "Alexa or Siri instead of, say, searching online yourself? Maybe the last time you did this, what did you need to know, and how did it play out? Are you still there? Are you still there?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3d1dc974a24f46ca97f65c3d7",
        "index": 7,
