      {
        "callId": "3d1dc974a24f46ca97f65c3d7",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:48.458000Z",
        "message": "Oh, yeah. Yes. Okay. So I was texting someone about Iceland. And I had a question about location and population. So I just asked Alexa."
