        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:21.407000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for confirming. Is there ever a time when you choose not to use Alexa or Siri Maybe you switch to Google or another tool for answers. Instead. If so, what leads you to make that switch?"
      },
      {
