        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:33.048000Z",
        "message": "Okay. First, my go to, as I said, is Siri or Alexa. And then if that doesn't work, if if they it don't give me an answer I want, then I go to Google, which is takes much longer, I think, than just to ask speaking what you need."
      },
