        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:52.468000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. When you switch to Google after Alexa or Siri, what kind of questions usually push you to do that? What feels different about the experience when you use Google instead."
