    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:50.840000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:58.640000Z",
        "message": "It's going well. How about you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:01.930000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. I'm doing well too. For asking. Let's start by talking about how you usually get answers online. When you're curious about something or need quick information, what's the first thing you tend to do"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:15.339000Z",
        "message": "Either Google search or use Gemini, a"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:21.750000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So you usually choose between Google Search and Gemini. Can you walk me through how you decide which 1 to use for a particular question or task?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:31.260000Z",
        "message": "If it's something that's more specific, more complicated, I would typically ask Gemini. And if it's just something simple and quick, like, you know, looking up an address or something like that, I'll use Google search."
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:47.240000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. Thinking back to the last time you used Gemini for a more specific or complicated question, you tell me the full story? What did what did you need, and what steps did you go through?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:01.370000Z",
        "message": "So I just needed tips on a drawing that I was doing, and like, how to shade a certain area of it and what are the steps to do it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:13.410000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you were looking for shading tips your drawing. Can you describe how you interacted with Gemini for this? You know, for example, what did you type in? And how did Gemini's response help or not help with your drawing project?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:28.640000Z",
        "message": "In particular, this time, I used to be live option. So it was like kinda how we're speaking now."
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:40.090000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. You used the live conversation option with Gemini. Can you tell me more about what that back and forth felt like? What kinds of questions or prompts did you give? And what did Gemini's responses make you feel as you worked through your drawing?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:56.400000Z",
        "message": "Well, I mean, it it was pretty informative. And you know, made me feel kind of confident, like I was doing I was doing good in my drawing. And kept giving me positive feedback."
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:17.290000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like it was a supportive experience, uh, besides the the positive feedback. Was there anything about Gemini's responses or the way it interacted that stood out? Maybe in terms of detail, clarity, or or or the steps that suggested. Anything that felt especially helpful or maybe a bit frustrating"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 13,
