      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:39.240000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Shifting gears a bit. Can you think of a time when you used Google Search instead maybe for a simple task? What was the situation, and how did you go about it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:56.280000Z",
        "message": "So I believe that the last time I used Google search for a test would be, like, a have to look up a calculator, and to use it real quick."
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:11.480000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for that example. When you looked up the calculator, uh, on Google search, can you walk me through what you did, like, what you typed in, how you got, what you needed, and how you felt about using Google for for that sort of simple task?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:27.260000Z",
        "message": "Could you repeat that? I'm sorry."
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:30.520000Z",
        "message": "Of course, no problem at all. When you needed a calculator and used Google Search, can you walk me through exactly what you did? For example, what did you type in? How did you get what you needed? And how did you feel about that experience?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:45.090000Z",
        "message": "So I I just typed in calculator. And it, you know, it brought up 1 I could use it on a web page, And I mean, I did the math real quick, and that was it. It was I mean, it was pretty quick and simple."
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:03.510000Z",
        "message": "Sounds really straightforward. When you compare that to your Gemini experience with drawing tips, what feels different for you about using Google for quick stuff versus Gemini for more complex questions?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:16.360000Z",
        "message": "Well, so Gemini is more descriptive give you more detail, and kind of gives you different ideas along the way as well. So it doesn't just give you a simple answer It gives you well, so, like, an answer and alternatives."
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:42.810000Z",
        "message": "That's a great description. When Gemini gives you those those different ideas and alternatives, how does that affect your confidence or or creativity? Compared to a straight answer like Google's calculator?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:54.870000Z",
        "message": "Well, I mean, it's"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:00.270000Z",
        "message": "Take your time. What comes to mind when you think about how Gemini's detailed responses affect your confidence or creativity especially compared to Google's more direct answers? Feel free to ask me any questions. Are you still there?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:38.080000Z",
        "message": "Yes. I'm still here."
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:41.289000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for confirming. Picking up where we left off. When Gemini gives those detailed answers and alternatives, do you notice any changes in how you approach your task or project? For example, does it ever lead you to try a different technique or feel more sure about what you're doing?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:58.229000Z",
        "message": "Yes. I mean, it makes me explore different avenues. Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:04.199000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. When Gemini helps you explore"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:05.150000Z",
        "message": "Or it doesn't make me."
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:09.810000Z",
        "message": "got it. So Gemini doesn't necessarily make you try new things, but it opens up options that you can choose from. Thinking about that, what do you like most about"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:18.240000Z",
        "message": "Exactly."
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:21.130000Z",
        "message": "thanks for clarifying. Now thinking about both Gemini and Google, if you could line them up from most helpful to least helpful for your own needs, how would you rank them? And what makes you put the 1 ahead of the other?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:37.410000Z",
        "message": "Well, for I mean, really, I I'd go with Gemini overall, like, just for everything. But sometimes it's just a little bit simpler to, you know, I'm already on, uh, say, a website on my phone or something, I can just flick over to Google real quick instead of you know, pulling up Gemini."
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:58.220000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful. So sounds like Gemini is your top pick overall. But Google is quicker when you're already browsing or need something super simple. If you were telling a friend about the personalities of these engines. Like, if Google and Gemini were people at a party, how would you describe each 1?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:17.240000Z",
        "message": "Google would be the more introvert, like, just kinda you know, not really talking to many people, but you know, still having a drink here and there. Being a little bit shy, I guess. And Gemini would be, like, a super smart, friendly, you know, like a people pleaser, I guess."
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:44Z",
        "message": "That's great imagery. Thinking about trust, when you get an answer you want to share with someone else, maybe quote it, does either Google or Gemini feel more credible to you What leads you to feel that way?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:57.259000Z",
        "message": "Well, I mean, probably probably Gemini just because it's it's trained. Like, you know, it's trained AI."
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:07.680000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. Can you tell me more about what makes Gemini's training feel trustworthy to you? It the way it explains things, the sources it sites, or maybe just the overall experience?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:19.729000Z",
        "message": "Well, I mean, pretty much everything you just said."
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:25.449000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Looking back over the past year or so, have you noticed any changes in how often you use Google? Compared to Gemini? Was there any moment or or reason that led you to use Gemini more than before?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:42.329000Z",
        "message": "Not specifically. I can't think of any moments or anything, but Gemini just I started using AI a little bit more and getting more comfortable with it, trying to do a little bit of side work. Or figure out how to make a passive income with artificial intelligence, and know, Gemini just became part of the daily activity when I was doing that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:11.800000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful context. Thinking about those daily activities, like using AI for side work or exploring passive income, what, if anything, have you wished these engines could do differently or better as you use them more often? Anything on your wish list?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 43,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:29.170000Z",
        "message": "Nothing that I can think of. I mean, I wanted to to be able you know, relating do certain kinds of searches, like, that are you know, not considered I don't know. No. I can't think of nothing."
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:49.400000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate your honesty. Before we wrap up, is there anything else about how you use Gemini or Google that stands out for you? Any thoughts or stories that haven't come up yet?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "62a2c4548351481eb6e59df0e",
        "index": 45,
