  {
    "id": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
    "responseId": "ad808f0dc7334c26b2fc89f8d",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:05.866000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:14.566000Z",
        "message": "Good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:18.376000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. Let's start with something simple. When you need answers online, like, solving a random question or figuring something out, what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:30.886000Z",
        "message": "I asked chat GBT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:34.066000Z",
        "message": "Got it. ChatGPT is your starting point. Can you walk me through your typical process? You use ChatGPT to look something up? What's the sequence"
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:44.096000Z",
        "message": "I usually pull up JaiGVT and ask it the questions that I'm needing in find out."
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:51.456000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. Thinking back to the last time you did that, can you tell me the full story? What did you need, and how did you go about asking JaiGBT?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:00.466000Z",
        "message": "I needed to know what all was going on in Palestine, so I asked Chad GBT what are the issues going on in Palestine."
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:11.956000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that example. What stood out to you about the experience? Was there anything especially helpful or maybe even frustrating? About how ChatGPT handled your question?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:23.686000Z",
        "message": "It was extremely helpful. I like the way that it spread all the information and presented it to me very well."
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:33.056000Z",
        "message": "Nice. What was it about the way ChatGPT presented the information? That worked well for you? Was it the amount of detail, the"
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:39.665000Z",
        "message": "It was very it was very easy to understand, and it was simple and to the point."
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:49.796000Z",
        "message": "That's clear. When you got that answer, did you feel confident in the information? Or did you do anything extra, like double check details elsewhere?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:58.466000Z",
        "message": "I felt confident."
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:02.316000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for that. Now if you haven't used ChatGPT for your Palestine question, what else might you have done to find those answers?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:10.106000Z",
        "message": "I would have asked Google or looked it up on Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:16.006000Z",
        "message": "Alright. Thinking about times you've used Google instead of ChatGPT, does the experience feel different to you? If so, what feels different about using Google for those sorts of questions?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:29.026000Z",
        "message": "ChatTBT was simpler. Google gives me a wide variety of answers, so I'm having to look through deeper through all the information."
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:40.506000Z",
        "message": "That's really clear. So with Google, you're doing more sifting, lots to sort through. Is there ever a situation where you prefer Google over ChatGPT? If so, what kinds of questions or tasks tend to push you back to Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:55.056000Z",
        "message": "There is no situations where I wouldn't go to."
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:01.336000Z",
        "message": "Got it. You're mainly sticking with ChatGPT. If you line up ChatGPT and Google side by side, how would you describe each one's biggest strength from from your perspective?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:12.286000Z",
        "message": "Chad GBT gives you a more simple presentation of the answers to the questions you're asking."
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:19.906000Z",
        "message": "And how about Google? What, if anything, would you say is its main strength? Even if you don't use it first anymore?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:26.846000Z",
        "message": "Google's main strength is has a vast source of information from all over the web."
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:35.386000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for that. If you imagine each of these tools ChatGPT and Google, as a person at a party kind of guests would each 1 be? How would they act?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:47.626000Z",
        "message": "Chad GBT would be simple when straightforward, while Google would be complicated and confusing."
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:54.696000Z",
        "message": "That paints a pretty vivid picture. When you share an answer with someone else, say, copy paste or tell a friend, which engine's information feels most credible to you to quote. Why?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:06.886000Z",
        "message": "Chat GBT because it words it in a simple manner."
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:12.906000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate that perspective. Uh, thinking back over the past year, has anything changed about how you look things up online? Any habits or routines that's that's shifted for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:23.316000Z",
        "message": "Nothing has changed."
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:27.256000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for being straightforward. For the last touch, have friends or coworkers ever mentioned certain answer engines to you, like ChatGPT, Google, Perplexity, Gemini? Which ones and what kinds of things do they say about them?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:42.045000Z",
        "message": "They always recommend ChatGBT because it's very user friendly."
      },
      {
        "callId": "1a3e635046ee4007b0ee6ddce",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:48.326000Z",
        "message": "That's super clear. Thanks for sharing all that. It's really helpful to understand your search habits and what works for you. Quick 1. How did you find talking with an AI today? And just letting you know, you're all set. You can end the call whenever you'd like."
      }
