        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:51.500000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. So when you need answers online, even for something simple or random, what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c4a994d3708848b9be794a168",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:59.329000Z",
