        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:06.820000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like Google is your go to. Can you walk me through what that process looks like for you starting from when a question pops into your mind to finding the answer?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c4a994d3708848b9be794a168",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:17.580000Z",
