        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:21.790000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Sometimes Google, sometimes Instagram. Can you tell me about the last time used Instagram instead of Google to look something up? What were you trying to find and how did you go about it?"
