        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:47.350000Z",
        "message": "That's really telling, getting answers that make you feel more confident. Is it mostly because the advice comes from people you relate to, or or is there another reason another reason those answers stand out for you?"
      },
