        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:59.850000Z",
        "message": "I use chatty pt and Google too."
      },
      {
        "callId": "c4a994d3708848b9be794a168",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:05.700000Z",
        "message": "Nice. So you use both ChatGPT and Google. Can you tell me about a time when you chose ChatGPT instead of Google for a question? What kind of question was it? And what made you pick ChatGPT that time?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "c4a994d3708848b9be794a168",
