        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:26.130000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful to know. Thinking about the last time you used ChatGPT for an educational question, can you walk me through what you needed, how you asked, and what the experience was like from start to finish?"
      },
