        "message": "Yeah. AI is a very key attribute better than Google. AI is the most most popular right now attending attending because most of people use AI judge a bit. But in you know, Google use, but AI HTTP is very used, like doing something and you create new idea, new idea generate That's why in, uh, I think, AI best"
