      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:57.943000Z",
        "message": "Like I said, I can't think off the top of my head the things I've asked Gemini, but I guess they were more like, vague kind of questions. Not very specific questions like the Google can answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:16.533000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. So when you say vague questions, can you describe what feels different about those versus the specific ones you'd give to Google? Going on in your mind when you're picking between the 2?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:29.703000Z",
        "message": "Things that might not have a an exact straightforward answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:35.972000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful. So for those not straightforward questions, when you use Gemini, how do do you tend to feel about the answers it gives back? Anything stand out?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:45.593000Z",
        "message": "Yep. So far, I've been very happy with the answers."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:50.763000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. What is it about Gemini's Answers that actually makes you feel happy? Compared to what you might get from Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:57.883000Z",
        "message": "They, um, all except for 1 time, it's given me the answers I was seeking. Except for 1 time, it was not able to give me the answer I was seeking."
      },
