        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:35.422000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. It Fair enough. Not every search sticks in the memory. Especially if it's not urgent. When Gemini does give you answers that hit the mark, is there anything in the experience? How the response is written? The level of detail or or something else? That you especially notice or appreciate."
