        "message": "Uh, not that I can recall. I'm just happy to get a good answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:03.963000Z",
        "message": "Simple and straightforward sounds like you value just getting what you need."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:08.133000Z",
        "message": "Right. Exactly."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:08.353000Z",
        "message": "So if you didn't shifting gears for a moment. Thinking about Google and Gemini as brands or personalities, if each were a person at a party, who do you think they'd be How would they act?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
