        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:34.183000Z",
        "message": "That's a cool way to put it. Rigid versus fluid. Um, when you say Google is rigid, what kind of behavior comes to mind? And for Gemini, what does fluid look like and how it acts?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:48.443000Z",
