      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:15.783000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for clarifying. You see Google as more rigid and Gemini as more innovative and intuitive. That says a lot about how they feel to you. Thinking about trust for a second, if you find an answer with Gemini or Google and want to share it with someone, does 1 feel more credible or quote worthy to you, or are they pretty much the same?"
