        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:59.013000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:01.453000Z",
        "message": "When sharing answers. When you're searching just for yourself,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:01.873000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:05.093000Z",
        "message": "does that same trust difference matter as much? Or do you feel okay using Gemini even if you wouldn't quote it to others?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:16.103000Z",
        "message": "So far I feel okay as Gemini because usually I'm answer I'm relatively simple questions."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:27.433000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. For those relatively simple personal questions. You're comfortable with Gemini. Even if you might hesitate to share its answers more publicly. Thinking back over the past year,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 43,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:37.492000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:39.653000Z",
        "message": "has anything changed about how often you use Google versus Gemini or the way you decide which 1 to try first?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 45,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:46.933000Z",
        "message": "Well, I've just started Gemini in the past maybe 2 months. So I've obviously used Google a lot more. I've been using Google for years."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:00.723000Z",
        "message": "That's a long history with Google. Since starting with Gemini recently, have you noticed yourself"
