        "index": 48,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:05.823000Z",
        "message": "reaching for it more often, or is it still a once in a while thing?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7e7d79921e704072a5c3d6877",
        "index": 49,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:10.803000Z",
        "message": "It is still a once in a while thing. I'm still sort of getting used to it."
      },
