  {
    "id": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
    "responseId": "2530e827553e4f5c887642a22",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:14.713000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:23.403000Z",
        "message": "Good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:26.313000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. When you need"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:27.403000Z",
        "message": "Good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:30.543000Z",
        "message": "glad to hear it. Let's start with something simple. When you need answers online, uh, any kind of info, what's the first thing you usually do? Feel free to ask me any questions."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:56.853000Z",
        "message": "Hello?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:57.653000Z",
        "message": "Feel free to ask me any questions."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:00.923000Z",
        "message": "I said I used chat GPT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:05.013000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. So you usually reach for ChatGPT when you need answers online. Could you walk me through the last time you used it? What exactly did you need? And what were the steps you took from start to finish?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:18.813000Z",
        "message": "I just asked it for a recipe."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:23.663000Z",
        "message": "Nice. Can you tell me more about that moment? What led you to look for a recipe using ChatGPT? Instead of another tool? What kind of recipe were you after? How did the experience play out for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:37.203000Z",
        "message": "I use child GPT because it was the easiest, and I was trying to find a recipe for dumplings."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:47.613000Z",
        "message": "You picked ChatGPT because it felt easiest? Got it. Let's dig in a bit. When you searched for that dumpling recipe, what part of the whole experience felt especially helpful or smooth for you? Anything about the process that was annoying or less useful?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:05.513000Z",
        "message": "No. I don't think so."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:09.873000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Sounds like it just worked the way you wanted. If you hadn't used ChatGPT for that, dumpling recipe, what do what you think you would have done instead?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:21.723000Z",
        "message": "Probably would have used Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:26.853000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful to know. When you think about searching for a recipe on Google versus asking ChatGPT, what feels different about how you'd get the answer from each?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:37.643000Z",
        "message": "It's because has, like, a person not like a person, a talking AI that you can just, like, when you're doing it, like, right now, you can just ask them a question out loud. And they would answer correctly."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:57.543000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. So having an AI that that responds kind of like a person, more conversational, easy to interact with is a big part of what makes ChatGPT useful for you. Does that feeling of talking to someone change how confident you feel about the answers you get compared to, say, reading results from Google or another search engine?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:16.503000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. I think it's pretty it's, like, really helpful because it's, like, LGBT as option. Where you can talk to, like, a AI assistant, but it's like you're literally talking to a person. It feels like you're talking to a person."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:33.613000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like that. Human like conversation really stands out for you. When you think about know, other engines, maybe Google's regular search, Gemini, or Perplexity, do any of them give you a similar feeling, or is ChatGPT unique in that way for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:47.813000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. Chad GPT is unique."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:51.543000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate you sharing that. If you were to line them up chat GPT, Google, Gemini, Perplexity, from most to least helpful, how would you rank them for your needs these days? And what makes you put each 1 where you do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:06.193000Z",
        "message": "I'll say, uh, Chad's. Yeah. Chad GBT would be the number 1, Gemini would be, like, number 3. And then would be, like, number 2."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:18.753000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for rank Just so I'm clear, that's ChatGPT first. Then Perplexity second, Gemini third, and Google after that. Could you tell me what makes ChatGPT stand out? And earn that top spot for you? Well, what landed, like, Perplexity, Gemini, and Google? In the order you mentioned?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:38.213000Z",
        "message": "Like I said, it's like I'm talking to a real person. Like, I'm talking to you. It's the exact same feature on ChatGBT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:48.893000Z",
        "message": "So that person like conversational feel really puts ChatGPT at the top for you. How about perplexity? What's different or or less appealing about using it compared to ChatGPT? Anything that stands out"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:03.703000Z",
        "message": "It doesn't have that feature or or I'm not aware of."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:09.603000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So Perplexity doesn't give you that same conversational vibe, at least as far as you know. When you think about Gemini and Google, do you ever use them for anything specific? Or do they just feel less helpful overall?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:22.703000Z",
        "message": "I think they're less helpful overall."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:29.273000Z",
        "message": "Understood. Thinking back over the past year, do you notice any changes in how often you're using chat GPT compared to Google or other engines? Has anything specific triggered a shift in your habits?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:42.082000Z",
        "message": "Nope. Not at all."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:47.923000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing. Before we wrap up, when you get an answer from ChatGPT, do you ever share those responses with friends or coworkers? And if so, does anything about ChatGPT's answers make you feel more or less confident sharing them?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:03.043000Z",
        "message": "No."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:06.783000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for answering that. 1 last quick thing. You could wish for a new feature or something that would make ChatGPT or another answer engine even more useful for you, what would that be? Or are you pretty satisfied with how things work now?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:21.303000Z",
        "message": "I would say if I needed help with, like, something on my phone, I would like screen share so they can see my screen."
      },
      {
        "callId": "f71498eb948d4ca8ba31474b4",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:31.443000Z",
        "message": "That's a great idea. Having a screen share feature so the AI could help more directly with what you're doing. Thanks for being so open today. Any feedback for me about how this AI interview felt for you? And just so you know, you're all set and can end the call whenever you'd like."
      }
