        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:22.586000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like it's going pretty well."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:22.966000Z",
        "message": "Hello? Yeah."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:25.116000Z",
        "message": "Hey. I'm here. Sounds like you might just be checking in. How's your day going so far?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:30.116000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. Good. How about yours?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:36.226000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for asking. I don't really have days like you do. But I'm ready to dig in and listen. So when you need answers online, like, anything from what's the weather to how do I fix this thing, what's the very first thing you usually do, me through your typical routine."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:54.286000Z",
        "message": "I really just opened Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:59.636000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So Google's your go to. Uh, can you tell me about the last time you used Google? To look something up? What was the question? And walk me through exactly what you did from start to finish."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:12.876000Z",
        "message": "Picked up my phone and looked to see what time Michigan game was today. Oh, and what channel to watch it on?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:21.236000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that example. So you picked up your phone. Opened Google, and searched for the Michigan game time and channel. What happened next? Did you get the answer right away, or did you need to click through a few links?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:35.206000Z",
        "message": "Nope. They told me."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:38.576000Z",
        "message": "Sounds pretty seamless. When Google gave you the answer, was it kind of right there? At the top, like, a summary box? Or"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:44.456000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. Because I searched sorry. I searched that up a lot, so it was right there."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:52.006000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. It's like Google knows what you're asking before you finish typing. Thinking about that experience"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:56.476000Z",
        "message": "All the time."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:00.706000Z",
        "message": "So it sounds like searching for game times and channels is something you do often, and Google is quick with those answers. What part of that experience feels most"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:09.866000Z",
        "message": "Yep."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:13.016000Z",
        "message": "when you use Google for these kinds of quick answers, is there anything that ever feels annoying or or gets in your way? Or does it pretty much just work how you want it to?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:24.966000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. Pretty much works how I want it to."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:28.596000Z",
        "message": "Alright. So it just does what you need. Do you ever use any other tools? Like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or any of those AI engines? Instead of Google, either for sports stuff or other questions, or is it just mainly Google for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:41.766000Z",
        "message": "Mainly Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:45.016000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So Google's the main 1. Are there certain types of quest"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:47.896000Z",
        "message": "Yep."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:51.846000Z",
        "message": "have you ever tried those other tools out? Or not really? If you think back, there ever a moment where you considered switching maybe for a different type of question or or because someone mentioned 1 of those?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:06.966000Z",
        "message": "I don't know. I've checked out the chat. Or what's it called? Or the Gemini a couple times."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:14.625000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. So you've tried out Gemini a couple of times. Do you remember what you were looking for? Or what kind of question you asked Gemini? What made you decide to give it a shot instead of just using Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:29.826000Z",
        "message": "Honestly, I don't remember, but I think it tried to direct me there, and I just was like, okay. Whatever."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:36.466000Z",
        "message": "Totally fair. Sometimes things just pop up. Right? When you saw Gemini's answer, did anything about"
      },
      {
