        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:44.185000Z",
        "message": "got it. The site itself nudged you toward Gemini. When you saw the answer it gave, did it feel different from a typical Google search result? About the tone, the detail, or how the answer was presented that stood out to you, or did it all feel about the same?"
      },
