        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:10.246000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So the details seemed a little weird, but not in a bad way. Just kind of different from what you're used to. Thinking about that,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
