        "message": "Different."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:21.125000Z",
        "message": "okay. Just different. Was there anything about that different detail that made you trust Gemini's answer more or less than Google's? Or did you feel about the same level of confidence in it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:35.946000Z",
        "message": "Um, about the same. I'm just kinda standoffish because so new."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:42.906000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for being honest. So you're a bit cautious since Gemini's new, but overall, you trust the answer about the same. If you think about sharing answers with"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:51.076000Z",
        "message": "Yep."
