        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:54.516000Z",
        "message": "if you think about all the different answer engines out there, Google, Gemini, ChatGPT, even Perplexity, do any specific feelings or words come to mind for each of them? Or do they all just kind of blur together for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 39,
