        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:33.256000Z",
        "message": "Love how you put that. Google's your ride or die. Thinking about that, can you picture anything that would make you actually switch your go to? Like, something that would have to happen with Google or something a new engine would have to offer you."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 45,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:52.216000Z",
        "message": "Not right offhand. No. Like,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:58.215000Z",
        "message": "Totally fair. Nothing obvious comes to mind that would make you switch. You just stick with what works. Before I wrap up, is there anything you wish Google"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 47,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:04.945000Z",
        "message": "Yep."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 48,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:08.366000Z",
        "message": "alright. That's super clear. Thanks a ton for sharing your habits and thoughts. Really helpful to hear. Before we wrap up, any thoughts or feelings about having this kind of chat with an AI today? And you're free to end the call whenever you'd like."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 49,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:26.616000Z",
        "message": "It is kinda weird because I know that you're not a real person, but it was a decent experience. It's useful. I don't know. It creeps me out to use it for certain things, but this was useful. And made the survey a little more interesting, I guess."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 50,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:47.486000Z",
        "message": "Really appreciate you saying that. You've been honest and open. And that's exactly what I'm here for. Hope the rest of your day goes great. You're all set to, uh, end the call. Whenever you're ready."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d148ddb304546e0821c5791c",
        "index": 51,
