  {
    "id": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
    "responseId": "dde6e6998454452388c683dc0",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:53.717000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:01.277000Z",
        "message": "Good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:03.917000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. When you're online and need answers to something, whether it's a quick fact, advice, or just figuring something out. What's the very first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:14.517000Z",
        "message": "I go to chat GPT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:19.657000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Chatty PT is your first stop. Thinking about the last time you used ChatGPT, what did you need to find out? Can you walk me through every step of how you went about it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:29.817000Z",
        "message": "Sure. I usually use it several times each day, but today in particular, my mother sent me 1 of these reels, which are on Facebook And the reel tells you about if you put a if a person of crime puts a plastic bottle between a tire, and you hear that noise, you get out and they could rob you. Well, I get skeptical about stuff like that. So I went ahead and used check GPT to inquire if that was true and it's basically a scam."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:10.836000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. The plastic bottle entire story definitely sounds suspicious. Can you tell me more about what you typed into ChatGPT? And what the answer looked like? For example, did it give you sources of summary or anything else that stood out?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:29.177000Z",
        "message": "What I exactly what I told you how I pronounced it to you is exactly how I typed in the chat GPT. And the answer that came out was a couple different paragraphs but the premise was that it was basically an online scam that's been going around for quite some time now."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:53.967000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for painting that picture. Um, when you read that answer, how did it make you feel? Was there anything about, uh, ChatGPT's response? That felt especially helpful or maybe annoying, confusing, or missing?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:07.797000Z",
        "message": "No. Actually, I expected that answer because there's so many scams nowadays. Especially when you see these reels and memes that are on social media. People just making stuff up for attention. So it was something I basically almost knew the answer to, but I just wanted to make sure and and tell my mom so she doesn't worry."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:37.087000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. You wanted a second opinion. To settle your own doubts and help reassure your mom. When you get"
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:41.797000Z",
        "message": "Exactly."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:45.887000Z",
        "message": "that's clear. Thinking about that experience, what made you go straight to ChatGPT instead of, say, searching on Google or another site? Was there something about ChatGPT that made it feel more suitable for this kind of question?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:59.956000Z",
        "message": "I used to use Google. They were my number 1 for any type of research or answers. And it seemed like after a while, Google stopped giving you deep information. And my brother is the 1 who told me about Chad GPT. And I just love it. I mean, any subject, it can dive deep into an answer and give me a lot more than I really even realized."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:34.917000Z",
        "message": "That's a helpful comparison. You mentioned Google. Not giving you deep information anymore. Can you tell me more about what you noticed changing with Google? Any examples or specifics come to mind?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:48.337000Z",
        "message": "I used to be able to just find out, say, like, if there was an obituary, if somebody had passed away or where they're buried or whatever. And the answers would come up right away. And it could be any topic. It seems like I would get so many more results. And now there's just nothing. I don't even use Google anymore. Now that I found ChatGPT, that's all I use."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:21.067000Z",
        "message": "That's vivid. So before, Google often showed direct answers. And lots of results even for topics like obituaries. Now, you're finding nothing comes up for those things. When did you first notice Google wasn't working as well for you? And do you remember a moment when you decided to stop using it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:39.267000Z",
        "message": "I'm trying to think of the time frame. I mean, it's been over a year. And let me make something clear. Every once in a while, I go instead of going into ChatGPT, I will try to go into Google and maybe try to get a phone number, like, say, to a pizza place low locally, that information I can get. I I don't feel I need to use chat GPT for like, our local pizza joint here."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:09.457000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense? Sounds like Google still works for quick local info like phone numbers. But for deeper or less typical topics, you lean on chatty thinking about the answer engines themselves."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:18.497000Z",
        "message": "Correct."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:20.916000Z",
        "message": "Got it. With chat"
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:21.037000Z",
        "message": "Correct."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:23.286000Z",
        "message": "thanks for clarifying. Uh, if you line up ChatGPT and Google, side by side, just thinking about the answers you get, not the websites themselves. Which engine feels more trustworthy or credible? When it comes to"
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:35.077000Z",
        "message": "Of course. Of course, chat chat GPT. Because they not only give just the straight answer, they give you more information about that answer. So you get a lot more result In the past, Google would give me a result, but it wouldn't give me all the information. I would have to put more into the browser and ask more detailed information on Google in order to kinda, like, basically pull it out of them. You know? But chat GPT you just put in a question or an answer and and it what I'm trying to say is you just put in a question, and you get a real good result from it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:28.957000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like with ChatGPT, you get fuller, richer answers. Right away. While with Google, you'd need to keep digging and refining your search to get what you want. When you get a"
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:39.117000Z",
        "message": "Exactly."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:41.807000Z",
        "message": "when you're sharing answers with someone else, like your mom, in the scam example, does it feel any different depending on whether you got the info from ChatGPT or Google? Is there 1 you feel more comfortable quoting or passing along?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:57.177000Z",
        "message": "When she has a question, I mean, she'll use chat GPT, but it's like something she sends to me that she believes is true. And in my gut feeling, I feel it's a scam. I will go to check GPT and just see what they have to say. I will take that information, copy and paste it, into Facebook Messenger, and give her those results."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:23.457000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful. Seems like you trust ChatGPT enough that you'll copy and paste its answers, directly to family when you want to clear something up. When it comes to brand personality, if ChatGPT and Google were people at a party, how would you describe how each 1 acts?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:42.757000Z",
        "message": "Well, let's take Google, first of all. Google would be the nerd sitting in the corner trying to fit in but can't. Chad GPT would be the center of attraction with all the people around them and a good rapport, uh, at the party."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:06.027000Z",
        "message": "Love those descriptions. So Google's off to the side, smart, but out of the conversation. While ChatGPT is the friendly center of attention. If you had to sum up each with 1 word or feeling, what comes to mind for Google? And what for ChatGPT?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:24.797000Z",
        "message": "1 word for Google is unclear. For ChatGPT, satisfied, clear."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:36.947000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for capturing that. You you mentioned that your brother introduced you to ChatGPT. Have you noticed friends or family talking about which engines they use or recommending certain ones for different types of questions? If so, can you recall any specific times or stories?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:29:54.797000Z",
        "message": "Act no. The only 1 that I really talked to, like, on Facebook is, like, my mother my sister, my brother, And with some of them, I I don't really discuss what search engines It's really my mom and myself And I just happened to mention it to my brother, and that's when he says, oh, I don't use Google anymore. I use ChatGPT. And that's how he introduced me, and that's all I use now."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:28.337000Z",
        "message": "That's clear. Sounds like the switch mostly happened within your immediate family. Through word-of-mouth. Wrapping up, is there anything you wish ChatGPT could could do that it doesn't right now? Any features or ways it could get even better for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:30:43.136000Z",
        "message": "I can't really say because I think it wants me to pay some money to do something. I haven't done it But there's so much more. I mean, I just as of recent, was talking about a certain touchy subject, and I asked it to write me a couple paragraphs. And I was quite pleased with that. So I don't know all of its capabilities at this point, what it can do for me without having to pay something, and I don't even know if I'd have to pay. But thus far, it's been perfect."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:20.967000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate your thoughts on that. It sounds like you're still exploring everything ChatGPT can do. And so far, it's suiting your needs even without trying any paid features. Before we wrap, how did this AI interview experience feel for you today? Any feedback for me? And you can"
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:36.787000Z",
        "message": "I loved it. I loved it. It almost sounds like we're, you know, 2 human beings talking to each other. But in essence, you are AI."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:31:51.006000Z",
        "message": "That's awesome to hear. Thanks for saying that. I've really enjoyed hearing your stories and learning from your experiences. If you ever want to chat again while I'm here, you're all set now and can end the call. Whenever you'd like."
      },
      {
        "callId": "36e14c82d8d644c588cb1f3f1",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:32:05.197000Z",
        "message": "Thank you."
      }
