  {
    "id": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
    "responseId": "99403eede68943b3865f831b9",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:19:52.170000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:19:59.890000Z",
        "message": "Pretty good. Thank you."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:02.350000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. To start us off, you need an answer online, say you're curious about something or solving a problem, what's what's the very first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:14.819000Z",
        "message": "Go to my search engine search engine, like Google. Or Chrome."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:21.669000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Sounds like Google is your usual starting point. Can you walk me through what you typically do after you land there?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:24.310000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:28.440000Z",
        "message": "What's your step by step process from the moment you want to look something up?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:32.600000Z",
        "message": "So if, for example, if I wanna look up the size of the sun or the moon, then I just put in what is the size of the moon. And if if it doesn't come up that way, then I try to word it in a different way, moon size or something like that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:56.270000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for breaking that down. So you start with a direct question, and"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:00.110000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:01.080000Z",
        "message": "the answer isn't obvious, experiment with rephrasing. When the results come up, what do you usually look for or click on first?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:11.740000Z",
        "message": "Usually, I could find the answer within the first 3 little paragraphs? And I just yeah. That's it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:23.360000Z",
        "message": "So most of the time, get what you need right up top. Without having to click into a specific website. What's the last thing you looked up this way?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:26.710000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. Right."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:31.180000Z",
        "message": "Can you tell me the whole story from start to finish?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:40.650000Z",
        "message": "The last thing I looked up was yes yesterday. And oh, I know what it was. I looked up how many inmates are in the Snake River Correctional Institution."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:59.490000Z",
        "message": "That's an inter"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:59.670000Z",
        "message": "And and it popped up, like, within the first paragraph. And then it went on to tell me, you know, other things about the prison."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:11.980000Z",
        "message": "When that quick answer appeared, how did it make you feel? Relieved, confident, Maybe something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:20.400000Z",
        "message": "Hey. I got my answer. It didn't take me forever."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:25.810000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Quick and straightforward. Was there anything about that experience that felt less than ideal? Or a bit frustrating?"
