      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:56.280000Z",
        "message": "When you switch to Chrome,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:58.030000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. I'm not really that savvy on the computer. Or on the Internet."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:05.770000Z",
        "message": "Totally understandable. So pretty much, Google is your go to for online answers. And you mostly just adjust your search terms until you find what you need. Have you ever tried any of those newer AI answer engines, like ChatGPT or Perplexity for looking things up?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:25.220000Z",
        "message": "No. Because I'm just kinda learning about those things. Because I noticed taking surveys, when it has, like, a picture and you're supposed to click on all the pictures of the motorcycle. In the little frame that had, like, little squares in it. And when I click on all of them, I noticed that on the bottom, says like, when you're finished, it says c h a g t So I'm kinda learning about what that is. Yeah. So it's all this AI stuff that I'm just kinda catching on to. And if I don't find my answer, in Google or Chrome, I usually call my daughter. She'll help me out."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:18.240000Z",
        "message": "That's really interesting. So you notice bits of AI showing up. Like, in those picture check questions, but"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:23.420000Z",
        "message": "Yes. Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:25.620000Z",
        "message": "you haven't knowingly used things like ChatGPT yet. When your daughter helps out,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:29.880000Z",
        "message": "No. No. She just does it for him."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:32.359000Z",
        "message": "Do you great. She just goes ahead and finds what you need. When she helps you look up answers,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:39.100000Z",
        "message": "Yeah."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:41.970000Z",
        "message": "does she stick with Google like you do, or does she use any different tools or methods?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:49.100000Z",
        "message": "Sometimes she does, but not always."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:53.820000Z",
        "message": "Can you recall a time she used something different? What did she do? And how did that work out?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:01.650000Z",
        "message": "She found my my answer. And if she does something different, I I don't really have asked because I'm just kind of learning about this AI stuff. And she is way techy more than I understand sometimes when she's telling me something."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:21.990000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like she handles the tech side for you, so you just focus on getting the answer. When she explains or talks about these newer AI tools, do any feelings or words come up for you? Curious? Skeptical, confused, interested?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:36.310000Z",
        "message": "Um, interested. Definitely. Confused, definitely. It's like, how do you even find that? And, like, why did you even think about using that? Because those are not typical terms that kinda come up on my iPhone. So I don't know how she gets from my basic stuff, Google, to her more AI advanced stuff. I don't know how she does that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:05.650000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Uh, the jump from your usual Google routine to these newer tools feels a bit mysterious. If you could wave a magic wand and ask for anything that would make online searching easier or clearer for you, what would you wish for?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
