        "message": "Yeah. Yeah."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:33.740000Z",
        "message": "What's what's the first thing you'd wanted to explain?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 45,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:37.770000Z",
        "message": "I think that I would just really kinda wanna know, like, all the terms and what they mean and what they do, like, columns and what they do. And how do I get to it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:53.640000Z",
        "message": "So you'd want clear simple definitions of things, what they're called, what they do, and step by step how to get to them. Does it matter to you"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 47,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:00.710000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 48,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:01.500000Z",
        "message": "How trustworthy? Or accurate the tool is? Or is it more about just being able to get to it and use it easily?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 49,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:09.070000Z",
        "message": "I think it would be trustworthy. I don't I'm not worried about that for some reason. And I think I would just wanna know what they are. And and what they do."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 50,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:23.180000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. You're focused on knowing what's out there and how it works. Trust feels automatic."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 51,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:26.730000Z",
        "message": "Yeah."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 52,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:28.080000Z",
        "message": "Or at least not something you actively question."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 53,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:28.870000Z",
        "message": "Yeah."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 54,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:30.599000Z",
        "message": "As we start wrapping up"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 55,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:31.109000Z",
        "message": "Unless I unless I have a reason to not trust it, then I will continue to trust it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
        "index": 56,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:41.919000Z",
        "message": "That's a good rule of thumb. Trust until given a clear reason not to. Before we finish, how's this this whole AI interview experience felt for you? Anything you want to add about searching online or AI tools?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5d026cb9e89640c0b18dee95d",
