        "index": 58,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:58.109000Z",
        "message": "I can't send things directly. But if I could, I'd make it simple, showing common tools, what they're called, and a few lines about what each 1 does. Maybe your daughter could help create 1 with you or you could find some online by searching AI tool cheat sheet. If you want tips"
