        "index": 62,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:24.650000Z",
        "message": "I really enjoyed our chat. If you have any last thoughts or questions, feel free to share Otherwise, you're welcome to end the call whenever you'd like. Have a great rest of your day."
