  {
    "id": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
    "responseId": "4ff622224e364753a4fb94682",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:43Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:51.430000Z",
        "message": "Good. How's yours?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:54.710000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. Mine's going well. Thanks for asking. Lots of interesting conversations, uh, which I genuinely enjoy. So let's get started. When you're looking for answers online, whether it's something practical, random, or work related, what's the very first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:19:10.280000Z",
        "message": "I search on Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:19:13.280000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Walk me through, uh, your typical process when you search on Google. Starting from the moment you realize you need to look something up? What steps do you take?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:19:23.230000Z",
        "message": "I just I just search exactly what I'm looking for."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:19:28.570000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you type your question or topic right into the search box. When you do that, what do you usually see or do next? Are you clicking into"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:19:36.760000Z",
        "message": "Different web different websites that tell me the answer to my question."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:19:43.970000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Do you tend to look at the first result that pops up, or do you scroll and check a few different websites before settling on 1? Tell me a bit about how you decide, uh, which site to click."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:19:55.010000Z",
        "message": "Scroll and check different websites to see which gives me the best best answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:02.450000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful. Can you think of the last time you looked something up? Maybe today or recently? Can you walk me through what you searched for and how you picked which website to to trust for the answer?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:16.610000Z",
        "message": "Today, I'll search something up."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:20.450000Z",
        "message": "Great. What did you search for today? Could you walk me through the full story from what you needed to what you what you typed in? And how you went about choosing where to look for the answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:33Z",
        "message": "Move. Different things I looked up today."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:41.850000Z",
        "message": "No problem. Is there 1 example from today that stands out? A question or or topic where you really wanted to get a good answer? Could you walk me through that particular search and how you sorted through the results?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:57.360000Z",
        "message": "Different foods that my cats could eat."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:01.329000Z",
        "message": "Perfect. So you were searching about what foods are safe for your cats. Can you walk me through exactly what you typed into Google, what showed up, and how you decided which sites or information to trust."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:14.209000Z",
        "message": "Yes. I just looked up what foods are safe for my cats. And showed me different things that I could feed them. That was safe. And I scrolled until I found a website particularly designed for animals."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:30.070000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Um, what made you, uh, trust the website designed for animals over the others? Was it something about the site name? How the info was presented, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:41.070000Z",
        "message": "How the info was presented."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:44.700000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So something about the way they laid out the information helped to build trust for you. Can you describe what felt trustworthy about their presentation? Was it the clarity, details, tone, or maybe the presence of sources or expert opinions?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:01.080000Z",
        "message": "Clarity. It seemed like they knew what they were talking about."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:06.080000Z",
        "message": "That's really clear. When the info is straightforward, and confident, it's easier to trust. Did you do any double checking or compare that animal sites advice with other results? Or did you feel confident enough to go with what they said?"
