      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:26.720000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So that clear and confident presentation was enough for you to move forward. Curious. You ever used anything other than Google, when in you're looking for these kinds of answers? Like, have you tried ChatGeePety, Perplexity, Gemini, or even Google's own new AI summaries? Or is it pretty much always Google for you?"
