        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:08.990000Z",
        "message": "I'm here for your stories and thoughts, so I'll focus on your answer earlier about using Gemini. Can you tell me more about a time you used Gemini to look something up?"
