        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:23.279000Z",
        "message": "I'll keep us focused on your experiences with Answer Engines. When you use Gemini, can you walk me through what you searched for, how Gemini responded, and how that experience compared to searching on Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
