        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:23:46.710000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. That's helpful. When Gemini gave you those those answers, did anything about the experience feel different? Compared to Google? Like, how the info was presented, how confident you felt, anything else? Or did it all feel pretty much the same to you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:02.350000Z",
        "message": "It all felt pretty much the same."
