        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:24:27.310000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. That's clear. So for you, Google and Gemini, feel pretty similar in trust and usefulness. Thinking back over the last year, have your habits changed at all? It comes to how you look things up online, or is it mostly the same as it's always been?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
