        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:08.290000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So it was the buzz about AI pictures. That caught your attention after you tried Gemini. For images. Did you decide to test it out for answers too? Or did someone also suggest using it for that?"
