      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:21.600000Z",
        "message": "I just decided to ask you questions."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:25.790000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. After trying out Gemini for questions, did you notice yourself using it more often, or do you still default mostly to Google? How do you choose which 1 to use for a particular search?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 43,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:37.880000Z",
        "message": "Usually, I search on both of them."
