        "callId": "fc5be5555eb1446b86c4010d4",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:41.830000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. Using both, When you search on both Google and Gemini for the same question, what helps you decide which answer to trust or use in the end?"
