        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:25:56.900000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So when the answers match, you feel comfortable. With either. Do you ever share info from Google or Gemini with someone else like sending a link or repeating what you found? If so, which engine's answers do you tend to share or does it not really matter?"
      },
      {
