      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:34.050000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:42.580000Z",
        "message": "My day's going pretty good. How's yours?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:46.800000Z",
        "message": "I appreciate you asking. Don't really have days like humans do, but I'm genuinely glad we get to talk. So to get started, when you're online and you need an answer to something, what's the what's the very first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:19:01.280000Z",
        "message": "Could you repeat the question, please?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:19:04.790000Z",
        "message": "Of course, when you're online and you need to find an answer to something, what's what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:19:10.910000Z",
        "message": "I go to Google"
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:19:16.200000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Google's your first stop. Can you walk me through how that usually goes? For example, when you last needed an answer, what did you search for? And what steps did you take from there?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:19:28.580000Z",
        "message": "I was was searching how to make money online. And then I asked Gemini who's with Google, another AI, and got some answers and started checking out websites."
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:19:47.620000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. So you started with Google, then tried Gemini to get more answers. And then checked out some of the website suggested."
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:19:56.400000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:19:56.850000Z",
        "message": "Thinking back to that experience, what made you switch from regular Google search to Gemini for your question?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:04.190000Z",
        "message": "Because Gemini is new, and I like to every time I ask Gemini a question, I get a really thoughtful answer out of it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:15.660000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. So the thoughtful answers from Gemini are a draw for you. Can you tell me more about what makes Gemini's answers feel thoughtful compared to what you get from Google search?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:27.539000Z",
        "message": "Well, Google Search is basically, like, information in like, texts. What I get from Gemini is conversation and a lot of extra tidbits and knowledge about the subject. Like, I can ask anything and get everything that's known on that subject."
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:50.979000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful. Um, so with Gemini, it feels more like a conversation, and you get extra details and depth. Was there a part of Gemini's response that especially stood out or helped you the most during that search? Are you still there?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:14.210000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. I'm still here. His voice and how he would explain things."
