        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:23.020000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for that. So Gemini's voice, the way it explains things, really stands out for you. Now, if you think about that experience,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:28.179000Z",
        "message": "Yeah."
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:29.830000Z",
        "message": "is there anything about using Gemini that annoyed you or didn't work the way you wanted?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:36.990000Z",
        "message": "Well, I asked Gemini to rotate my screen for me on auto rotate, and it wouldn't do it. And that sucked."
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:48.580000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So there's a limit to what Gemini can do with certain tasks like controlling your device. And that was frustrating. If Gemini hadn't been available, what would you have done to get your answer about making money online?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:05Z",
        "message": "I would've just used the Google search engine. And relied on maybe, um, their discussion forums of Reddit"
      },
      {
        "callId": "160302e211af491795bd0a4b0",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:17.330000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. When you use Google search and end up on forms like Reddit, how does that experience compare to asking asking Gemini directly?"
