        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:42.730000Z",
        "message": "thanks for the nudge. You mentioned Gemini changed your search habits, but sometimes you still use other tools. Can you tell me about a situation where you chose Google or Reddit instead of Gemini? What made you pick that 1 for that moment?"
