        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:26:56.780000Z",
        "message": "Like, I was looking up casinos for Arizona, and I needed to get a specific website not just a casino name. And Gemini wouldn't wouldn't do it for me. So I used Google. To look it up. The website ended up not working."
