        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:27:19.780000Z",
        "message": "That's a great that's a useful story. Um, so when you needed a specific website, Gemini couldn't provide it. So you switched over to Google, Even then, the website didn't work like you hoped. Looking at that, is there anything you wish these answer engines could do better when you need something really specific like that?"
