        "index": 62,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:04.050000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. Uh, you'd like more flexibility. Even if it means Answer Engines could take extra actions. Like controlling some settings or handling personal details. If Gemini or 1 of these other engines added those kinds of features, do you think it would become your go to all the time, or would anything still make you switch?"
