        "index": 64,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:28:30.740000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Super clear. I really appreciate your stories and honest answers today. Before we wrap up, I'm curious, how did it feel having this chat with me as an AI interviewer? Anything stand out to you about the experience?"
