        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:16:41.550000Z",
        "message": "That sounds like a powerful memory to hold on to. If you're comfortable sharing, like, uh, was there a moment where you, um, sort online for anything related to that, maybe trying to get answers or make sense of what happened. If so, what tool or site did you choose first to look things up?"
