        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:17:49.760000Z",
        "message": "I usually go with it because it I think, usually brings me to correct choices."
      },
      {
        "callId": "43780cc5e93049c690a458a17",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:03.879000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. So when you use Google's AI summaries and it points you in the right direction, what about that experience works best for you? Is it the speed, the way the info is presented, or or maybe something else that feels most helpful?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "43780cc5e93049c690a458a17",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:19.240000Z",
        "message": "I think because it narrows down the choices, of what I can look for, and gives me a direction to head in."
