        "callId": "43780cc5e93049c690a458a17",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:32.190000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful to know. So when Google's AI narrows things down, and gives you a direction, do you usually do next? Do you click 1"
