        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:55.520000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for thanks for spelling that out. When you pick 1 of those suggested links, do you usually feel confident in the answer you find there? Or do you sometimes double check by looking elsewhere, maybe using a different engine or source?"
      },
