        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:01.710000Z",
        "message": "Good to know. When you need more info after Google's AI summary, do you stick with Google, just digging deeper, or do you ever jump to a different tool like ChatCPT, Perplexity, or something else? Your usual move in those moments?"
