        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:22.060000Z",
        "message": "That sounds familiar for a lot of people. If you think back, got it. Thanks for clarifying. So just to check, have you ever tried other tools like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Gemini for finding answers online, or is it pretty much always Google for you?"
      },
