        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:42.500000Z",
        "message": "With my phone, it's Google. I did just buy an HP desktop. Which is Microsoft, so I know I'm gonna start using it some of the time. And that will be a different search engine."
