        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:21:01.060000Z",
        "message": "That's an interesting shift. So now that you've got your HP Desktop and Microsoft Search Engine, how do you feel about the idea of using something other than Google? Is there anything you're curious or maybe even a little hesitant about when thinking of trying out a new answer engine?"
