        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:22.930000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Sounds like you're hoping the newer setup and Windows 11 will maybe surface more or better answers or just open up more options for you. When you think about more answers, is that about getting different perspectives on the same question? Or more detailed explanations. Or something else."
