        "time": "2025-09-14T00:22:48.680000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for clarifying. So having different perspectives really matters to you, uh, when you're looking when you're looking for answers online. Thinking about that, you sure you had do you recall any times with with Google where you wished you had seen more viewpoints or maybe even doubted you were getting the full story? What did you notice or feel in those"
