        "message": "Equally confident."
      },
      {
        "callId": "2430eb66d40c4ca5b5a527075",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:01.540000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for explaining. Looking back over the last year, has anything changed about how often you use Google or Gemini? When you look things up, or is it pretty much the same routine as before?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "2430eb66d40c4ca5b5a527075",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:12.921000Z",
        "message": "Same routine as before."
      },
      {
        "callId": "2430eb66d40c4ca5b5a527075",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:16.591000Z",
        "message": "That's clear. Last quick question. Do you ever hear friends or classmates talking about which answer engine they use maybe recommending Google, Gemini, or even something like ChatGPT for certain things. If so, what do they say?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "2430eb66d40c4ca5b5a527075",
