        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:33.801000Z",
        "message": "Good to know. Um, when your friends mentioned using ChatGPT, is there a reason they give like, what makes it their pick, or do they just use it without much discussion?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "2430eb66d40c4ca5b5a527075",
