        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:52.624000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate that. Sounds like it was smooth. Especially with the tip from your friend. If you hadn't used Google let's say your phone suggested an AI answer or you saw something from ChatGPT or Perplexity, would you have done anything differently?"
