        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:21.473000Z",
        "message": "Well, I don't know what I was looking up, but a lot of times, I'll look like let's say the distance between towns. If I have to travel somewhere to do something. Or that's just something I thought of because I just did that. But she uses she's using the AIs a lot. She hands it right over."
