        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:20.383000Z",
        "message": "And a lot of times, she'll say, can you ask Would you like to ask? And it'll be the chat. Whatever the AI is on there. And then you just say yes, and then she sends it over."
