        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:19:52.203000Z",
        "message": "if you imagine Siri as a person at a You trust Siri more for clear answers? If you imagine Siri, Google, and and that chat engine, as as people at a party, how would you describe each one's personality?"
