        "time": "2025-09-14T00:17:06.946000Z",
        "message": "I've actually never discussed that with anybody, so I think it's just sort of a given."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fed3a0de06f04bd399ceb50b1",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:17:13.236000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate you sharing all that. Um, that's all I needed for today. Since this, uh, chat was with an AI, curious. How did you find the the experience? And you're welcome to end the call whenever you'd like."
