    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:10:25.172000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:10:32.272000Z",
        "message": "Okay. It's good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:10:38.432000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. Let's ease in. When you need to look something up online, hey. Thanks for sticking with me. When you need answers online, say you're curious about something"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:10:47.402000Z",
        "message": "Chilling rice."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:10:49.682000Z",
        "message": "got it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:10:49.712000Z",
        "message": "We even work more."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:10:52.701000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. Can you walk me through what you did when you wanted info about Chilling Rice? What was your first step?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:03.082000Z",
        "message": "I looked it up. And ingredients. I looked up ingredients."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:09.822000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing. When you say you looked it up, which website or tool did you use first?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:17.642000Z",
        "message": "Oh, Google, Google AI,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:26.022000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Google and Google AI. What made you choose Google for that search?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:32.762000Z",
        "message": "It's my main search engine."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:36.482000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. About how often would you say you use Google? When you're looking for for answers like that?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:45.472000Z",
        "message": "All the time."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:47.942000Z",
        "message": "That's clear. Thinking about your last search for chilling rice. Can you walk me through what happened from start to finish? What did you type? What did you see? And what did you do next?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:00.612000Z",
        "message": "I didn't type anything. I searched chili rice ingredients. And it pulled up different ingredients about chili and rice."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:09.352000Z",
        "message": "Super helpful. Thanks. When Google showed those ingredients, what did you find most helpful about how it presented the info? Or was there anything frustrating about that experience?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:20.042000Z",
        "message": "No. They gave me a variety of chili and rice ingredients and how to make it. Just different recipes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:26.952000Z",
        "message": "Sounds pretty smooth. Nice. So it sounds like you got what you needed without any hassle. When you see those answers from Google AI, sometimes right at the top, do you usually trust what it shows? Or do you ever double check elsewhere?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:44.582000Z",
        "message": "Most time, stress what it shows because searches where it gives typically the same answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:53.211000Z",
        "message": "Gotcha. So seeing the same info across searches, makes you trust it more. Thinking about other tools, like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Gemini, Have you ever used any of those for getting answers? Do you mainly stick with Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:08.662000Z",
        "message": "I use Gemini on occasions."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:14.122000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. Can you tell me about a time you you used Gemini instead of Google? What were you looking up, and what made you switch?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:25.412000Z",
        "message": "Gemini's more accurate on finding things and putting things together that you have no information about. So I can maybe maybe can take a picture on Gemini, and ask to find this, and it will find whatever it is."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:43.152000Z",
        "message": "That's really interesting. So Gemini helps when you have less info to start well with or need to use pictures. Do you remember a specific time you did that you did that with Gemini? What was the task, and how did it go from start to finish?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:58.692000Z",
        "message": "Yes. I was looking at the specs for a phone, but I didn't know what type of phone it was. So I took a picture of the phone and has Gemini. To find information about it and all that. Found everything. Phone,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:12.772000Z",
        "message": "Great example."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:13.802000Z",
        "message": "specs,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:18.121000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for clarifying. So Gemini figured out phone and gave you all the specs. When you got that info, how did it make you feel? Compared to using Google? Anything stand out emotionally or in how confident you felt?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:33.961000Z",
        "message": "No. It made me feel good that I can take a picture of something and get an instead of having search and search for."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:43.032000Z",
        "message": "That sounds satisfying. Just snap a photo. And get everything you need. Were there any parts of using Gemini that felt annoying? Slower compared to Google? Or was it about the same for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:55.222000Z",
        "message": "It was about the same."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:58.552000Z",
        "message": "Helpful to know. If you think about Google, Google AI, and Gemini, how would you describe the main difference between the info you get? Each 1? Stands out about the answers or the way they show them?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:15:12.902000Z",
        "message": "Well, Google's, it pulls up words and definition of information about something, Gemini mostly pulls up pictures and the information about it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:15:28.162000Z",
        "message": "That's a clear distinction. When you tell someone else an answer, uh, you found online, which engine's result feels most credible, to quote or share? Why is that?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:15:44.421000Z",
        "message": "I really can't say."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:15:49.331000Z",
        "message": "Fair enough. Everyone's different with that. Thinking about both tools, if each 1 were a person at a party, who do you picture Google as? And who's Gemini? How do each of them act?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:16:03.672000Z",
        "message": "Google would be the normal girl. Gemini would be the super girl."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:16:13.742000Z",
        "message": "Nice comparison. What makes Gemini feel like the super girl? At the party? Any traits or behaviors that stand out?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:16:22.122000Z",
        "message": "Because she's it would be more informed on what's going on. I have to tell Google everything. That I want."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:16:32.452000Z",
        "message": "That's vivid. So Gemini is more in the know. You don't need to explain as much. While Google needs more guidance. Looking back over the past year, has anything shifted in how you look up"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:16:39.602000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:16:41.981000Z",
        "message": "information online? Any moments where you found yourself reaching for Gemini? First instead of Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 43,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:16:50.372000Z",
        "message": "It depends on what I'm searching."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:16:54.402000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for clarifying. Uh, can you remember a moment when you you chose Gemini first? What made you do that instead of going straight to Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 45,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:17:04.132000Z",
        "message": "Times I use Gemini first is when I have less information about a a thing. Or something."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:17:15.872000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. When friends or coworkers talk about Answer Engines, do they ever mention certain tools or recommend 1 over another? If so, which ones? And for what kinds of questions?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 47,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:17:27.312000Z",
        "message": "No. It typically use Google, the regular search engine."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 48,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:17:33.152000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Google's still the standard among people you know. Before we wrap up, is there anything you wish these tools could do that they don't maybe a feature or type of help that would make searching even easier for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 49,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:17:47.312000Z",
        "message": "No. They pretty much got it under wraps. Right now. Find the way it is."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 50,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:17:55.862000Z",
        "message": "Thanks so much for sharing your stories and insights today. Before we finish, how did it feel talking with an AI interviewer about your search habits? You can end the call whenever you're ready."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 51,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:11.082000Z",
        "message": "It was okay. Wasn't as bad. The AI listens and just just understanding."
      },
      {
        "callId": "04ae309f0e2f4281b3112040f",
        "index": 52,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:15.752000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear"
      }
