  {
    "id": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
    "responseId": "f539f61ddc084f62884d17e09",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:10:59.284000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:07.624000Z",
        "message": "My day going good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:11.744000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. Let's start with your usual habits online. When you need an answer to something, big or small, what's the very first thing you typically do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:27.724000Z",
        "message": "I answer the big ones first."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:32.354000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like you prioritize your most important questions. Thinking about the last time you needed an answer to something important, Can you walk me through what you did? Step by step?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:45.634000Z",
        "message": "I went on my phone, and searched on Google. And asked a question."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:54.844000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you grabbed your phone and went straight to Google. What made you choose Google for that question?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:02.614000Z",
        "message": "It was quick and easy."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:06.044000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Speed and simplicity sound important to you. When you searched on on Google, what did you do next? Did you look at the top result, scroll for others, click into a site, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:22.754000Z",
        "message": "I verified with another site."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:27.234000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. You double checked. Your answer. What was it about the first result? That made you want to verify with another site?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:36.274000Z",
        "message": "Nothing. I just wanted to make sure I was getting the correct answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:42.834000Z",
        "message": "That's pretty thoughtful, making sure the information is accurate. When you looked at another site, did you feel more confident in your answer? Or do you sometimes keep checking until you're really sure?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:55.534000Z",
        "message": "No. The answers were the same, so I felt confident."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:01.964000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Consistency between sources helped confirm things for you. Thinking about, I don't know, other tools out there, like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Gemini. Have you ever tried any of those to get quick answers, or do you do you mostly stick with Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:19.454000Z",
        "message": "I have used the others before."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:24.954000Z",
        "message": "Nice. You've tried a range of them. Uh, tell me about a recent time you used something like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Gemini. What kind of question did you ask? And what made you pick that tool? Instead of Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:39.054000Z",
        "message": "I use AL chat to ask a question about an account."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:49.383000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. So when you used AI chat for your account question, what was the experience like? Did it feel different from using Google? Can you walk me through what stood out good or bad?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:05.644000Z",
        "message": "I felt like they didn't really understand my question. And they didn't give me the answer I was looking for."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:19.124000Z",
        "message": "That sounds a bit frustrating. When that happened, did you try rephrasing your question, or did you switch to another tool or method to find your answer?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:29.484000Z",
        "message": "No. I rephrased it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:32.984000Z",
        "message": "You gave it another shot by rephrasing makes sense. When you did that, did the AI chat get closer to your answer, or was it still off? What did you end up doing next?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:41.514000Z",
        "message": "And it's Actually, no. It did not."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:47.143000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So even after trying to rephrase, the answer still didn't hit the mark. At that point, did you feel like giving up, or did you go back to Google or somewhere else to look for your answer?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:15:01.814000Z",
        "message": "Actually, I made a phone call and spoke with someone personally on the phone."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:15:11.314000Z",
        "message": "That's a pretty big pivot. You went from AI chat to talking with a real person. How did you feel about making that switch? Did it feel like more effort or more reliable or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:15:23.364000Z",
        "message": "I got better answer. I got my answer answered My question answered."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:15:36.834000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like talking to a person felt more direct and helpful. For that situation. Uh, If you compare that experience to using Google or AI chat, what did the phone call offer that the others didn't stand out to you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:15:53.183000Z",
        "message": "Yes. If I had to rephrase what I was saying, they understood And I got more information."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:16:07.414000Z",
        "message": "That's really clear. So having a person who could understand if you had to rephrase, plus getting more info made a big difference. Thinking about your habits now, do you ever start with AI tools instead of Google? Or is Google usually your first stop? Has anything about your go to choice changed in the past year or so?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:16:28.484000Z",
        "message": "I usually use Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:16:33.034000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for clarifying. Sticking with Google sounds like your main habit. When you think about all these answer engines, Google, ChatGPT, Perplexity, Gemini, are there any words, feelings, or impressions that come to mind for each? For example, how would you describe Google compared to ChatGPT?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:16:54.194000Z",
        "message": "I feel when I ask a question, Google will rephrase it for me. And give me a good answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:17:07.304000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. So Google kind of translates your question and gets you to a solid answer. Thinking about ChatGPT or the other AI chats, how do they feel different to you? Any specific words or impressions?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:17:22.104000Z",
        "message": "They're okay, but I don't I'm not too interested in them."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:17:30.044000Z",
        "message": "Got it. You're not that drawn to them. When it comes to sharing answers with someone else, like sending a link or telling a friend, do you feel more comfortable quoting Google's answer? Or would you ever share something from an AI chat? What's your thinking behind that?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:17:46.674000Z",
        "message": "I would prefer Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:17:50.044000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing your style. Wrapping up here, if you look back over the past year, would you say your habits for looking things up or getting answers have changed at all? Or has it stayed pretty much the same?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:04.914000Z",
        "message": "Pretty much stayed the same."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:08.714000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Thanks for walking me through your experiences and for all the honest answers. Before we finish up, just out of curiosity, how did you find chatting with an AI about these habits? Anything stand out? And you're welcome to to end the call. Whenever you'd like."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:25.254000Z",
        "message": "Oh, can you repeat that, please?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:28.493000Z",
        "message": "Absolutely. I was just asking, how did you find talking with an AI about your online Answer Habits today? Did anything stand out to you? About the conversation? And you're totally free to end the call whenever you'd like."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7393bbad81a3472f810767516",
        "index": 43,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:44.343000Z",
        "message": "No. Nothing's good out."
      }
