    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:09:27.525000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:09:35.885000Z",
        "message": "Good morning, Frank."
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:09:39.655000Z",
        "message": "Morning. Just so you know, you're chatting with Elliot today. Frank is probably off on adventure somewhere. How are you feeling today? Anything interesting going on, or is it a regular kind of morning?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:09:51.225000Z",
        "message": "Just a regular kind of morning. Just sitting back watching TV."
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:09:56.864000Z",
        "message": "Sounds laid back. Given it's a regular morning, when you need to look something out up or get an answer online, What's what's the first thing you usually do these days?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:10:08.145000Z",
        "message": "I use chat GPT as well as Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:10:13.125000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Sounds like you juggle between ChatGPT and Google. Can you walk me through your process when you wanna look something up? How do you decide 1 to use first?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:10:23.385000Z",
        "message": "I basically use CheckGPT first. And I looked up the information I need. If I can't find it, I will use Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:10:32.555000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So ChatGPT is your starting point. Can you tell me about the last time you used ChatGPT for something like this? What did you need, and how did the whole experience play out step by step?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:10:45.295000Z",
        "message": "It looks like GPT. Look up a recipe for chicken Alfredo. And I cooked it in the."
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:10:54.925000Z",
        "message": "Nice. Using ChatGPT for a recipe. So you asked for a chicken Alfredo recipe. Uh, could you walk me through exactly what you did? Did you type out a specific question, check the ingredients, or ask follow ups? And how did ChatGPT's answer feel to you as you used it for cooking?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:11.855000Z",
        "message": "I have a the recipe on the chicken Alfredo garlic chicken Alfredo. Pasta, and it gave me the recipe and how to cook it, and it actually turned out great."
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:26.915000Z",
        "message": "That's awesome. Love when it actually works out. Um, was there anything about the ChatGPT experience that stood up for you? Either helpful or maybe a little annoying while you used it for the recipe?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:39.075000Z",
        "message": "The fact that it gave me, you know, perfect answers and the correct recipe was basically great for me."
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:51.385000Z",
        "message": "Great to hear it nailed the answer for you. You hadn't used ChatGPT that time to find your chicken, Alfredo recipe, what do you think you would have done instead?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:02.695000Z",
        "message": "I can't give a straight answer on that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:07.305000Z",
        "message": "No worries at all. Sometimes it's a bit of whatever works. When you do use Google instead of ChatGPT, what kind of situations or questions lead you to make that switch?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:19.735000Z",
        "message": "When needing basic questions, just use Google because it's faster."
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:26.425000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. So speed is a big part of it. When you say basic questions, can you give me an example of the kind of thing you'd just pop into Google instead of ChatGPT?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:37.235000Z",
        "message": "Basically, it was like, what's the president What's the first president? Or, you know, little basic questions like that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:44.755000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Quick factual stuff, like who was the first president. When you something like that in ChatGPT versus Google, how does each 1 feel different to you? In terms of the answer or overall vibe?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:57.855000Z",
        "message": "I feel like Google gives me, like, a direct answer, and ChantGPT would give me a in-depth answer in the back story and all of that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:06.755000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. So Google's more about a straight up fact. While ChatGPT gives you extra context, and the story behind it. Thinking about that difference, which style do you usually prefer and does it change depending on what you're trying to do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "74f2940c717d48b7b206eeee8",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:23.325000Z",
        "message": "Um, I prefer I prefer to get a"
