    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:21.524000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:30.884000Z",
        "message": "Going wide."
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:33.764000Z",
        "message": "Got it. You're in going wide mode today. Is there something on your mind? Or are you just multitasking? We chat?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:43.264000Z",
        "message": "I'm just thinking."
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:46.783000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like you're in a reflective spot. When you're thinking or curious about something. And need quick answers online. What's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:58.453000Z",
        "message": "Menus. A search engine,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:04.624000Z",
        "message": "That is interesting. So when you're searching for menus, can you walk me through your typical process? For finding them online? Uh, what's your first step?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:15.014000Z",
        "message": "It needs my computer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:19.014000Z",
        "message": "Okay. So you reach for your computer first. Once you're at your computer, which tool or site do you end up using most often? To find the menu you're looking for? Are you still there?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:38.784000Z",
        "message": "I use glucocortone."
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:43.494000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. You mentioned glucocortone. I'm not familiar with that as a search engine or answer tool. Could you tell me a bit more about what it is and how you use it for finding menus?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:56.564000Z",
        "message": "It's a engine that allows the toller imaging thing."
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:02.054000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So glucocortone helps with imaging, almost like a tool for searching visual content. Could you tell me the story of the last time you used glucocortone? What were you trying to find and what steps did you take? From beginning to end?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:21.004000Z",
        "message": "Was searching for a new location."
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:25.514000Z",
        "message": "So you were searching for a new location. Maybe a restaurant or or store. When you use glucocortone for this, what did you type or do first? And what happened next?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:37.794000Z",
        "message": "I was typing for different places. For food."
