        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:45.864000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you typed in the names of different places for food. When the results came up, um, what did you notice? Was there anything especially helpful or frustrating how glucocortone showed you the menus or locations?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:59.644000Z",
        "message": "I saw a different review."
