        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:38.954000Z",
        "message": "So the the positive review helped you decide go there for your work lunch. In that experience, was there anything about using glucocortone that felt especially helpful or maybe annoying? Anything that stood out?"
