        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:15:00.743000Z",
        "message": "When you say the design is still there, you referring to the layout of glucocortone? Did the way everything looked and was organized make a difference in how easy or hard it was for you to get what you needed? Tell me a bit more about that."
