        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:15:20.463000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like the design made things easier for you as you went along. Can you share what part of that experience felt the most helpful? Or maybe, you know, maybe saved you the most time as you were searching for places for lunch?"
