        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:15:39.904000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for explaining. So speed is a big deal. For you. Glucocortone made it faster to decide on a place for lunch. You hadn't used glucocortone, what do you think you would have done instead to find that info?"
