        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:16:03.174000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Sometimes you just pick whatever's handy. Uh, thinking of other tools, have you ever tried something like ChatGPT, Perplexity, Google AI summaries, or Gemini for these kinds of searches? If so, how does using glucocortone compare for this type of task?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
