        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:16:28.604000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like glucocortone stands out. It's different from everything else. You've tried, but maybe not completely separate. What feels unique about it compared to those other tools? Anything about the experience or or results that that really sets it apart for you."
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
