        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:17:10.173000Z",
        "message": "So the way glucocortone supports you, uh, by helping to answer your question really works for you. When you think about all these engines, does glucocortone feel more reliable or trustworthy? Or do you think of it differently in any other way?"
