        "message": "I did not think of it differently."
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:17:32.504000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you see glucocortone much of the same as other tools, terms of trust and reliability. Thinking back, you remember a time when you used a different engine for something similar, maybe Google ChatGPT or another, what made you switch in that moment?"
      },
      {
