        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:07.184000Z",
        "message": "I used Google because it was stronger."
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:16.564000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing. You used Google because it felt stronger. In that moment, what did stronger mean to you? Was it about the speed? The quality of info, the trust, or something else? Tell me more."
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 43,
        "role": "user",
