        "message": "Nothing has changed."
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 54,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:26.304000Z",
        "message": "That's clear. Sounds like your habits haven't really shifted. Last couple of questions. Do friends or coworkers ever recommend any search or answer engines to you or talk about them? If so, which ones come up, and what do people say?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 55,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:43.244000Z",
        "message": "Recommend because it is versatile."
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 56,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:20:51.614000Z",
        "message": "So people recommend certain engines, like Google. Because they see it as versatile. When you hear that, does it make you more likely to stick with Google, or do you ever feel tempted to try something new?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "4c293f44d4774b8d817a7cedf",
        "index": 57,
        "role": "user",
