        "message": "Got it. So with Google, you just got a bare list lots of movies, but no explanation for why they might be like hostile. But with GPT, the answer included reasons or even descriptions that made it clear how they were similar. Thinking back to that experience, what part of using GPT felt especially helpful? Any part that was annoying or or didn't work for you?"
