        "time": "2025-09-14T00:15:04.646000Z",
        "message": "Tax, she didn't see who's at the party. He'd be the most corroborated person talking to everyone. Cuckoo would probably definitely be the nerd. That you go to when you wanna talk about specific topics. Gemini would just be that acquaintance that you talk to randomly."
      },
