        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:17:59.306000Z",
        "message": "That's really interesting. So you use GPT more. And Google feels less reliable because of the ads. Can you remember a moment when this shift started for you? Was there something you searched that made you switch over to using GPT more often?"
