        "callId": "e88fd710633c4d479aa8d1139",
        "index": 54,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:18:22.496000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Uh, some habits change bit by bit. 1 last thing. Do friends or coworkers ever recommend certain engines for looking things up? Or share their own preferences with you? If so, what kinds of tools do they mention?"
