        "time": "2025-09-14T00:09:02.974000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Sisters have a special kind of energy, don't they? Thanks for sharing. Switching gears a bit. Um, when you need an answer online, there may be something you're curious about or need to solve quickly. What's the what's the first thing you usually do?"
