        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:09:53.215000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like Harmony's on the move. You've got your hands full right now, we can pause or pick up later. No worries. Either way. But just in case, you've got a moment, when you do get to look something up online, what's your go to way of finding an answer?"
