        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:08.925000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for clarifying. So when it's a quick straightforward search, Google's your go to. Can you tell me a bit more about that last time? What exactly were you looking for? And how did you go about getting your answer on Google? Feel free to ask me any questions."
