        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:16.415000Z",
        "message": "I found the video. It popped up as Google AI and was from the quick search when I first looked up what I was looking up. And then I watched the video. And it showed me the steps."
      },
      {
        "callId": "98cfee3f3e6949e2a599fd062",
