        "callId": "98cfee3f3e6949e2a599fd062",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:02.405000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. Sometimes it misses the mark, but this time, it hit just right. For what what you needed. When Google doesn't get it right, what do you usually do next?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "98cfee3f3e6949e2a599fd062",
