      {
        "callId": "98cfee3f3e6949e2a599fd062",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:16.295000Z",
        "message": "Just clarifying, you switch over to ChatGPT when Google doesn't give you what you need. If so, could you tell me about a time that that happened? What was the question, and how did ChatGPT handle it compared to Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "98cfee3f3e6949e2a599fd062",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:33.815000Z",
        "message": "It was a problem, and I needed it to be explained better than Google could, which ChatGPT was able to screen it in step."
      },
      {
        "callId": "98cfee3f3e6949e2a599fd062",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:43.214000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. So when Google didn't break things down clearly, ChatGPT helped by explaining step by step. You use ChatGPT, what about its style or or answers feels different from Google's?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "98cfee3f3e6949e2a599fd062",
