        "callId": "98cfee3f3e6949e2a599fd062",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:02.805000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful to know. Sounds like ChatGPT makes things more understandable for you. Uh, was there anything else about using ChatGPT? Maybe the way it responds, the tone, or how it lets you ask follow-up questions. That stands out compared to Google."
