        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:19.305000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. I like how it's all questions, or would you like to add this with it? Like to be removed It give me more options, availability when I am looking something up."
      },
      {
        "callId": "98cfee3f3e6949e2a599fd062",
