        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:31.535000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. It feels more interactive, giving you options. And letting you add or remove things. While you search. How does that make you feel when you're using ChatGPT versus just getting a straight answer from Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "98cfee3f3e6949e2a599fd062",
