        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:15:54.114000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So you feel like ChatGPT is the more intelligent AI? There anything about its style or results that makes it feel that way? Maybe the way it talks. Or the details it gives or is it just the overall impression you get?"
