        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:16:15.135000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate that. The way it talks, the details, and how it describes problems really stand out for you. Thinking back over the past year, has the way you look things up changed at all? Maybe a bit more ChatGPT, or do you still lean on Google mostly? What's different now versus before?"
