        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:17:02.035000Z",
        "message": "That's a cool story. So you saw an ad showing someone using ChatGPT to solve a problem step by step, and it made you want to try it yourself. After you first tried it, what kept you coming back? Was it the clarity, the options, anything else?"
