        "index": 52,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:17:20.275000Z",
        "message": "So it's it's the clarity and having options that keep you coming back to ChatGPT. If you could change or add anything about how these answer engines work. Google, ChatGPT, any of them, what's something you wish they could do for you that they don't yet"
