      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:08:51.927000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for walking me through that. Can you tell me more about what you do on Google? What's your typical process step by step from when you have a question to finding your answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:09:05.767000Z",
        "message": "I asked you a specific question. Like, how do you do this, or where do you find this? And see what's the best answers."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:09:14.987000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you type your question. Directly into, uh, Google and scan through the answers. When you say you look for the best answers, what makes an answer stand out for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:09:25.337000Z",
        "message": "The 1 that resonates with me the most"
