        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:09:31.197000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. Can you tell me a bit more about what resonates means to you in this context? Is it the way the answer is written? Details offered, who's providing it, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:09:43.686000Z",
        "message": "The details that's offered in more in-depth with the information so I can better understand what the answer is saying and what better fits my question."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:09:59.237000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for explaining that. Thinking back, can you tell me, uh, the story of the last time you used Google for an answer? What did you need, and how did the whole process unfold for you? Step by step?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:10:11.217000Z",
        "message": "Well, x it what's the best stores to go shopping for food What's the closest Costco and mass store? Like Costco and BJ's, as to my location. It gave a rundown the best locations, the the ratings, the stars, and the distance."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:10:32.067000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that example. When you got those results, what part of the experience felt most helpful? To you? And was there anything about it that you found annoying or frustrating?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:10:45.577000Z",
        "message": "No. There was nothing annoying in what stood out was it's filtered the most relevant, best rated and the 1 that's the most closest to me for stores I was looking for."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:00.656000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like that worked out really smoothly for you. I'm curious, you hadn't used Google in that moment, what would you have done instead? To find those stores?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:11.037000Z",
        "message": "I would've went to chat with GPT. And ask you the same questions."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:18.637000Z",
        "message": "Interesting switch. Can you walk me through the story of how you'd yeah, use ChatGPT for that task? What's different about the process or the results compared to Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:28.427000Z",
        "message": "I mean, it's the same conduct because now Google has their Google AI. So it kinda was almost the same. So I basically would compare and contrast between the 2 platforms to see which 1 is more relevant, especially when it comes to stores. And then I also go and Google Maps and do the rest myself."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:50.857000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for breaking that down. When you're comparing the info between the engines, say Google AI versus ChatGPT, what feels different about the answers each 1 gives you? Are there any strengths or weaknesses that you notice between them?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:07.677000Z",
        "message": "Not really. It's more so how it's presented. If it filters it from best to the least then that's what I can say will make a difference. I know Google and JetGP Jet GPT both try to be as organized as possible when they give an answer to, like, step 1 or they'll say, store 1, store 2, store 3, depending on your location. This 1 is, of to you. So there isn't anything really too much of a difference, but to answer your questions, if I didn't go to Google, I said I'll do chat GBT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:47.957000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Thinking about all the engines you've used, Google, ChatGPT, maybe even Perplexity or Gemini, if you had to line them up from most to least helpful for your needs, what would the order be? And what what makes you rank them that way?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:02.697000Z",
        "message": "Prior to ChatGPT, Google, Perplexity, and, what's up, Copilot. I've ranked them between because I go from which ones I use the most. Honestly. Other ones, I use them, but not as much because I'm not I'm not getting a paid prescription for every single 1 of them, and I know a lot of them When you don't have the paid prescription, it's limited on what you can do with it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:31.117000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful context. Can you tell me more about what makes you use 1 more than another? It mostly about what you're able to do on the free version? Or are there other factors at play for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:42.587000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. I like to use the ones to see that gives you the most from the free version, and then that will let me know, dang. If I can do this much on the free version, sky's the limit if I get the paid version and and that's what saying. It'll give me even more tools to be able to use. Like ChatGPT. For instance, you had to pay you had to free version, but if you get the paid version, do you have access to all the other tools that they have within the paid prescription."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:14.497000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate that. You mentioned tools a couple times. What kinds of extra tools or features would actually make you consider subscribing to the paid version of any answer engine? What's on your wish list?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
