        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:26.357000Z",
        "message": "Anything?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:29.477000Z",
        "message": "tool 1 of the tools to create videos and images. It basically will give you a better better if you ask for some type of picture or videos to be done, you know, use the tool. I forgot the exact name of the tool, but it'll use that to create it and give you a better better, more clarified image more professional looking video. Yeah. It's pretty other ones in there, but I like to make content. So that helps me the most."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:15:07.527000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for laying that out. So the creative tools, like generating videos or high quality images are big draws for you, especially since you make content. When you think of brands like Google, ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Copilot, what kind of personality or feeling comes up for each If they were people at a party, how would they act?"
      },
