        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:16:20.877000Z",
        "message": "Not really. Is is they all are pretty good tools and pretty powerful. So I wouldn't say, oh, don't get it from don't listen to this information because it's from this this AI or this platform because they all pretty good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:16:39.657000Z",
        "message": "Helpful. Sounds like you see them as equals in credibility. Thinking about your habits, looking back a year ago, has anything changed in how often or which engines you use first when searching for answers? Can you remember any moments when your default shifted?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fc4076e3f5eb40f79f4a86a02",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:16:55.897000Z",
        "message": "No. Just whatever 1 like, if I'm on my phone, whatever 1 that's just pops up on my if I'm on Google already, then I'll try to use the Google AI. And or if I'm just on my phone, you know, messing around, I got the chat GBT app sitting right there on my home So it all depends, like, what's there at the moment. It's just it's no, oh, I'm using this 1 because I don't like this 1. It's just where everyone is there at the time when I need it the most."
