        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:06.760000Z",
        "message": "Helpful. So the depth and amount of info are about the same. Is there anything that makes you trust 1 over the other when you're deciding which advice to follow for a project?"
