        "message": "I think that series is more in-depth I have noticed that YouTube would have good examples mixed with bad examples."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d53766c2a7174fc1b0119ec6c",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:49.580000Z",
        "message": "That's insightful. When you get an answer from Siri's, do you ever share it with other people? Like friends or family? So, does Seres feel credible enough that you're comfortable passing its advice along?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d53766c2a7174fc1b0119ec6c",
