        "callId": "d53766c2a7174fc1b0119ec6c",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:34.730000Z",
        "message": "I would think they'd be knowledgeable, but on the other hand, there might be uh, where it comes to be iffy to certain statements."
