        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:49.250000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. So maybe someone with some good advice. But 'd be careful about which tips you follow. Uh, looking back over the past year, would you say anything's changed about the way you look? Things up for projects or repairs? Maybe you use series more or less. Reach for YouTube first less often. Tell me bit about what's shifted, if anything."
