        "callId": "d53766c2a7174fc1b0119ec6c",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:12.089000Z",
        "message": "Oh, basically, I used to use, uh, YouTube until I found the positive and negative on the same situation. And, uh, I haven't found that on series, It's mostly, uh, correct information that I get."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d53766c2a7174fc1b0119ec6c",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:30.740000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So discovering mixed advice on YouTube. Pushed you to use Siri's more often since you found Siri's to be more consistently reliable. Did anyone friends, family, coworkers, ever suggest trying series, or was it something you found on your own?"
      },
