      {
        "callId": "8a4297f8fa7e4fe68b8cfb2e9",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:08:46.041000Z",
        "message": "Got it. ChatGPT is your starting point. Can you walk me through what usually prompts you to open it? Is there a particular kind of question or situation that makes it your go to?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8a4297f8fa7e4fe68b8cfb2e9",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:08:56.892000Z",
        "message": "Like, I I usually go to Google and search for ChatGPT. And I express what I feel or I feel overwhelmed. Something like that."
