      {
        "callId": "8a4297f8fa7e4fe68b8cfb2e9",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:09:10.062000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. You search for ChatGPT on Google, then use it to express what's on your mind, especially when you're feeling overwhelmed. Can you tell me about a specific time when you did this? What was going on, and what did you need answers or help with?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8a4297f8fa7e4fe68b8cfb2e9",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:09:25.642000Z",
        "message": "For example, when me and my husband had arguments and I need some advice how to deal with arguments."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8a4297f8fa7e4fe68b8cfb2e9",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:09:38.782000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. You turned to ChatGPT. Situations where you need advice about personal issues, like handling arguments with your husband. Can you walk me through what happened last time starting from when you decided to reach out? What steps did you take? What did you ask? And no worries. Are you okay with continuing? If you'd like, you can tell me what you were thinking or feeling when you decided to search for advice on arguments. Or if you prefer to switch topics, just let me know."
