        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:10:21.622000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. When you're not sure where to turn, you search for ChatGPT and see if it can help you figure things out or or provide an answer. When you use ChatGPT for advice about your"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8a4297f8fa7e4fe68b8cfb2e9",
