        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:04.572000Z",
        "message": "Really interesting. So you felt like ChatGPT gave you practical advice. Steps on how to handle and resolve arguments. Was there anything about using ChatGPT that frustrated you or felt a bit off during that process?"
