        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:17.261000Z",
        "message": "No. Not really. I just want ChatGPT to be honest. Of, um, who's who's, uh, wrong I mean, it's not really important for me who's right or wrong, but the is that I don't want chat GPT to how to say this? How to you know, like like, I just want him to be honest with me."
