        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:11:50.142000Z",
        "message": "That's clear. You want ChatGPT to be honest and direct. Not just polite or neutral. You're asking about something personal, you prefer straight answers over sugarcoating, even if it means tough truths, Thinking about the way ChatGPT responds,"
      },
