        "callId": "8a4297f8fa7e4fe68b8cfb2e9",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:02.112000Z",
        "message": "I just know about Gemini. And I the first time, my friend recommended me to chat GPT, and that's when exactly what I did. The first time. Every time I feel overwhelmed, So I just know this about the Gemini. So I tried but Gemini helps me a lot, though, just to, you know, edit photos and something like that stuff. But when it comes to advices, no."
