        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:31.572000Z",
        "message": "That's a great distinction. So Gemini is handy for things like editing photos or practical tasks. But when it comes to advice, especially emotional or personal stuff, ChatGPT is your go to. You imagine ChatGPT and Gemini as people at a party, what kind of personalities do you picture them having? How would they act"
