        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:14:59.631000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like you'd feel comfortable, um, sharing Chatzi PT advice? It's helpful, and you trusted enough to pass it on. Is there a word or feeling that pops into your head onto your head when you think about Chat GPT as a brand? Anything that really stands out emotionally or or just comes to mind?"
