        "message": "This is very, very awesome, and I'm glad that I what I'm feeling about the app that I'm using, especially ChatGPT. And I am so glad to talk to you. And, also, I want to know more about AI. In a positive way because, um, it has helped me a lot you know, especially when, um, I feel bored or I need something, ideas. You know? So this is very, very helpful to me, and this is very, very good."
