        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:03:13.527000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear yours is going well. Mine's been pretty good. Um, mostly chatting with folks and hearing how they use these AI tools. So you need to figure something out or have a question online, what's what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3d91d57e9ce346ddafec222c9",
