        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:03:34.087000Z",
        "message": "Classic Move. Walk me through your typical process. When you Google something. Like, what happens step by step from the moment you think, need to look this up to actually finding your answer"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3d91d57e9ce346ddafec222c9",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:03:46.127000Z",
        "message": "Just go to Google and ask the question."
