        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:03:50.997000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Pretty direct. You type in your question, do you usually click on a link right away, or do you look at things like the little summaries or answer boxes at the top? Tell"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3d91d57e9ce346ddafec222c9",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:04:00.537000Z",
