        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:04:06.727000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. You read the generated answer right at top. Uh, can you tell me about the last time you did this? What was the question or topic, and what happened from start to finish?"
      },
      {
