        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:04:21.077000Z",
        "message": "I can't really can't even remember put me on the spot. Oh, no. I was looking up something to do with how long it should take for a cut to heal? Qualified candidates tomorrow. Try Something to heal. Super grinder dot com slash try."
