        "time": "2025-09-14T00:04:44.617000Z",
        "message": "No worries. Some no worries. Sometimes details blur together. Especially with the everyday stuff. Let's stick with that healing cut example. When you were searching, what about Google's answer was most helpful to you? And was there anything that made you feel unsure or wish you'd done it differently?"
