        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:06:16.097000Z",
        "message": "Well, it just didn't you know, everything I read was supposed to heal and you know, within, like, 2 to 3 weeks, and that wasn't that's not the case. They took a hip out and a hip bone, and it didn't heal."
      },
      {
