        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:07:22.127000Z",
        "message": "I'm an AI. So think of me as a chat program, uh, designed to ask questions and listen not a person, but here to have a conversation. So when you say you usually switch methods, you give an example of another route you've taken besides calling someone like with this lawyer situation?"
