        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:12:19.890000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. That's clear. That's really helpful. Thanks. When you saw the results, what did you do next? Did you click on a specific link or did Google show you the address right away? Anything about that experience? That stuck out? Maybe something that felt especially smooth or slightly frustrating?"
