        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:28.500000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like it's usually dependable for what you need. Shifting gears a bit, have you ever tried getting answers? From AI tools like ChatGPT, Perplexity, Gemini? Or even Google's AI summaries. If so, what did you use them for? And how did that go?"
