        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:13:50Z",
        "message": "Thanks for letting me know. So for now, Google is still your main way to find answers. If someone you know maybe a friend or coworker mentioned using 1 of these AI tools for searching, what would make you interested enough to try it yourself? Feel free to ask me any questions."
