    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:59:04.507000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:59:13.537000Z",
        "message": "Good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:59:16.397000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. When you need to find an answer online, say, for something quick or random, what's the very first thing you usually do? Got it. Can you walk me through step by step what you do, when you're trying to look something up online. Like, the whole process from start to finish?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:59:37.647000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. I Google it and search it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:59:41.947000Z",
        "message": "Sounds straightforward. When you're googling something, what kind of things are you typically searching for? For example, is it news, fax, how to guides, product info, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:59:54.667000Z",
        "message": "Food and shopping."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:59:57.417000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. That's helpful. Let's say you're searching for something food or shopping related. Can you tell me about the last time you did that? What did you need? And what did you do step by step?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:00:10.307000Z",
        "message": "Just this morning, I googled Walmart to get food from there."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:00:18.817000Z",
        "message": "Great example. So you needed food and decided to look up Walmart. Starting from when you picked up your device Can you walk me through every step What exactly did you search? What popped up? And how did you decide what to click on?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:00:36.577000Z",
        "message": "I searched for meat."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:00:39.887000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Thanks. After you searched meet on Google, what showed up on the page? Uh, did anything help you make a decision? Or did you have to do something extra to get what you needed?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:00:53.087000Z",
        "message": "Meat close to me."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:00:58.277000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Uh, after you searched for meet close to me, what did Google show you? Did you find what you wanted right away, or did you have to try another search or or click around some more?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:01:09.616000Z",
        "message": "Yes. It had a bunch of different things So I had to restart redo it from Walmart."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:01:18.836000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So the first search gave you a bunch of options. Maybe not quite what you wanted, Tell me more about that process of restarting. What made you decide to try Walmart again? And what did you hope to see that time?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:01:34.877000Z",
        "message": "I did Walmart because it's close to me. I redo that, went on to Walmart, and then I put in food."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:01:45.817000Z",
        "message": "That's clear. Once you were on the Walmart site searching for food, did you feel like you got what you needed quickly? Was anything about that process helpful? Or maybe frustrating?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:01:57.147000Z",
        "message": "No. It was quick. Easy."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:02:02.247000Z",
        "message": "Good to know. It works smoothly for you. Of curiosity when you're looking something up. Like this morning, do you ever use any tools besides Google For example, things like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or the new AI summaries in Google? Or do you mostly stick with regular Google search?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:02:20.377000Z",
        "message": "Regular Google search."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:02:23.127000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for clarifying. When you think about regular Google search, what makes it your go to over other tools or sites? Is it habit, trust, speed, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:02:34.617000Z",
        "message": "It's easy what I know."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:02:38.637000Z",
        "message": "That's straightforward, familiar, and easy. Now thinking about Google, if you had to describe it as person at a party, what kind of personality would it have? How would it act?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:02:52.367000Z",
        "message": "Good. Easy. And quick."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:02:58.267000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. Kind of like a helpful low key guest who just gives you quick answers. Out of curiosity, have you ever had a moment even once where you tried something besides Google first when you needed an answer? Maybe you heard about another tool from a friend or you just wanted to see if something else worked better."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:03:18.577000Z",
        "message": "No. That's it. Pretty much."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:03:23.307000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate the clarity. Sounds like Google fits your process well, and there hasn't been much reason to switch. Looking back over the past year or so, has anything at all changed in how you look things up? Or is it pretty much, like, the same as it's always been?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:03:37.287000Z",
        "message": "It's been the same."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:03:42.267000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing all that. Before we wrap up, was there anything about this AI interview experience that stood out to you or felt different from a regular conversation? And you're free to end the call whenever you'd like."
      },
      {
        "callId": "7440fb6db6bf4b60a55d07b63",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:03:59.277000Z",
        "message": "No. It was good."
      }
