        "callId": "b8bb08f853694679af00c66be",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:57:14.408000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. When you need to look something up or get a quick answer online, what's what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b8bb08f853694679af00c66be",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:57:22.907000Z",
        "message": "Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b8bb08f853694679af00c66be",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:57:26.128000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Can you walk me through your usual process when you use Google to look something up step by step? For example, what's the last thing you searched and did you go about it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b8bb08f853694679af00c66be",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:57:39.898000Z",
        "message": "Fast food restaurants. I typed on the Google search bar, hit the microphone, and spoke my response."
