        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:58:37.947000Z",
        "message": "Speed sounds important to you. Was there anything about using Google that felt annoying or could have been better during that search?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b8bb08f853694679af00c66be",
        "index": 17,
