        "message": "Out? Thanks."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b8bb08f853694679af00c66be",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:00:07.858000Z",
        "message": "Just googling school."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b8bb08f853694679af00c66be",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:00:11.088000Z",
        "message": "So you used ChatGPT yesterday. Searching for something school related. Can you walk me through what you did? What question did you ask? And what kind of response did ChatGPT give you? Feel free to ask me any questions. Are you still there?"
      },
      {
