        "message": "Makes sense. When when you think about speed, accuracy, or feeling confident in the answer, how does ChatGPT stack up compared to Google for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b8bb08f853694679af00c66be",
        "index": 49,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:02:11.458000Z",
        "message": "It's much better. It's my first choice."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b8bb08f853694679af00c66be",
        "index": 50,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:02:15.228000Z",
        "message": "You've landed on ChatGPT as your go to. Thinking about brand vibes for a second. If ChatGPT and Google were people at a party, what kind of personalities would they have?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b8bb08f853694679af00c66be",
        "index": 51,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:02:28.307000Z",
        "message": "Chat. CPT would be be have a better personality than Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b8bb08f853694679af00c66be",
        "index": 52,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:02:33.448000Z",
        "message": "Love the comparison. What words or traits come to mind for each 1? How would you describe Chatuchu PT's personality at the party and Google's?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b8bb08f853694679af00c66be",
