        "callId": "b8bb08f853694679af00c66be",
        "index": 54,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:02:53.088000Z",
        "message": "That's clear. Fun and helpful versus dull and boring. You share answers, with friends or classmates, which engine's responses feel more credible or or trustworthy? To quote, why?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b8bb08f853694679af00c66be",
        "index": 55,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:03:06.768000Z",
        "message": "Chat CPT because it gives you more than 1 and is more detailed."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b8bb08f853694679af00c66be",
        "index": 56,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:03:12.938000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful. Looking back, has the way you search for info or answers changed compared to a year ago? Any moments when you started using something besides Google first? Or more often?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b8bb08f853694679af00c66be",
        "index": 57,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:03:26.948000Z",
        "message": "More often."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b8bb08f853694679af00c66be",
        "index": 58,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:03:30.658000Z",
        "message": "When you started using ChatGPT more often, was there anything that triggered that switch for you? Maybe a specific moment, recommendation, or frustration. With another tool."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b8bb08f853694679af00c66be",
        "index": 59,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:03:42.738000Z",
        "message": "Frustration with another tool."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b8bb08f853694679af00c66be",
        "index": 60,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:03:47.248000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Can you share a bit more about that frustration? What happened that pushed you to try ChatGPT instead?"
