        "index": 62,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:04:01.108000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Before we wrap up, is there anything you'd wish these Answer Engines could do that they don't yet? Any features or improvements you'd love to see?"
      },
