  {
    "id": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
    "responseId": "87ce4d3d99cd4a81b7de9fe6b",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:57:46.254000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:57:54.884000Z",
        "message": "Bed,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:58:02.154000Z",
        "message": "Feel free to ask me any questions."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:58:04.984000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. A male. All male. Don't have any? Oh, ma'am."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:58:10.444000Z",
        "message": "Got it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:58:12.013000Z",
        "message": "What?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:58:13.894000Z",
        "message": "No worries. I wanna make sure I'm following what you're saying. Um, can you tell me more about what you mean?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:58:20.104000Z",
        "message": "I have no questions at this time."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:58:23.593000Z",
        "message": "Totally fine. No pressure. Just so you know, I'm here to chat about how you search for answers online, and the different tools you might use, like Google, ChatGPT, or others. If you ever feel like sharing how you usually look stuff up, I'm all ears. Or if you prefer to wrap up, just let me know."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:58:42.954000Z",
        "message": "How do you look up certain answers?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:58:46.894000Z",
        "message": "Great question. I'm all about asking and listening, so I don't actually look things up myself. Um, but I'm curious. When you need to find an answer online, what's what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:58:58.904000Z",
        "message": "I usually look up Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:59:03.754000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing. Walk me through your usual process with Google. What's the typical way you go from having a question to getting your answer?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:59:13.784000Z",
        "message": "Just asking the question on Google. And looking up what it really means, I guess, you can say, or different websites where you can find the answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:59:28.064000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. When you see the results, how do you decide which website or link to click on first? What grabs your attention?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:59:35.864000Z",
        "message": "I guess mainly the 1 that has the definition of what it means. As you gravitate towards that more."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:59:44.764000Z",
        "message": "Got it. You're looking for that clear, straight to the point definition. When you pick 1, what makes you feel like you can trust that answer is actually correct."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:59:55.003000Z",
        "message": "I look at mainly different ones. And I see if some of them are similar. I just go with the 1 that's mainly the similar the other websites."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:00:08.374000Z",
        "message": "That's smart. Kind of like seeing if they all line up before trusting it. Has there ever been a time when the answers were really different from each other? How did you handle that?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:00:20.584000Z",
        "message": "I just considered both of them. Just to see maybe what is more different than the other person's opinion. On the definition."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:00:36.394000Z",
        "message": "Interesting approach. Sort of keeping both in mind and noticing the differences. Has there ever been a case where you wished Google or any of these tools could do something extra to help you decide between those conflicting answers?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:00:50.163000Z",
        "message": "Yes. Um, I just click on the websites and just jot down information from 1 and then go to the other 1. And go jot down the other information. Just see if there's a a little bit of similarities, but also different. Similarities. Different 1. Different aspects of it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:01:11.754000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for breaking that down. Sounds like you do a bit of a bit of comparing and note taking. What's, like, the most helpful part of that process for you? And is there anything about it that feels annoying or time consuming?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:01:25.014000Z",
        "message": "No. Not really."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:01:28.894000Z",
        "message": "Alright. Sounds like the process works pretty smoothly. For you. You mentioned using Google. Do you ever try other tools like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Gemini when you're looking for answers? Or is it usually just Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:01:43.254000Z",
        "message": "It's usually just Google sometimes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:01:49.564000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Can you remember a time when you used something other than Google to find an answer? What made you choose that other tool?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:02:02.264000Z",
        "message": "Just to see if there's a difference in Google and the other website to look up stuff."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:02:11.654000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. You were kind of comparing how the answers stack up. Um, when you did that, how did the experience feel different between Google and the other tool or website? Anything stand out to you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:02:23.304000Z",
        "message": "It was different. And it was pretty much different."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:02:30.884000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. When you say pretty much different, can you tell me a bit more about what jumped out at you? Like, was it the way the answers were written? How fast you got them? Or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:02:41.093000Z",
        "message": "It was, um, different answers and different definitions just like Google would give me, but it was just a little bit more how would I say it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:02:53.174000Z",
        "message": "Take your time."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:02:53.304000Z",
