        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:03:23.514000Z",
        "message": "Nice. It gave you more perspectives to consider. Is there a type of question or or situation where you'd pick that that tool over Google? Because of the way it breaks things down."
      },
      {
