        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-14T00:04:17.754000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like maybe Bing. That's helpful. When you used Bing for your paper, what made you feel it was giving you better or more useful answers than Google in that moment?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5690a627fa5140479a2c2b1bf",
