  {
    "id": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
    "responseId": "ce34a7560477410d9be88d06f",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:55:07.597000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:55:15.597000Z",
        "message": "Very good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:55:18.286000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. Let's get rolling. When you need answers online, what's what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:55:25.856000Z",
        "message": "Go on Google and search."
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:55:29.017000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Can you walk me through your typical process starting from when you think of a question to when you find your answer?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:55:37.147000Z",
        "message": "Right on the search bar for the question. Click on search and wait for the response."
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:55:44.577000Z",
        "message": "Once Thanks for sharing. Uh, thinking about the results you see, what's what's the next thing you do after Google shows you its responses?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:55:56.917000Z",
        "message": "Then I will click on whatever comes out. And the answer should be right there in the story for whatever I'm searching."
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:56:06.047000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Um, thinking back to your most recent search, uh, what was the topic or question you looked up? And can you walk me through how that experience went step by step?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:56:16.727000Z",
        "message": "Why did Jeffrey Dahmer kill people? I was watching his TV show, and I was curious about the life and his family and what happened."
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:56:27.087000Z",
        "message": "That's a pretty intense question. TV shows do spark some wild curiosity. So after you typed in, why did Jeffrey Dahmer, kill people, and hit search, did the results look like? Did you click on a new story, Wikipedia, an official site, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:56:42.767000Z",
        "message": "Yes. I was just a site, and it said the stories of how he died in jail and everything else."
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:56:53.777000Z",
        "message": "Got it. When you got your answer, was there anything about that process that felt especially helpful or on the flip side, annoying or frustrating?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:57:03.667000Z",
        "message": "It was helpful. I just reading, doing some research on movies or TV shows, stuff like that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:57:12.377000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. So for research on movies or TV shows, Google meets your needs pretty well. Have you ever tried using other tools? Like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Gemini? For these kinds of searches. If so, what led you to try those instead?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:57:30.287000Z",
        "message": "No. I tried Safari and Google. I don't really use AI."
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:57:35.457000Z",
        "message": "I hear you. So Google and Safari are your main go tos right now. What is it about Google that makes it your default choice over anything else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:57:45.917000Z",
        "message": "I've been using it for years, and it's fast. All I gotta do is Google information, and it just comes right after."
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:57:54.417000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for that. Um, when you think about Google, just the search part, do any words or feelings come to mind? Like, how would you describe it to a friend?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:58:05.827000Z",
        "message": "It's easy. Just go to search and it's exciting. You get to find out so many things you didn't know."
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:58:13.767000Z",
        "message": "I love that exciting doesn't come up often for search. If you imagine Google as a person at a party, how would they act? What kind of personality would they have?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:58:25.767000Z",
        "message": "Exciting personality."
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:58:29.526000Z",
        "message": "Nice. If you were to share an answer, you found let's say, about Jeffrey Dahmer. With a friend, does getting it from Google feel more credible or or trustworthy than from somewhere else? Or does that not matter much to you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:58:44.127000Z",
        "message": "Doesn't matter much to me. Even just wanted to find the information."
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:58:49.767000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for being honest. Thinking back over the last year or so, has anything about the way you search for information changed? How often you search, what you use, or how quickly you trust the results?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:59:01.386000Z",
        "message": "No. It's been the same."
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:59:04.617000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. And have friends or coworkers ever suggested you try any new tools for looking things up? Is it mostly just like Google in your circles too?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:59:14.327000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. They they don't really use the AI either. They just use Google Safari. Microsoft."
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:59:23.217000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful to know. Let's wrap up. Thanks for sharing your thoughts and stories. Before we finish, any thoughts about doing an interview with AI today? Anything you wish Answer Engines could do"
      },
      {
        "callId": "a728c7d7fce8441fbb0173127",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:59:35.636000Z",
        "message": "No."
      }
