        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:49:56.076000Z",
        "message": "Really interesting. So Google's basically your habit. But ChatGPT shines when you need those deeper dives. Thinking about how each makes you feel. If Google and ChatGPT were people at a party, how would you describe them? What kind of vibe does each give off?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ce42995be87d4254a448ca82f",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:50:13.586000Z",
