        "callId": "ce42995be87d4254a448ca82f",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:50:24.495000Z",
        "message": "That means the I like those descriptions. A relaxed, direct Google, and a thoughtful, in-depth chat GPT. When you share answers with friends, maybe about your bets or other info, which engine's answer feels more credible to quote or or pass along? But what goes into that feeling?"
