        "time": "2025-09-13T23:51:20.245000Z",
        "message": "No worries. I'm here just to listen and learn from your experiences. There's no right or wrong answer. Looking back a year ago, do you notice anything that's changed about how you look up answers online? Any shifts in how often you use Google versus ChatGPT or which you turn to first?"
