        "time": "2025-09-13T23:51:37.555000Z",
        "message": "Actually, use Google more. Like I said, I mean, if I wanna in-depth answer, on a topic that I think I don't want this general info, I would use ChatGP but I'm kinda using Google a little more I usually just want basic answers for the most part when I'm searching for something."
