        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:51:57.516000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful to hear. So day to day, it's mostly quick basic lookups. Which keeps Google as your main tool. But for deep or detailed stuff, ChatGPT steps in Has anyone in your circle friends, coworkers, or people online ever suggested 1 of these engines for specific tasks? If so, what were they recommending? And why?"
