        "message": "Understood. It sounds like your habits are mostly your own. Not really shaped by outside suggestions. Ahead, can you imagine anything that would make you switch your main tool away from Google and make something like ChatGPT your default even for quick stuff? Or do you think you'll always stick with Google for basics?"
