        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:47:27.478000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So when you switch over to Chateap or another AI tool for double checking What's that process like for you? Can you walk me through a specific recent time you did it? Starting with what led you to switch and then every step you took?"
