        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:47:43.028000Z",
        "message": "Recently, when doing research about the Charlie Curtiss I noticed there were a lot of articles and things on TikTok and other social media websites that would claim that NFL teams or players were doing special things to memorialize Charlie Kurtz. So I took all that information and asked CHITPT if it was correct, and it all ended up being false."
