  {
    "id": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
    "responseId": "4e190c3417264553a30ceb884",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:44:12.533000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:44:20.333000Z",
        "message": "It's gone okay. Thank you."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:44:23.503000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it's been okay. Let's start with something simple. When you need to find an answer online, whether it's something simple or or more involved, what's usually the first thing you do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:44:35.883000Z",
        "message": "Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:44:38.343000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Can you walk me through your typical process? When you use Google to look something up?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:44:44.083000Z",
        "message": "I just use Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:44:44.563000Z",
        "message": "Starting from what"
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:44:46.313000Z",
        "message": "I just used Google as a search engine, but now I've I'm starting to use Gemini."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:44:54.093000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. Sounds like there's been a recent shift for you. Can you tell me about the last time you used Gemini? Instead of Google? What led you to give it"
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:45:02.153000Z",
        "message": "Actually, actually, I tried it yesterday, I was looking for directions when I, uh, could not find on maps."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:45:13.093000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Tell me more about what happened yesterday. What did you need directions for, and how did you end up using Gemini instead of Google Maps?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:45:23.413000Z",
        "message": "Um, I've had Gemini for quite a while, but I just have never used it. Um, yesterday, I was just looking for um, actually, bus schedules."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:45:35.543000Z",
        "message": "Okay. So you were searching for bus schedules and turned to Gemini. Can you tell me the full story step by step? Start with what made you pick Gemini for that search and what happened as you used it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:45:48.753000Z",
        "message": "Because I couldn't I wasn't getting any answers from just regular Google. So I when I opened up Gemini, It was very interest interesting. It was so quick, and it gave me the website that I need needed to to find the bus schedules."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:46:12.593000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like Gemini felt a bit different. What part of that experience with Gemini stood out most for you? Was it the speed, the type of answer, or something else? Feel free to ask me any questions. Feel free to ask me any questions."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:47:08.043000Z",
        "message": "Are you still there?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:47:10.543000Z",
        "message": "Yes. I'm still here. I'm curious. When Gemini helped you with the bus schedules, was there anything about the way it answered? That felt especially helpful or maybe annoying compared to a regular Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:47:22.683000Z",
        "message": "It just popped up with answers that I needed to know. It was really quick. I just found it helpful and useful. I didn't think I'd be using it before, but I like it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:47:40.023000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. When you got Gemini's answer, did you feel confident it was right, or did you do anything else to double check, like looking the info up another way or asking someone else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:47:52.163000Z",
        "message": "No. I I believe it was correct because it gave me straight to the right the right bus schedule app that I needed, and I didn't have to to look through a whole page to see which 1 was the right 1."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:48:10.773000Z",
        "message": "That sounds pretty satisfying, not having to scroll through lots of links."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:48:15.733000Z",
        "message": "Scroll everything."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:48:15.993000Z",
        "message": "Thinking back if I hear you. Scrolling through a whole page of results can be a hassle. If you compare the experience with Gemini, uh, to how it usually feels with Google, how do you describe the difference? What stands out most between the 2 for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:48:33.903000Z",
        "message": "The screen image is just so different and easy on Gemini. And they don't give you a whole list of pages of options. I was specific at what I asked, and then they were specific at what they gave me."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:48:52.562000Z",
        "message": "That's really clear. Sounds like you value getting a direct answer rather than a bunch of options. You line up"
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:48:59.523000Z",
        "message": "Correct."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:49:01.343000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for confirming. Thinking about other answer engines like ChatGPT or Perplexity, have you ever tried those for finding information? If so, how did the experience compare to what you had with Gemini or Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:49:16.073000Z",
        "message": "I have never tried another program."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:49:21.783000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate your honesty. Uh, if you think about Gemini, Google, and maybe other tools you've heard of, what words come to mind for each 1. For example, what do you think of when someone mentions Google Answers? And what about Gemini?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:49:39.463000Z",
        "message": "I've never had a discussion about this with anybody except for you."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:49:44.943000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:49:45.393000Z",
        "message": "I I just find that the I found that Gemini seems to work fine. I know there's a couple other ones out there, but probably quite a few. But I have no option or no desire to use them after using Gemini."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:50:05.923000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like Gemini feels like a good fit for what you need right now. If you"
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:50:09.613000Z",
        "message": "Exactly."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:50:12.563000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Thinking back to maybe a year ago, you say anything's changed in how you look things up online now that you have Gemini in the mix? Or is it pretty much the same? Just with an extra option?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:50:26.813000Z",
        "message": "It's pretty much the same. Just an extra option. It's, um, but it's a good option to have."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:50:33.373000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate you sharing your take. Is there anything you wish Gemini or Any Answer Engine could do that would make things even easier or more useful for you. The future?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:50:46.673000Z",
        "message": "To be honest with you, I haven't really thought about it. So I don't have an answer for you for that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:50:55.113000Z",
        "message": "That's totally fine. Thanks for being open. Um, before we wrap up, what's it been like talking to an AI about your search habits today? Any thoughts or feedback for me?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:51:07.163000Z",
        "message": "No. It's just kinda creepy the way it's just like talking to a human being. And sometimes I get phone calls on my phone and I'm thinking it's a human and it's not. So that kinda creeps me out a little bit."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:51:25.953000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for being honest about that. It's definitely a new experience for a lot of people. If you ever want to end this call, you can do so anytime. And thanks again sharing your stories and and perspectives."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:51:39.282000Z",
        "message": "And thank you. I appreciate it very much."
      },
      {
        "callId": "df2cb72c1a7348dd83e80094e",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:51:42.522000Z",
        "message": "Thank you for calling."
      }
