        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:46:55.357000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like it was easy to spot since it was such big news. In that moment, you feel confident the info was accurate? Any urge to double check or look at other engines like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Gemini? Or was Google enough for you?"
      },
      {
