      {
        "callId": "d09ad856266a41819363458cf",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:47:18.948000Z",
        "message": "Very clear. So for breaking news, Google tends to, uh, be all you need. Now, thinking about AI tools like ChatGPT or Gemini, do you ever use those when you're searching for answers, or do you mainly stick with Google?"
