      {
        "callId": "d09ad856266a41819363458cf",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:48:13.708000Z",
        "message": "On May was actually looking for us in recipes on Jets GBTs easier, and I was looking for a cookie recipe."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d09ad856266a41819363458cf",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:48:24.958000Z",
        "message": "Walk me through that moment. What did you type into ChatGPT, and what happened next? Did anything stand out about the answer? Or how it felt different from a Google search?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d09ad856266a41819363458cf",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:48:37.408000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. So I should, uh, chat GBT. How does go what is Gordon Ramsey's cookie recipe he uses? And then it told me the step by step in, uh, everything. How to make it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d09ad856266a41819363458cf",
