        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:49:44.358000Z",
        "message": "You trust it if it looks useful and clear. Switching gears. You think up about Google Answers versus ChatGPT, and maybe Perplexity or Gemini, what words come to mind for each? Feel free to start with just 1 engine, whichever pops up first."
