        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:50:11.157000Z",
        "message": "Sure thing. When you think about Google, Chat GPT, Perplexity, or Gemini, what do you feel or imagine about each 1? For example, does Google feel trustworthy or old school? Is ChatGPT helpful or creative? You can pick any words or feelings that come to mind."
