      },
      {
        "callId": "d09ad856266a41819363458cf",
        "index": 48,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:50:48.748000Z",
        "message": "Love that. ChatGPT feels unique and gives proper answers, while Google feels old school, giving you just the basic If you had to tell a friend which 1 to use for a recipe, which would you recommend? And what would you say about it"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d09ad856266a41819363458cf",
        "index": 49,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:51:04.398000Z",
        "message": "I would say, recipes, I would recommend ChatGPT because it gives you the clear cut answers you need to know, and it's all neatly organized."
