        "index": 50,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:51:18.688000Z",
        "message": "That's clear. For recipes, you'd go with ChatGPT. Clear, organized answers. Is there any situation where you'd still definitely pick Google first instead? What sort of task or question pulls you back to Google?"
