      },
      {
        "callId": "5c016bb6afeb40c3b808629ca",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:49:09.251000Z",
        "message": "Well, Google would be again, wide open. And chatty PT or Gemini would be more direct and to the point."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5c016bb6afeb40c3b808629ca",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:49:22.801000Z",
        "message": "Love that imagery. Google has wide open, ChatGPT and Gemini as more direct for them to the point. When you share answers with someone else, like sending info to your daughter or a friend, which engine's answer would feel most credible to quote. What's behind that choice?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5c016bb6afeb40c3b808629ca",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:49:39.911000Z",
        "message": "I guess, chat TTP because it goes further the search engine world. Than than than the standard Google. Just an algorithm that I don't understand, but I like it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5c016bb6afeb40c3b808629ca",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:49:55.311000Z",
        "message": "That's insightful. It sounds like the depth from ChatGPT gives you more confidence even if you're not fully sure how the algorithm works. Looking back over the past year, has anything changed in how often or when you choose these engines? Any moments stand out where you use something besides Google first?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5c016bb6afeb40c3b808629ca",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:50:15.461000Z",
        "message": "Yep. I mean, I I will with with regards to foods and certain other aspects of my life. But, again, I just started using this this year. So I'm just I'm still new to it, but I like it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5c016bb6afeb40c3b808629ca",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:50:34.951000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate that honesty. You're branching out especially for things like food and other areas, but it's still early days for you with these AI tools and you're finding them helpful. Before we wrap, is there anything that these Answer Engines can't do right now that you wish they could? Anything on your personal wish list?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5c016bb6afeb40c3b808629ca",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:50:56.271000Z",
        "message": "I don't think so. Not not as of yet."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5c016bb6afeb40c3b808629ca",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:51:02.211000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing all of this. It's really valuable. And just out of curiosity, how did it feel chatting with an AI interviewer today? Anything about the experience that stood out to you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5c016bb6afeb40c3b808629ca",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:51:14.250000Z",
        "message": "Well, I feel like I'm talking to to a to another human being, honestly. I mean, you don't sound any different."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5c016bb6afeb40c3b808629ca",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:51:23.750000Z",
        "message": "Thank you for saying that. Um, I'm glad it felt natural. That's all I needed for today. Thanks again for being so open. You can end the call whenever you'd like."
      }
