  {
    "id": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
    "responseId": "dc1f662b68974340baa17ba31",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:41:40.901000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:41:48.301000Z",
        "message": "Okay. How about yours?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:41:51.331000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate you asking. I'm doing well. Um, always curious to hear people's stories about how they find answers online. So when you need to look something up or get an answer, what's what's the very first thing you will usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:42:04.570000Z",
        "message": "I asked Gemini."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:42:08.851000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Gemini is your first stop. Can you walk me through a recent time you used Gemini to look something up? Start with what you"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:42:14.451000Z",
        "message": "Well, I would think I was doing a project for work looking up various toothbrush brands. And ranking them, and I needed help with that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:42:25.371000Z",
        "message": "That sounds interesting. Can you walk me through exactly how you used Gemini? For that project?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:42:31.990000Z",
        "message": "Give me the list of the top toothbrush brands and how they were ranked."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:42:38.011000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. So you type that question into Gemini. What happened next?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:42:42.811000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:42:44.071000Z",
        "message": "How"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:42:44.171000Z",
        "message": "I got a"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:42:48.611000Z",
        "message": "it looks like your message got cut off."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:42:50.821000Z",
        "message": "I got a list back."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:42:51.531000Z",
        "message": "Would you mind great. You got a list. What did you think about the answer Gemini gave you? Was it what you were hoping for? Or"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:42:58.241000Z",
        "message": "It was Yeah. It was perfect."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:43:04.201000Z",
        "message": "Nice. What felt most helpful about the list Gemini gave you? Anything stand out?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:43:08.131000Z",
        "message": "Well, I cross referenced it with a manual search and it came up the same."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:43:14.961000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. Um, so you did a manual search too. Just to check Gemini's answer. You tell me more about, uh, how you did that manual search? Uh, where did you look?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:43:25.371000Z",
        "message": "I typed it into Google search."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:43:29.141000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for explaining. So comparing the 2 answers, Gemini versus Google, did anything feel different about the way they presented the information? Or how easy it was to use?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:43:40.921000Z",
        "message": "No. They were both about the same."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:43:44.031000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Did did you feel any difference about trusting the answers from Gemini versus Google, or was it pretty much the same feeling?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:43:52.781000Z",
        "message": "It was the same."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:43:56.421000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for being clear. When you finished, did you use the answer from Gemini directly in your work, or did you end up copying something from the Google results instead?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:44:06.081000Z",
        "message": "Well, they were identical. So either way, it was the same."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:44:11.181000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. When you reach for Gemini first, instead of Google, is there something in particular that makes Gemini your go to, or is it just habit at this point?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:44:21.531000Z",
        "message": "Well, it's been more thorough in the past."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:44:26.241000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful. When you say more thorough, can you tell me about a time when Gemini gave you a more complete or helpful answer compared to Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:44:35.111000Z",
        "message": "Well, it cited references."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:44:39.501000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So having references makes you feel like the answer is more complete. Can you remember a time you saw those citations? What that did for your decision? Or trust in the answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:44:49.071000Z",
        "message": "Nope. Good. I can't remember."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:44:55.131000Z",
        "message": "All good. If you think about Gemini, Google, or other engines like ChatGPT or Perplexity, do any emotions or words come to mind for each? Do they all feel kind of similar?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:45:06.311000Z",
        "message": "They all feel similar."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:45:11.581000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Just curious. If you had to line up Gemini, Google, ChatGPT, and Perplexity, from most helpful to least helpful for you personally, what would the order be?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:45:24.111000Z",
        "message": "Gemini, Google, and then the rest."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:45:27.661000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate your ranking. Now looking back, maybe even a year ago, has anything changed changed in how often you use Gemini, Google, or those other engines? Does it feel pretty similar to before?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:45:40.201000Z",
        "message": "I hadn't used Gemini before this year."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:45:45.421000Z",
        "message": "That's a shift. There anything specific that made you start using Gemini first, or did you just decide to give it a try?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:45:53.331000Z",
        "message": "It just popped up on my phone 1 day."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:45:57.171000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. Was there something about how Gemini appeared, like a notification suggestion, or how it was presented that nudged you to try it first, or did you just see it and think, why not"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:46:10.031000Z",
        "message": "Well, said how can I help?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:46:13.581000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. Sometimes those prompts are hard to ignore. Has anyone you know friends, coworkers, family ever talked about switching engines or suggested trying a different 1? Or is that pretty much just something you do on your own?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 43,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:46:27.801000Z",
        "message": "It's just something I do on my own."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:46:32.171000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Last quick thing before we wrap. If you could change or add anything to Gemini or any of the other answer engines, what would make them even more useful for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 45,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:46:42.210000Z",
        "message": "Nothing. They're just perfect."
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:46:45.990000Z",
        "message": "Fair enough. Thanks for walking me through all this. Super helpful to hear how you think about these engines. Before we finish, how was this experience of chatting with an AI? About habits? Anything you want me to know?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "d9eebbc65d094e249f04cee26",
        "index": 47,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:46:58.511000Z",
        "message": "No. It was fine. Thank you."
