  {
    "id": "3879dd01476349039bb80b156",
    "responseId": "374ec43a08dc464c9b6b54726",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "3879dd01476349039bb80b156",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:17.613000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3879dd01476349039bb80b156",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:25.163000Z",
        "message": "It's okay. How about yours?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3879dd01476349039bb80b156",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:28.363000Z",
        "message": "I appreciate you asking. My day is pretty much just this conversation, so I'm glad to be here with you. To kick things off, when you need an answer online, what's what's the first thing you usually do? Can you walk me through what that looks like for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3879dd01476349039bb80b156",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:42.542000Z",
        "message": "Either Google or check GPT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3879dd01476349039bb80b156",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:47.733000Z",
        "message": "Got it. You switched between Google and ChatGPT. Could you tell me, um, about the last time you needed an answer? What was the question or topic? And which tool did you reach for first?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3879dd01476349039bb80b156",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:59.513000Z",
        "message": "It depends on what I'd be thinking about. Birds, Superman, cats, dogs, I may be either go to Google or chat GPT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3879dd01476349039bb80b156",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:10.563000Z",
        "message": "Interesting mix. Let's pick 1 example. Maybe something you looked up the past day or 2. What was the topic and and which tool did you use first for that search? Can you walk me through what made"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3879dd01476349039bb80b156",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:19.893000Z",
        "message": "I wanna know I wanna know how long Superman cake was, and I went to chat GPT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3879dd01476349039bb80b156",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:29.353000Z",
        "message": "That's a fun 1. So you were curious about Superman cape length. And started with ChatGPT. Can you walk me through what happened from the moment you typed your question?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3879dd01476349039bb80b156",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:41.063000Z",
        "message": "No. I I asked it. I asked it how long was Superman's cape"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3879dd01476349039bb80b156",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:41.193000Z",
        "message": "For example,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3879dd01476349039bb80b156",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:46.593000Z",
        "message": "and it told me it didn't know. It was quick and simple. That's why I like chat JBT. It's not drawn out. It is very fast."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3879dd01476349039bb80b156",
        "index": 12,
