        "callId": "627b6f9affa44b41aaa5504ee",
        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:45:48.781000Z",
        "message": "GPT more often than before, or do you still reach for Google just as much?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "627b6f9affa44b41aaa5504ee",
        "index": 47,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:45:54.091000Z",
        "message": "Well, every time I say Siri, could could you find this for me? It's always pops out the GPT. And GPT is the search engine. Using to find whatever I ask for."
      },
      {
        "callId": "627b6f9affa44b41aaa5504ee",
        "index": 48,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:46:08.831000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like GPT, uh, has become your default when you ask Siri for something. Using it more now for your search"
      },
      {
        "callId": "627b6f9affa44b41aaa5504ee",
        "index": 49,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:46:13.661000Z",
        "message": "Okay. Yeah. Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "627b6f9affa44b41aaa5504ee",
        "index": 50,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:46:16.261000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for rolling with all these questions. 1 last thing before we wrap up. If you could chain"
      },
      {
        "callId": "627b6f9affa44b41aaa5504ee",
        "index": 51,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:46:22.001000Z",
        "message": "You're welcome."
      },
      {
        "callId": "627b6f9affa44b41aaa5504ee",
        "index": 52,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:46:24.341000Z",
        "message": "appreciate it. Before we finish, how to doing this kind of interview with an AI AI feel compared to other surveys or chats you've had? Any thoughts?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "627b6f9affa44b41aaa5504ee",
        "index": 53,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:46:34.921000Z",
        "message": "No. This is wonderful. If I could do all the surveys like this, it will be easier than reading. That'll be fantastic."
      },
      {
        "callId": "627b6f9affa44b41aaa5504ee",
        "index": 54,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:46:49.391000Z",
        "message": "That's great to hear. I'm glad it felt easy. Again for sharing your thoughts today. Um, you can end the call, um, whenever you're ready. Take care."
      },
      {
        "callId": "627b6f9affa44b41aaa5504ee",
        "index": 55,
        "role": "user",
