  {
    "id": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
    "responseId": "b4c083f647214f03a59ece477",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:36:46.194000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:36:53.704000Z",
        "message": "It's going pretty good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:36:57.234000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. Let's jump in. When you're looking for answers online, maybe to settle a debate, fix something, or just satisfy your curiosity. What's the first thing you usually do? Walk me through that process as it happens for you."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:12.484000Z",
        "message": "I go to DuckDuckGo, type it in, and see If not there, I go to Google. And type it in and see."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:20.644000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So DuckDuckGo is your starting point, and Google is your backup. Can you tell me a bit more about"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:25.994000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:27.294000Z",
        "message": "why DuckDuckGo gets the first shot? What makes it your go to for looking things up?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:33.794000Z",
        "message": "Well, I just like them more."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:38.403000Z",
        "message": "Got it. You like them more. Can you tell me a story about the last time you looked something up with DuckDuckGo? What was the question? And how did the experience play out step by step?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:49.304000Z",
        "message": "The question was a car part. My car that broke. I don't see where to buy it online."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:59.554000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing. So you needed to track down a car part online. When you type that into DuckDuckGo, what happened next? Did you find what you needed, or did you run into any roadblocks?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:10.753000Z",
        "message": "I found what I needed."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:15.224000Z",
        "message": "Nice. What part of that experience with Duck DuckGo felt most helpful to you? Anything that stood out or was it just straightforward?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:23.624000Z",
        "message": "Straightforward."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:26.564000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. If DuckDuckGo hadn't helped you find that car part, what would you have tried next?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:32.684000Z",
        "message": "Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:35.164000Z",
        "message": "When you do switch to Google after DuckDuckGo, does it feel any different? What stands out to you about using Google for those kinds of searches?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:43.874000Z",
        "message": "They run about the same."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:47.824000Z",
        "message": "Understood. So for you, DuckDuckGo and Google mostly feel similar in how they how they answer your questions. Do you ever use any of the newer AI driven tools like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Google's AI summaries you're looking things up. If so, what's the situation where you'd pick 1 of those?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:07.434000Z",
        "message": "I haven't used it yet, but willing to use it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:11.684000Z",
        "message": "Good to know. What would make you decide to try an AI tool like ChatGPT or Perplexity for a search instead of sticking with DuckDuckGo or Google. Any particular kind of question or situation where that sounds appealing?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:25.344000Z",
        "message": "Not that I can think of."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:29.544000Z",
        "message": "Fair enough. Let's shift a bit. When you think about DuckDuckGo or Google, are there any words, feelings, or mental images that into your head? For example, some folks associate DuckDuckGo with privacy. Or Google with being very big. What comes to mind for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:46.094000Z",
        "message": "Both of those come to mind. DuckDuckGo is private."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:48.744000Z",
        "message": "That's a clear that's helpful. Privacy sounds like a big part of DuckDuckGo's appeal for you. What about Google? Any emotions or associations, positive or negative, that pop up when you think about using it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:40:03.604000Z",
        "message": "It's positive."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:40:07.464000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. If you had to describe DuckDuckGo and Google as people at a party, what kind of personalities would they have? How would each of them act?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:40:20.074000Z",
        "message": "I think it'll be entertaining."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:40:24.604000Z",
        "message": "That's an interesting way to put it. What about Duck Duck Go's personality at this party? How do you imagine they'd behave? And how about Google? Any differences you'd picture?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:40:34.584000Z",
        "message": "I find that doctor Go may be more humorous. And Google will be more facts."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:40:43.704000Z",
        "message": "Love that. DuckDuckGo, as the more humorous guest, Google as the fact sharer. You get an answer that you want to share with someone else, say, sending a link or giving advice, does it matter to you which engine it came from? Do you feel more confident quoting 1 over the other?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:40:59.844000Z",
        "message": "No. I feel the same."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:41:03.994000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate your honesty, Thinking back over the past year or so, has anything changed about how often you use DuckDuckGo or Google? Any shifts in your habits even small ones?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:41:15.114000Z",
        "message": "I use DuckDuckGo mostly now. I used to use Google a long time ago, but I like dot dot gov. It's newer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:41:22.924000Z",
        "message": "That's a neat shift, moving mostly to DuckDuckGo, because it feels newer and and you like it. Was there a particular moment or or reason that you to switch away from Google, or did it happen gradually?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:41:36.154000Z",
        "message": "No."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:41:38.154000Z",
        "message": "Crystal clear. Before we wrap up, is there anything you wish DuckDuckGo or Google could do better or any features you wish they had? Anything missing from your ideal answer engine?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:41:49.784000Z",
        "message": "No. They're doing a pretty good job."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:41:51.914000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing your thoughts. Perfect. So thanks for sharing your experiences and and stories with me. Before we end, how was chatting with an AI moderator today? Any thoughts about the experience itself?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:42:03.124000Z",
        "message": "I like I like it. You feel like a real person."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73a05d92fc234fc5a3940dc70",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:42:09.254000Z",
        "message": "That's really nice to hear. Thanks for saying that. You've been super helpful. You can hang up the call whenever you'd like."
      }
