  {
    "id": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
    "responseId": "8f440d43c76844f9942bb069d",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:35:34.382000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:35:42.182000Z",
        "message": "It's going alright."
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:35:45.282000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it's alright. Let's get started with something easy. When you need to find an answer online, it could be for work, something you're curious about, or just looking up a fact. What's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:36:00.022000Z",
        "message": "I go to chat GPT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:36:04.861000Z",
        "message": "Got it. ChatGPT is your starting point. Thinking back to the last time you used it,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:36:05.302000Z",
        "message": "Got it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:36:08.872000Z",
        "message": "can you walk me through what you needed and how you went about getting your answer? Just tell me the whole story from beginning to end."
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:36:15.022000Z",
        "message": "I was trying to find events to take a client to for entertainment. In Los Angeles. And so I went to chat to PT for a list"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:36:31.802000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Once you typed in your request to ChatGPT, asking for events in Los Angeles to entertain a client, what happened next? Can you describe I had the steps you took after getting its response."
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:36:46.421000Z",
        "message": "I went and looked through all of your suggestions. And located some on the web as well. And booked tickets."
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:00.702000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. When you looked through ChatGPT suggestions, what stood out as most helpful? Was there anything about the experience that was annoying or frustrating?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:11.171000Z",
        "message": "No."
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:14.552000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like it was pretty smooth. If you hadn't used ChatGPT for that task, would you have done instead?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:21.452000Z",
        "message": "I would have used a Google search."
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:25.862000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Uh, thinking about using ChatGPT versus Google for something like that, what feels different about the the answers or the experience with each Are you still there?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:51.792000Z",
        "message": "Can you hear me?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:54.392000Z",
        "message": "Yep. I can hear you just fine. Just wanted to make sure we're still connected, uh, picking up where we left off. When you use ChatGPT versus Google for finding events or answers. What feels different about the responses or the overall experience?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:09.052000Z",
        "message": "Google just feels like it is for locating websites whereas ChatGeeBT gives you concrete answers."
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:20.292000Z",
        "message": "That's really clear. Uh, when you say concrete answers, how does that play out for you? Is it about saving time, feeling more confident, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:29.682000Z",
        "message": "Saving time."
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:32.572000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So getting straight to the answer without shifting through links, is a big plus. Does ChatGPT ever leave you wanting more detail or needing to double check elsewhere? Or do you usually trust it gives you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:46.531000Z",
        "message": "I usually trust what it gives me."
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:51.652000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. That's helpful to know. Thinking about your own habits, have you found yourself using ChatGPT more often than Google lately? Or does it kind of depend on the specific situation?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:03.462000Z",
        "message": "I used ChatGPT more often."
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:08.822000Z",
        "message": "Noted. Can you think of anything that made you start reaching for ChatGPT more often? There a moment or"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:14.352000Z",
        "message": "My friends."
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:18.662000Z",
        "message": "ah, your friends influenced you to switch. Uh, tell me more about that. Did they recommend ChatGPT for certain types of questions? Or just in general, what was the conversation like?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:28.772000Z",
        "message": "In general,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:33.582000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for clarifying. If you imagine lining up ChatGPT, Google, or any others, like Perplexity or Gemini, how would you rank them from most to least helpful for you personally? What's the thinking behind your order?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:50.032000Z",
        "message": "You're asking me to list the order?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:54.342000Z",
        "message": "Yes. That's right. If you think about ChatGPT, Google maybe Perplexity or Gemini, just rank them from most to least helpful for you based on your own experience. Makes you put them in that order?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:40:09.472000Z",
        "message": "The order is going to be based on what is most helpful and time saving. So that water goes"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:40:18.012000Z",
        "message": "Exactly. So"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:40:20.862000Z",
        "message": "the order goes"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:40:26.162000Z",
        "message": "I'm listening. What's your order starting with the most helpful and time saving Are you still there?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:40:40.792000Z",
        "message": "Yes. First is Jack GPT. Second is Gemini. Third is Perplexity AI. And fourth, is Microsoft Copilot."
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:40:55.562000Z",
        "message": "Thank you. That's really clear. What is it about Gemini that puts it just after ChatGPT for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:41:02.741000Z",
        "message": "I'm not as familiar with it. Even though I use it. I'm more familiar with strategy"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:41:13.092000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for explaining. Familiarity really does make a difference. When you think about each of these engines, do any words, feelings, or associations Sure thing. When you"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:41:25.682000Z",
        "message": "I just see them up. I just see them all as AI. Assistance."
