        "message": "Chat GPT because it is the most common"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:41:55.612000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Familiarity and common use can feel reassuring. Looking back over the past year, has anything else changed about the way you look things up or decide which engine to use? Any habits, routines, or feelings that are different?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
