        "callId": "27e8682432024200bc2744bf6",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:42:12.292000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for being so direct. That's really helpful. Before we wrap up, how did this conversation feel for you? Compared to other interviews or surveys you've done? You're welcome to end the call. Whenever you'd like. And I appreciate your time today."
