        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:33.206000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. When you need answers online, maybe for a quick fact, advice, or solving a problem, what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:45.757000Z",
        "message": "I go to my assistant."
