        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:12.527000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So Llama 4 is part of your routine. Can you walk me through a recent time you needed to look something up? Used Llama 4? What was the question or task, and how did the process go from start to finish?"
