        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:29.637000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. When you were researching social research using LAMA 4, what exactly were you trying to find out? Can you tell me step by step how you interacted with Llama 4 during that process?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:46.277000Z",
        "message": "The interaction was positive."
