        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:53.447000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it was a positive experience. Uh, can you tell me what made it feel positive for you? For example, was it how quickly you got results? The the kind of information LamaFor provided, the way it explained things,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:01.586000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
