        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:05.087000Z",
        "message": "or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:06.827000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. The the amount of knowledge was really quality."
      },
      {
        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:13.137000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful to know. When you say the knowledge was really quality, can you give me an example? Maybe something Lama 4 answered, especially well or a detail it provided that stood out to you."
      },
      {
        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:25.797000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. We were talking about Euclid's elements."
      },
      {
        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:30.467000Z",
        "message": "Great example. When you asked Lama 4 about Euclid's elements, what kind of answer did you get? Did it give historical context, explain mathematical concepts, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
