        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:50.277000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like having historical context added a lot of value for you. Did Llama 4 provide sources, or did it feel trustworthy enough you didn't feel the need to check elsewhere?"
