        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:27.467000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. What makes LAMA 4 stand out from others you've tried, like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Google? Is there a specific strength or feeling you get using it that those other engines don't give you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
