        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:43.377000Z",
        "message": "Personal. Got it. Can you tell me more about what feels personal? Is it the way Llama 4 interacts with you, the tone of its responses, or maybe how it remembers what you've asked before?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
