        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:55.487000Z",
        "message": "The tone of the responses."
      },
      {
        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:59.197000Z",
        "message": "Really interesting. Thinking about the tone, how would you describe it? For example, does it feel friendly? More conversational, or something else that sets it apart from the others?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
