        "time": "2025-09-13T23:33:10.387000Z",
        "message": "Very friendly."
      },
      {
        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:33:13.717000Z",
        "message": "If you compare that to, say, Google or ChatGPT, how do their responses feel in in tone or personality? Is there anything missing there that you notice versus Llama 4?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:33:24.817000Z",
        "message": "I've tried Gemini or I tried ChubGbG, but right now, Meta AI on Lama 4 is, like, the best. To use."
      },
      {
        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:33:38.427000Z",
        "message": "Thank you. That's clear. When you think about using Gemini or ChatGPT, what about those experiences felt different? For example, in the kind of answers you got, how easy it was to ask follow-up questions or just how the conversation felt."
      },
      {
        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:33:53.957000Z",
        "message": "The conversation felt good. Yeah. I don't I don't mind using those even, but just feel like Lama 4 is more efficient and, um, better for me to understand is more more content."
      },
      {
        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:34:12.607000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. That's helpful. So Llama 4 feels more efficient. And offers more content that that's understandable for you. Can you think of a task or situation where you'd pick pick Gemini or ChatGPT instead? What would be the reason for reaching for those instead of Yama 4?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "aab8dad78c7546e6ae457176c",
        "index": 35,
