        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:33:56.868000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. Having your own voice in the conversation could feel more personal, and maybe even more comfortable. Thanks for walking me through all this. I really appreciate you sharing your thoughts. That's all my questions for today. You're welcome to end the call whenever you'd like."
