        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:37.795000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. So when you need to find an answer online, what's the very first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:44.906000Z",
        "message": "Check social media."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:48.426000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. Uh, can you walk me through how you go about that Like, which social media platform do you reach for first? And what's your process once you're there?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:59.386000Z",
        "message": "Whatever one's popular at the time and then just finding people that had big influences that could factor my decision."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:10.276000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So it sounds like which platform you use can shift over time depending on what's trending. Can you tell me about the last time you did this? What were you looking for? And how did you decide whose opinion mattered most?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:25.476000Z",
        "message": "Today, sneakers."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:30.056000Z",
        "message": "Nice. So walk me through the whole story. Starting with what got you interested in those sneakers today. How did you search? Who did you end up trusting? And what made their input feel valuable?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:42.996000Z",
        "message": "They were famous, and I needed new sneakers."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:47.246000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. When you saw recommendations from these famous folks, exactly made you feel confident in their opinions? Was it something about how they describe the sneakers or maybe just their reputation? Tell me a bit more about what"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:01.126000Z",
        "message": "The their reputation."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:05.186000Z",
        "message": "makes a sense. After seeing those recommendations, uh, on social media, do you usually do any follow-up searches? Maybe hit up Google or try an AI answer engine, or do you mostly stick with those influencer opinions?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:17.825000Z",
        "message": "Sometimes I try different things."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:22.816000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for that. Thinking about those times when you try something besides social media, like, Google, ChatGPT, Perplexity, or other answer engines can you remember a recent situation when you used 1 of those tools instead what did you need to find out, and what made you switch away from social media that time?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:42.155000Z",
        "message": "It's if it's very important social media is not always honest. So you gotta switch to, like, Google and look through new resources."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:52.456000Z",
        "message": "That's really insightful. Um, can you remember a specific time when you did that? Switch to Google because you needed"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:58.655000Z",
        "message": "Today."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:01.196000Z",
        "message": "great. Let's dig in a bit. What was the very important thing you needed answers about today that made you switch from social media to to Google? And what was your step by step process once you made that switch?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:16.306000Z",
        "message": "Just to do a lot of research, and that was about how many miles my car gets."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:25.116000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Starting from when you realized you needed to know your car's mileage, what did you type into Google first, and how did you decide which results or sites to trust once they popped up?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 21,
