        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:34:03.326000Z",
        "message": "Got it. That's helpful to know. If you had to recommend just 1 tool to a friend who wanted quick, reliable answers, would you pick, and what would you tell them about it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:34:17.756000Z",
        "message": "Google because I'd just be more familiar with it. I wouldn't have to explain as much."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1e86c901065401f9dde2e2bb",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:34:23.496000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Familiarity is huge. Looking back, would you say your habits for looking things up have changed much over the past year? Or have you pretty much stuck with the same tools and routines?"
