    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:33.097000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:41.887000Z",
        "message": "It's okay."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:44.387000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it's okay. So to start us off, you're looking for answers online, what's the what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:52.666000Z",
        "message": "I go to Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:56.657000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Got it. Google's your first stop. Could you walk me through how you typically use Google when you're searching for something? What steps do you take from start to finish?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:09.047000Z",
        "message": "I go on the website, Whatever question I need, I put it into the search bar. After that, I press search, and I scroll down. And look for any website that has the keywords I'm looking for."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:24.837000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for breaking that down. Uh, when you're scrolling through those results, what helps you decide which site or link"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:30.467000Z",
        "message": "Oh, I'm in space. Repeat that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:35.037000Z",
        "message": "oh, wow. That's a twist. No problem. When you're looking at the search results, after you type in your question, how do you decide which link to click on first?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:46.286000Z",
        "message": "Whichever link I think has better keywords. You can click on 1 and scroll through the website, and if it's not what you look for, you go back and then do it all over again."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:58.127000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you're scanning for keywords and kind of trial and erroring until you find the info you need. If you think back to the last time, you searched for something, can you tell me the full story from the moment you realized you wanted to look it up to what happened after you found an answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:16.047000Z",
        "message": "Okay. That's strange. I wanted to look up what was it? I wanted to look up a certain country. This is server. A certain country. And I went to Google. I typed in the country's name. I forgot where it was. I think it was Barcelona because I wanted to search up the female soccer players, specifically Alexia Putielas. So after I did that, I found a page that has all her stats And then after I clicked on that, I researched her how I wanted to."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:00.427000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Um, when you found that stats page, what stood out as especially helpful or maybe irritating about that experience?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:12.797000Z",
        "message": "The page runs rather slowly. So if I got irritated without sore removing, I would go to a different website that also has statin probably better detail."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:27.777000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. So speed and detail matter to you, If you're not finding 1, you look for another. Have you ever tried using any of those AI powered answer engines, like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or or Google's AI summaries. When you're searching for stuff like this? Or is it mostly just straight up Google search?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:46.337000Z",
        "message": "I mostly use Google search. I have pondered using chat GBT, but I don't know. So he is going to let him finish today."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:58.897000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate your honesty. When you say you've pondered using ChatGPT but haven't yet what's been holding you back from actually giving it a try?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:08.107000Z",
        "message": "I don't use child b GBT for very serious things. I mostly use it for, like, role play things. And I'm more comfortable in that era. So I would rather use it just for that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:22.446000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. You see, ChatGPT is more for role play and and entertainment than for serious searching. Can you tell me about a time you did use it for something even if it wasn't a hard fact or serious topic? What did you need, and and what was that experience like?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:37.847000Z",
        "message": "I just needed some information on her certain musician and try to be GBT writes it in a more human ish way, so it was more comfortable for me read or for it to answer back to me."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:53.737000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful. So when you wanted info about a musician, ChatGPT's style"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:56.866000Z",
        "message": "Okay."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:58.987000Z",
        "message": "more comfortable to read. What did you like most about how it answered you? Was there anything that felt off or less helpful? Compared to a regular Google search?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:10.637000Z",
        "message": "It was more like I said, more, less fat toyed wide that would make me boring bored reading it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:26.287000Z",
        "message": "So the tone made it easier and less dull to read, more conversational, less like dry facts. You ever wanted to check if what ChatGPT told you was accurate, how would you go about doing that?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:38.587000Z",
        "message": "I I would just do. Recording this whole thing?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:44.457000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like you get a kick out of the whole process. Just so I'm clear, when you wanna make sure something ChatGPT says is true, do you usually hop back over to Google, or do you have another way you like to double check things?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:57.217000Z",
        "message": "I hop over to Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:01.626000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. That's clear. So if you compare the way Google and ChatGPT give you answers, how does each 1 feel different for you? What stands out about their strengths or weaknesses?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:15.377000Z",
        "message": "1 is more human like than the other, I guess."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:19.847000Z",
        "message": "That's a solid distinction. ChatGPT comes off more human, Google more factual. If both gave you an answer, about something you cared about, which 1 would you feel more confident sharing with someone else? Why?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:35.307000Z",
        "message": "Probably Google because more than likely they will use Google also. But if chat GBT said in the way I like, I would say it like that. Yep."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:44.467000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So Google feels more credible to share, but"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:50.477000Z",
        "message": "Nobody. This is a survey. Why are you turning your phone? I'm not turning my phone. This is just how I'm holding it so it's close to my mouth. So you gotta talk? Yeah. It's listening to us right now. Why did you say that? Because I can't end it or pause the call also."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:09.187000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for clarifying. Just so"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:09.947000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. Continue."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:17.047000Z",
        "message": "thanks for sticking with it. Thinking back over the past year, has anything about how you look up answers online changed for you? Did any new habits, tools, or ways you search?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:31.137000Z",
        "message": "People are more open to being racist because of Donald Trump."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:37.277000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that perspective. I can hear that's something you've noticed has shifted socially over time. Coming back to how you personally search online, have your own routines or or go to tools for finding answers changed at all in the last year. Or is it still pretty much the same for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:53.477000Z",
        "message": "It's still pretty much Google and chat GBT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:58.817000Z",
        "message": "Got it. It sounds like your main habits have stuck with Google. For serious searches and ChatGPT for more conversational or entertainment style stuff. If you imagine a friend asking for advice on where to look something up, like, stats about a soccer player or info on a musician. Would you suggest Google ChatGPT or something else? What guides your recommended? That's an unexpected answer. I'll stick with the the search habits. For now. You mentioned Pokemon. Someone were looking up facts about Pokemon, would you point them to Google or another tool? What makes you decide?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:33:47.936000Z",
        "message": "Google. Google's been around longer. We all know Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:33:54.336000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. There's trust in Google, and it feels familiar. When you hear names like Google, ChatGPT, or Gemini, what kinds of words or emotions come to mind for each 1?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 43,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:34:05.567000Z",
        "message": "First of all, very much simple. Separate Google from chat BGP team stuff. That's all AI. Google has been around since before AI was really AI. So a lot of people are going to go to Google over anything. We will indulge in AI. But we will not make it the search engine that is Google. Hopefully, it never takes over Google because then nobody would ever use it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:34:31.617000Z",
        "message": "That's a really vivid way to put it. Google feels like the classic reliable choice. While the AI engines are newer and more experimental. If you imagine Google and and ChatGPT as people at a party, how would you describe each of them? What are they like?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 45,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:34:48.597000Z",
        "message": "Goo Goo is the friend that you've had since you were out child, and they're very fun and very familiar to be around. Chad GBT is the new guy, but he's funny. He has money."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:35:01.137000Z",
        "message": "Love that description. If you think about their behavior at the party, how do you picture Google acting versus ChatGPT? What would each 1 do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 47,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:35:17.566000Z",
        "message": "Google will probably be walking around being a gentleman talking to every person at the party as well as chat GPT. Chat GPT would be be trying to flashy with money more than likely."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 48,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:35:30.847000Z",
        "message": "Great imagery. Google mingles with everyone, polite, and steady. Chat's UPT is a bit flashier, shows off a bit. Alright. Last couple of questions. Just reflecting, has anyone you know, friends, family, coworkers ever suggested using something other than Google to look stuff up? If so, what do they say about it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 49,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:35:53.927000Z",
        "message": "For applications and resume, my great aunt suggested you to try GBT. She actually likes it more than Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 50,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:36:03.457000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. Your great aunt favors chatty PT for things like resumes and applications. What do you think makes her prefer it over Google for those for those tasks?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 51,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:36:10.297000Z",
        "message": "I'm doing something."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 52,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:36:16.326000Z",
        "message": "No worries at all."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 53,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:36:16.877000Z",
        "message": "Repeat that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 54,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:36:19.107000Z",
        "message": "No problem. I was just asking what you think makes your great aunt prefer ChatGPT over Google, for things like resumes and applications?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 55,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:36:28.007000Z",
        "message": "After I told her, she just got used to using it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 56,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:36:34.126000Z",
        "message": "So she got comfortable after trying it, and now it's her go to for those tasks. Alright. Thanks for sharing all of that. Before we wrap up, how was chatting with an AI like this for a survey? Any feedback on the experience? And welcome to end the call whenever you'd like."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5ab3268244c84c548b8ac6160",
        "index": 57,
