    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:05.187000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:13.307000Z",
        "message": "Great."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:17.787000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. When you need an answer online, say you're curious about something, or need quick info, what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:26.467000Z",
        "message": "Need click info."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:29.797000Z",
        "message": "Got it. You're after quick answers. Walk me through what that looks like for you. When you want that fast info, what's the very first step you take?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:39.177000Z",
        "message": "I go and just use the AI and ask if they could search up this information. There's, like, Gemini. They're really easy."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:37:49.627000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing. So Gemini is your go to right now for asking questions and searching information. Can you tell me about the last time you used Gemini? What were you looking for? And how did the whole process go for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:03.086000Z",
        "message": "I was looking for a recipe on how to cook a roast in Instant Pot. I just asked for recipes that are good, and they gave me suggestions."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:12.456000Z",
        "message": "That's a classic use case. Thinking back to that moment, about using Gemini? Felt the most helpful or satisfying And was there anything annoying or confusing in the process?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:24.347000Z",
        "message": "It got me the answers I needed right quick, and there was nothing confusing."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:29.327000Z",
        "message": "Sounds smooth. When Gemini gave you those recipe suggestions, did you check elsewhere to compare, or did you feel confident enough to just go with what Gemini presented?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:40.077000Z",
        "message": "I felt confident to not to go with it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:45.247000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. You felt confident enough not to double check. What is it about Gemini that gives you that sense of trust or confidence with the answers it provides?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:54.397000Z",
        "message": "Always give me quality answers."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:38:58.206000Z",
        "message": "That's clear. When you've used other engines besides Gemini, say ChatGPT, Perplexity, or even Google's AI features? What's been different about the experience? Anything stand out? In terms of how helpful, fast, or trustworthy they feel?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:12.857000Z",
        "message": "There's helpful. And gives me good answers."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:19.607000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like you find them generally helpful as well. Do you notice any differences in how the answers feel between Gemini and something like ChatGPT or Google AI? For example, do they give you more details or is the tone different? Or maybe the way they show sources?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:36.687000Z",
        "message": "Gemini gives me more information."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:39:40.307000Z",
        "message": "Good to know."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5a46b723b7534f1b841ffcaff",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
