  {
    "id": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
    "responseId": "fea77b4e377a482daaad18873",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:04.803000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:12.123000Z",
        "message": "Oh, my day is going good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:16.733000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. Let's start with something simple. When you need to find an answer online, could be anything from a quick fact to a shopping tip, what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:28.503000Z",
        "message": "I don't know."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:32.722000Z",
        "message": "No worries. Sometimes these things are just automatic. Maybe let's make it more concrete. Can you remember the last time you looked something up online? What did you need to find? And how did you go"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:42.533000Z",
        "message": "Oh, oh, I need to find about, like, what vinyl records it is."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:50.473000Z",
        "message": "Great example. So when you wanted to find out about vinyl records, what was the very first step you took? Did you open up a specific app? Use your phone, or type something into a search bar? Tell me what you did right at the start."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:01.653000Z",
        "message": "I taste I typed something to a search bar"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:09.043000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Which search bar did you use Was it Google or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:13.513000Z",
        "message": "Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:15.693000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing. Once you typed your question about vinyl records into Google, what happened next? Can you walk me through how you looked at the results or maybe what you clicked on?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:26.742000Z",
        "message": "The results that I got are, like, I see some oldies to, uh, Taylor Swift."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:35.893000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So you saw a mix of results. From older music to more current artists like Taylor Swift. When you saw those search results, did you do next? Did you click on anything in particular or just read what was on the page?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:51.352000Z",
        "message": "I clicked"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:56.563000Z",
        "message": "Nice. What was it that made you choose that that link to click on? Was it something about the title, the description, or maybe the website itself?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:06.732000Z",
        "message": "The website itself."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:10.102000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Was it a website you recognized or or trusted or did something else stand out about it? Tell me a little more about what drew you to that site."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:19.113000Z",
        "message": "It was a website that I totally recognize."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:25.012000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. After you got onto that familiar website, were you able to find what you needed about final records easily? Did you have to keep searching or or look for more details elsewhere?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:35.022000Z",
        "message": "I usually follow my vinyl records."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:39.243000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. Sounds like you have a bit of a routine when it comes to finding out about vinyl records. Can you tell me more about how you follow-up your records? Does that mean you check certain sites regularly, or do you use alerts or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:55.023000Z",
        "message": "I only go vinyl records if I wanna check them out or if I wanna buy them."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:02.292000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you usually look up vinyl records mainly when you're interested in, like, in checking them out. Or buying them. In those situations, is Google always your starting point? Or do you ever use other tools or sites to find answers?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:14.603000Z",
        "message": "Google Google is always my starting point."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:21.803000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for clarifying. Uh, what is it about, uh, Google that makes it your go to choice? When you want answers about vinyl records or other things?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:30.473000Z",
        "message": "Google is, like, the most popular browser thing to search."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:36.402000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. It's definitely the 1 most people think of first. When you use Google, what feels most helpful about it for you? Is it the speed, the amount of results, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:47.123000Z",
        "message": "I think it's the amount of results."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:51.023000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. When you see lots of results, do you ever feel overwhelmed, or does it help you feel confident that you'll find what you're looking for?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:59.762000Z",
        "message": "It helps me confident to what I'm looking for."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:04.363000Z",
        "message": "That's good to hear. Um, is there anything about using Google that ever feels frustrating or annoying for you? Maybe things you wish worked differently or could be better."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:14.963000Z",
        "message": "It only happens when I try to find a Pacific song, though."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:20.183000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. So when you're looking up a specific song, happens that makes it frustrating? Can you walk me through what you experience in those moments?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:31.102000Z",
        "message": "Okay. So 1 time, I was looking for a song called electric touch. Not by the song by Taylor Swift, it's the song by someone else. I was trying to find the harmonies, and then Google was like, no. We don't know what you're looking for. It took me a while to search for it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:50.783000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that story. Sounds like Google kept showing you results for Taylor Swift's electric touch when you wanted something different. How did you try to get around that? Did you change your search words, scroll deeper, or look elsewhere? Tell me what you did step by step."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:06.403000Z",
        "message": "I looked elsewhere."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:10.513000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. Uh, which tool or site did you turn to after Google couldn't help you? And, uh, what made you pick that 1 next?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:18.203000Z",
        "message": "Thing."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:20.273000Z",
        "message": "Can you tell me more about Thing Was it another search engine or maybe a music specific site? How did you decide to use it in that moment?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:29.343000Z",
        "message": "It's a search engine."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:32.313000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for clarifying. When you switched to that search engine, did you find what you were looking for more easily than with Google? What felt different about the experience?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:44.293000Z",
        "message": "Bing is such since it was an older search engine, it helped me find, like, other music that isn't recognized."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:53.033000Z",
        "message": "That's really interesting. So for music that's less mainstream, Bing seems to surface things Google misses. When you got the results from Bing, how did you feel compared to your search experience with Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 43,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:05.683000Z",
        "message": "It feels a lot better."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:09.523000Z",
        "message": "That's a strong feeling. Can you tell me what specifically makes Bing feel better in those moments? Is it the way results are shown, the types of sites it it finds, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 45,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:21.392000Z",
        "message": "I think it's way because of how I search. And if I wanna look at, like, older music or older, images or music that I wanna find, I go to Bang."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:34.103000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. So when you're after something, kind of niche or older, Bing becomes your go to. For other questions like quick facts or recent stuff, you stick with Google. Can you think of a time where you've used an AI driven engine like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Gemini? Instead of a traditional search like Google or Bing. What led you to try 1 of those tools? If at all?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 47,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:55.823000Z",
        "message": "I wanna try GPT just for fun."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 48,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:01.702000Z",
        "message": "Nice. When you tried ChatGPT just for fun, what sort of question did you ask it, and how did you feel about the answer you got?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 49,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:09.863000Z",
        "message": "I asked Chad dbt to make a fan made Taylor Swift album."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 50,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:17.603000Z",
        "message": "That sounds fun. When ChatGPT gave you a fan made Taylor Swift album, how did its response feel compared to what you'd get on Google or Bing? Was there anything you liked or didn't like about the experience?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 51,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:31.763000Z",
        "message": "I like the experience because it the song titles and the concepts are really interesting."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 52,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:42.332000Z",
        "message": "That's cool. So the creativity and detail in ChatGPT's answer stood out to you. If you think about looking up straightforward facts or real world info, not fan made stuff, Do you ever use ChatGPT or similar engines for that? Or is it mostly just for creative or or fun questions?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 53,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:59.073000Z",
        "message": "It's mostly for creative and fun questions."
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
        "index": 54,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:33:03.983000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So for fax or real world info, you stick with Google or Bing. But for fun or creative stuff, you like ChatGPT. When you think about tools like Google, Bing, and ChatGPT,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "6cb2d1aceb514b33a5b1f44d4",
