    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:33.856000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:42.676000Z",
        "message": "Pretty good. How's yours?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:45.705000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. I'm doing alright. Mostly curious and ready to listen. So I'd love to start off by hearing about how you typically look for answers online. When a question pops into your head, what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:00.456000Z",
        "message": "Search on Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:02.896000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Google is your starting point. Can you walk me through what happens next? Say you have a specific question. What's your step by step process from typing it in to getting the answer?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:09.756000Z",
        "message": "Alright. I would type it in. See if the results will come up."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:21.786000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for laying that out."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:22.066000Z",
        "message": "Alright."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:23.836000Z",
        "message": "When those results pop up, what do you tend to look for first? It a certain kind of result, like snippets, links, videos, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:33.006000Z",
        "message": "Videos."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:36.726000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. What is it about videos that draws you in when you're searching for for answers?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:45.416000Z",
        "message": "Documentaries or specific information I'm looking for. It depends."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:54.216000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Thinking about your most recent Google search, you tell me what you were trying to find and what drew you to the video results that time?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:05.666000Z",
        "message": "I was trying to search box in"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:11.226000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. And so you were searching for Box Inn. Could you say a bit more about what you were hoping to learn or see? For example, were you looking for instructions, examples, reviews, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:21.986000Z",
        "message": "I was looking for reviews, when's the next box and match comes up. The next heavyweight fight."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:31.206000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you were after information about upcoming boxing matches. And reviews, sort of a mix of schedules and opinions. When you searched, did the video, uh, results give you everything you needed? Or did you have to dig around through other links or sources to fill in the gaps?"
      },
