      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:12.126000Z",
        "message": "I caught that you mentioned both using chat boxes and possibly talking over the phone. Just so I'm clear, when you search for answers, do you mostly type into Google's search box, or do you also use voice search or chat based AI tools sometimes?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:26.286000Z",
        "message": "I use both about the same pens. Sometimes they don't recognize my voice that good. I'm not speaking fair enough."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:40.776000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for explaining. When you use voice search and it doesn't pick up what your saying clearly, what do you usually do next? Do you repeat yourself, switch to typing, or try a different tool?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
