        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:57.836000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful to know. So when typing gets you the answer more reliably, do you ever try other tools? Like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Gemini for answers? Or does it mostly stick with Google for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 27,
