        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:11.786000Z",
        "message": "Mostly Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:14.626000Z",
        "message": "Understood. What is it about Google that keeps it your main choice? Instead of those other engines?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:20.486000Z",
        "message": "It's easy access. It's I'm used to it. Been using it for a long time."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:26.296000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Familiarity goes a long way. If you think back, has there ever been a situation recently where you tried getting answers? From another engine, like ChatGPT or something? And if so, what led you to switch that time?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:42.016000Z",
        "message": "Maybe I was on a different platform. I was on social media. I used the Instagram chat The chat box has the has that service, I believe."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:54.716000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. You used a chat feature on Instagram when you were already on that platform. Can you tell me about what kind of question or information you were looking for in that moment and how it felt compared to searching on Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:14.226000Z",
        "message": "The it's different. I like Google better. They got the m e t a melted oil, the the, uh, what is it called? Chat."
