        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:31.926000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. Yes. Yeah, I tried to meta AI. I use in in Instagram. It works good too."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:48.426000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for confirming. I'm thinking about when you used Meta AI. In Instagram, what sort of things do you usually ask it? Is there anything it does a little better or worse than Google in your experience?"
