      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:30.956000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So for you having access to the broad web, and lots of info is a big advantage with Google over tools inside apps like Instagram. Thinking about other engines, ChatGPT, Perplexity, Gemini,"
