        "index": 48,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:31:59.616000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate you sharing that. Google and Meta AI cover what you need. If you imagine a feature or improvement in any search engine or AI tool that could make things even easier for you, What comes to mind?"
