        "index": 50,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:19.916000Z",
        "message": "Fair enough. Uh, sometimes it's hard to think of what's missing. When things work well. And before we wrap, you find an answer you're confident in, do you ever share it with someone else? If so, is there a specific tools answer you'll quote or send or do you just grab whatever works?"
      },
