        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 51,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:39.536000Z",
        "message": "Usually, whatever works. Or if I have any resources around me, I use the tools."
      },
      {
        "callId": "3b300624332347119eddf2a07",
        "index": 52,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:32:46.686000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for that. Sounds like it's about convenience and, uh, what's handy in the moment. Last quick question. Thinking back over the past year, has anything changed about how often where you look things up online? Or does it feel pretty much the same to you?"
      },
      {
