    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:57.167000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:05.366000Z",
        "message": "Very good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:08.317000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. Start with something simple. When you need answers online, what's what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:16.397000Z",
        "message": "I go to chat GPT. On Microsoft, Copilot, and search up the answers that I need in AI. And they gave me the answers that I need."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:30.737000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you reach for ChatGPT often through Copilot. For answers. Can you walk me through the last time you did that? What were you looking for? And how did you go about it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:42.647000Z",
        "message": "The last time I did that, I was looking for something work related. Done, uh, for my construction business. I was looking up new ideas to come up with for, my planning and modeling. And they gave me new ideas to work with, and I decided to use them. And the came out wonderful."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:05.126000Z",
        "message": "Love hearing a real story like that. Could you walk me through each step of that experience? Starting with what led you to use Copilot and ChatGPT for those new construction ideas. What did you type in? What did the answers look like? And how did you decide to to run with them?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:23.497000Z",
        "message": "Well, let me to use it. I went to a Google search and engine, and I searched up different AI sites. And I came across the different ones, comparing them using each last 1. And Microsoft Copilot was the best choice for me, which 1 I prefer. And the first step I did, I searched up. It like, similar things dealing with the idea that I was already had in mind. And they gave me more ideas that relate to the idea that I had in mind. So I just put them together and made collaboration with that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:03.437000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for laying out those steps. When you saw Copilot's answers, what made them stand out? Compared to what you'd seen from other engines or even from Google? Was it something about the way that the answers looked, how fast they arrived, the detail, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:18.317000Z",
        "message": "They the answers are very fast. It was hot. Authentic the answer was, how human based the answer was. Instead of a AI program it gave, like, human writing."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:32.087000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful. When you say the answers felt authentic, and human based, can you tell me more about what that looked like? Was it the way the text was written, uh, the suggestions it made, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:44.037000Z",
        "message": "Yes. It was both the way to text was written and the suggestions. It's like answers you will get if you ask the human that like, a real answer you'll get if you ask a human that question."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:59.366000Z",
        "message": "Really clear description. Thanks. Um, was there anything about experience with Copilot that felt less helpful or was annoying to you, even just a little?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:08.747000Z",
        "message": "Nothing at all. It was very simple and easy, and I enjoyed it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:14.397000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. If Copilot wasn't available for some reason, what would you have done instead to get those answers for your business?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:23.246000Z",
        "message": "I probably would have tried a new method. Or gather the my team ideas and put them together and collaborated with that if the AI didn't work."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:38.356000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you tap into your team's input more directly. Thinking back, have you ever compared Copilot's answers to ones you might get from ChatGPT itself, Perplexity, or Google's own AI for the same kind of question. If so, how did those experiences feel different for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:56.547000Z",
        "message": "Yes. I did. And they feel different about a different axis each last 1 provided in their own way. All of them was very helpful, but I was looking for a more, like, human authentic more like not so hey. I'm not so robot. And Microsoft Copilot gave that to me."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:17.657000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for clarifying what you value. If you lined up Copilot, ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Google's AI, just in terms of how helpful the answers feel for your work, how would you rank them from most to least helpful? And what's the main reason for your top pick?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:35.587000Z",
        "message": "My topic will be Marcus Microsoft Copilot, then second will be ChatGPT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:43.317000Z",
        "message": "And"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:43.717000Z",
        "message": "Third will be"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:49.657000Z",
        "message": "did you mean third would be Google AI and fourth would be Perplexity, or is Perplexity somewhere else in your ranking? What puts Copilot above the others for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:00.957000Z",
        "message": "Opala is very helpful for me. It gave me it give me ideas, summarize, writing, coding. Everything I need in 1. It's very helpful, and I don't have to do a lot to deal with it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:16.716000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for explaining that. When you think about Copilot as a brand, what words or qualities come to mind? If Copilot was a person at a party, how would you describe them?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:30.797000Z",
        "message": "Exciting. Authentic, modern, innovative, creative, trustworthy, cooperative, personalized"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:49.187000Z",
        "message": "Great list. And if you compare that to Google's answer engine, what words or qualities come up for Google? If Google was a person at the same party, what are they like?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:01.637000Z",
        "message": "Autemic. Exciting, creative. Driven, technology advanced, AI advanced,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:15.977000Z",
        "message": "I hear a lot of positive words for both. When it comes to trust, like when you share an answer with someone in your business or team, do you feel more confident quoting Copilot's answer or Google's? What makes you lean 1 way or the other?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:31.357000Z",
        "message": "I feel more confident in either or because I feel like either or is the right answer choice for me. Both of them gives you very descriptive answer as a choice that you can use. So I will say both."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:49.577000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate your honesty. Looking back over the past year, has anything changed in how you look things up? Online? Have you shifted to using Copilot or or other AI tools more often? Or do you still stick with your previous habits? What triggered any changes you've noticed?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:06.566000Z",
        "message": "Yes. I started using AI tools more At first, I wasn't trusting it, but then I started getting into it more. And I started using AI tools more, and that became very effective and efficient to my life and very helpful, making it easier."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:24.447000Z",
        "message": "Interesting shift. Can you remember a specific moment or or situation when you first started trusting AI tools enough to use them instead of your old search methods? What happened that convinced you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:28:36.237000Z",
        "message": "When I was in my business, when I had end up using it, I thought the answer was wrong that they was giving me, but I said I allowed, and it actually was right. And they actually loved the performance that I that I did. The AI had give given me the ideas to do. So that's why I started trusting him more, giving him more hope, and then I just start building into it. Well, yeah."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:07.207000Z",
        "message": "Love the story. Real world success builds trust, for sure. Wrapping up here, is there anything you wish AI Answer engines like Copilot, ChatGPT, or others could do for you? That they don't do yet. Anything that would make them"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:21.247000Z",
        "message": "Okay. Nothing at all. I love everything that they do. I love everything that they provide, the features, the answers, the details. The supporting details, all of that. I love all that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:36.697000Z",
        "message": "That's great to hear you're satisfied. Last quick question. How did it feel talking about your experiences with AI today? Anything you'd like to add before we finish up?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:29:47.217000Z",
        "message": "It actually felt great expressing how I feel about AI. I will highly recommend AI to everyone if they want a more simple life, more efficient, effective life. If they need help with anything, go to AI."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:05.677000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing your story and thoughts so openly. I really enjoyed hearing your perspective. You're all set and can end the call whenever you'd like. Have a great rest of your day."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9164cdf74c964c1c9e35e1af9",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:30:16.827000Z",
        "message": "Yes, sir."
      }
