  {
    "id": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
    "responseId": "64156d8941804dc382285a4e6",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:42.397000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:51.097000Z",
        "message": "Day is going fine."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:54.027000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. Let's start with something simple. When you need answers online, what's, like, the very first thing you you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:02.677000Z",
        "message": "Google,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:07.236000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Google's your first stop. Can you walk me through your typical process when you look something up with Google? Just tell me step by step what you do."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:16.267000Z",
        "message": "I open up the browser, which is Google and I do go to the search bar. And I type in what I'm searching for. Whether it be a recipe, weather, or anything that I need information on. And then I look at the results and see which results that I want to use."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:36.127000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for laying that out. When you're scanning those results, is there anything particular you look for that helps you decide which link to click on?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:45.577000Z",
        "message": "Usually, I choose the between the first 3 because they're seem to be the most popular. But I do search through all of them to see which ones that are gonna give me the precise answer that I want. Whether it be a forecast for the week or a"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:58.946000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:01.927000Z",
        "message": "simple answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:04.647000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for clarifying. Thinking about your last search, can you tell me the full story? Start with what you needed, then walk me through every step, including what helped and anything that annoyed you."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:18.727000Z",
        "message": "My last search was today. And I was searching on the Philippines Mount Puntumo, And when did that occur? What year, and what were the results from it. And I did get what I needed. I found the year, the date, and the time when that occurred and what it did"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:47.437000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. For that search, what part of using Google felt most helpful to you? Was there anything about it that you found annoying or or wished was better?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:56.987000Z",
        "message": "No. Nothing at all."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:00.027000Z",
        "message": "Alright. Sounds like a smooth"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:00.377000Z",
        "message": "The only thing yes. So with the screens."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:06.186000Z",
        "message": "tell me more about that. What about the screen stood out? Was it something with how the results appeared or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:13.467000Z",
        "message": "Everything was fine because it was laid out You can choose. They even have videos if you wanna watch the video. Or you can read the information. Um, I prefer the video because you get more visual."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:29.557000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful to know. So having both videos and written info is useful for you, and you lean toward watching videos for certain topics. If Google wasn't available, do you think you would have done instead? To get that information?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:44.477000Z",
        "message": "I would just actually go to the main search Google wasn't available, and search and find out what the I guess, the results will be by typing it in up the URL bar."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:02.696000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you try another way to reach similar info. Maybe directly typing in a site or using another search, just checking. Do you ever use other tools or or answer engines like ChatGPT, Perplexity, Gemini, or anything besides Google for getting answers?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:17.997000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. I can use Alexa, which will give me a a voice results without the video."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:26.637000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:27.207000Z",
        "message": "And yeah."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:33.047000Z",
        "message": "You mentioned Alexa for voice answers. Can you think of a time you chose Alexa instead of Google? Was the situation, and what made you pick Alexa that time?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:42.807000Z",
        "message": "I was in the kitchen cooking, and the Alexa device is right downstairs. And I just wanted to clarify a recipe that I was working with and make sure I had all the ingredients and I just asked Alexa for what I was cooking for the ingredients to make sure I had them all"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:04.867000Z",
        "message": "That's a great example. What did you find most helpful about using Alexa for that? And was there anything about the experience that didn't quite work for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:15.417000Z",
        "message": "Everything worked fine. As far as using Amexa, it was quick, easy, and straightforward. I just didn't remember all the ingredients, but Alexa gave me all the ones I needed. Plus some extra."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:30.857000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like convenience and speed really stand out for you there. If you compare how you feel using Google versus Alexa, for these kinds of quick searches, does 1 feel more reliable or or satisfying than the other? Or do you see them as as pretty similar just for different situations?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:48.167000Z",
        "message": "Basically, Alexa is a voice where Google you know, you have to be at the computer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:58.207000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:58.286000Z",
        "message": "All you do is yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:04.536000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So really, depends on what you're doing and where you are. If you think about Google, ChatGPT, and Alexa as people at a party, who would each of them, just go with whatever pops into your head."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:17.147000Z",
        "message": "Well, if I was a party, I'd probably use Google because I have to type it in because it it could be a lot of noise. And with Alexa, it could pick up a lot of background noise."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:28.267000Z",
        "message": "Nice way of putting it. So Google's kind of the reliable guest who doesn't mind the chaos. While Alexa might struggle to hear through the party noise When you think about Google ChatGPT and Alexa, there certain words or feelings that come to mind with each? Whatever you associate with them."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:47.987000Z",
        "message": "As far as Google, you have to type in precisely what you want. With Alexa, you can your voice. And if you don't get the right answer, you can give it a more defined voice Question?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:06.757000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. Uh, it sounds like both need clear directions. But you adjust depending on whether it's typing or talking. When you share an answer, found with someone"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:14.767000Z",
        "message": "Correct."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:16.887000Z",
        "message": "thanks for clarifying. Thinking back, has anything changed plain changed about how you look things up? Compared to, say, a year ago? Any habits, favorites, or trust levels shifted at all?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:32.376000Z",
        "message": "Everything seems to be the same. I I can really can't tell any difference."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:37.147000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Thanks for sharing that. Before we wrap up, anything you wish these engines or tools could do that they don't? Right now? Any wish list features or things you secretly want them to improve?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:54.957000Z",
        "message": "Maybe give you a follow-up."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:58.927000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. Like, having the"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 43,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:59.847000Z",
        "message": "I guess, your email yeah. A a follow-up. In case if there's any more information that can be provided that's become new,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:13.577000Z",
        "message": "Got it. A kind of update or or notification. If new info comes out on a topic you've searched."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 45,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:17.857000Z",
        "message": "Yeah."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:19.207000Z",
        "message": "Sounds super useful. For talking through all this with me. That's all I need."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 47,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:20.367000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "fdb7031479044e60a41f11757",
        "index": 48,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:23.977000Z",
        "message": "Today. How did you find chatting with an AI interviewer? And you're free to end the call whenever you'd like."
