  {
    "id": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
    "responseId": "f50ac8aa7d694c5d95639f1f2",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:09.247000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:17.207000Z",
        "message": "Good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:19.976000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. Let's jump in. When you need answers online, what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:26.547000Z",
        "message": "I go to chat. GPT or Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:30.497000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you typically reach for either ChatGPT or Google. Tell me about the last time you looked something up using 1 of those What did you need? And which tool did you pick first?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:40.587000Z",
        "message": "I was looking up sweepstakes casinos and which ones had the best sign up deals. And yeah, I used ChatGPT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:52.157000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing. Walk me through that moment. What made you decide to use ChatGPT first for that? What did you do step by step once you got there?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:02.337000Z",
        "message": "I googled most reputable sweepstakes casinos or sorry. I ChatGBT'd the information. And then I it gave me a a layout of all of the sweeps casinos with the most Trustpilot reviews that are positive. And I utilized that to make my decision."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:32.747000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. When you got that answer from ChatGPT, what stood out to you as especially helpful or maybe not so helpful? In the way it presented the info."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:45.406000Z",
        "message": "I I don't know. I feel like maybe it was a shorter list than I expected. And I eventually had to go through it again."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:58.707000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like you were hoping for a bit more depth Can you tell me more about what you did after seeing that shorter list? You look things up elsewhere, tweak your question, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:11.177000Z",
        "message": "Uh, just asked for more, like, a a continued list, and it gave me a continued list."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:20.437000Z",
        "message": "So you kept the conversation going with ChatGPT. And asked for a longer list. What was that like?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:25.687000Z",
        "message": "Yep. It was pretty easy."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:28.387000Z",
        "message": "Thank Sounds straightforward. Um, when you got that continued list, did you feel confident in the info, or did you double check anywhere else? Before deciding?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:42.366000Z",
        "message": "I have faith in Chad GBT. It seemed pretty, intricate."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:50.097000Z",
        "message": "Great. So it sounds like ChatGPT earned your trust for this task. Thinking back, what specific part of its answer or style gave you that that feeling of confidence?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:01.447000Z",
        "message": "And just how he, uh, portrayed the or like, helped me visualize data with, uh, charts and, uh, bullet points?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:14.727000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. Seeing things visualized really helps. Now if you hadn't used ChatGPT for this, what would you have done instead?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:22.417000Z",
        "message": "I probably would have gone to Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:25.947000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Thinking about using Google for something like this. How do the results feel different compared to what you get from ChatGPT?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:35.027000Z",
        "message": "I feel like on Google, it's more sponsored, uh, and I don't feel like ChatGPT really has, like, that sponsorship going on. So it's it's less biased."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:48.057000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. The sponsorship and bias stand out for you. When you're deciding which engine to use, does this feeling about bias and sponsorship ever tip your choice? Can you think of a moment when it made you pick ChatGPT over Google specifically?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:05.377000Z",
        "message": "Let's typically why I picked ChatGPT over Google. Like, as far as even Gemini, like, because I don't trust that it's not behind some type of pay for play."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:17.027000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. It sounds like trust and transparency are big drivers for you. If you line up ChatGPT, Google, and Gemini in terms of how much you trust their answers, what's the order for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:32.276000Z",
        "message": "What were the 3?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:34.657000Z",
        "message": "The 3 are ChatGPT, Google, and Gemini. How would you rank them from most trustworthy to least in your eyes?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:41.977000Z",
        "message": "Probably, uh, ChatGBT, Gemini, then Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:47.707000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate your ranking. Thinking about each 1 for a second. If they were people at a party, what kind of personality would you say ChatGPT has, and how does that compare to Gemini or Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:59.706000Z",
        "message": "Chatty bitty would probably be, like, a stuck up arrogance overly confident guy. And then Google would be like, like that life to party, like, but like, you know, accepting bribes type person, like a politician. And then Gemini would be like down to earth chill person."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:32.007000Z",
        "message": "Love those descriptions. When you get an answer that you want to share with someone else, family, friends, coworkers whose response feels most credible, to quote. Is it ChatGPT, Gemini, or Google? What makes that 1 feel safer?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:50.317000Z",
        "message": "ChatGPT just because of you know, a lot of the you know, that's how Google made their mint was off of advertisement and accepting money from companies to boost their listing. And, I mean, I know there's always, like, SEO, you know, search engine optimization, but you know, mostly, it's, uh, like, the top 5 to 10 items depending on what you're searching are usually, paid for."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:24.067000Z",
        "message": "That's really insightful. Um, looking back over the past year or so, has anything changed in your habits for looking things up? Frequency, which tool you pick first or how much you trust different engines. Tell me about any shift you've noticed."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:38.817000Z",
        "message": "You know, I've been shifting a lot of my AI, ML, stuff to my local LLM. And, also, I've been utilizing things like the paid subscriptions to Perplexity and ChatGBT more often."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:58.887000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. That's a big change. What sparked that move to local LLMs and paid subscriptions like Perplexity and ChatGPT? Any story that's"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:06.907000Z",
        "message": "Trust."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:09.597000Z",
        "message": "got it. Trust seems like your North Star here. When you use Perplexity, how does the experience or the answers compare to what you get from ChatGPT or Google? What stands out to you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:24.197000Z",
        "message": "I well, I just started I was accepted to a pro plan for free for a year and then also their Comet browser. So I'm just kind of getting to know Perplexity more, uh, where it seems like a really good, uh, AI, like, gonna be able to integrate with our everyday lives and just doing normal things. I would typically take more it's gonna try to take the more mundane tedious, monotonous work out of my life."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:58.806000Z",
        "message": "That's really interesting. So Perplexity feels like it could automate some of those tedious everyday tasks for you. Are there any specific jobs you're hoping it will take on or features you wish these answer engines had that no 1 quite does yet?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:14.907000Z",
        "message": "To be honest, not really. Like, uh, I'm just kind of a long the ride. I'm kinda just waiting to see, um, utilizing it to analyze, like, what, uh, HTTP and just source code of websites, which is pretty cool."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:31.797000Z",
        "message": "Nice. So you're exploring seeing where I should go and appreciating those analysis features. Before we wrap, anything else about your serves search or AI habits you think matters that I haven't asked about? Anything you wish these tools did differently?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:46.196000Z",
        "message": "Not that I could think of."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e57733b5af4b4282a3855af2e",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:50.137000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing your experiences and insights today. That wraps things up on my end, and you're free to end the call whenever you'd like. Have a great rest of your day."
      },
