    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:04.280000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:12.420000Z",
        "message": "It's going fine."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:15.750000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. Let's start simple. When you need an answer online, anything from a quick fact to something you're researching, what's what's the very first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:25.070000Z",
        "message": "Go to chat GPT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:28.330000Z",
        "message": "Got it. ChatGPT is your starting point. Thinking back to the last time you used ChatGPT, can you walk me through the whole story? From what sparked the need all the way through how you interacted with it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:40.680000Z",
        "message": "I just wanted to know if something I saw on was true or not or if it was AI or somebody made it up. Or if it was clickbait. And I asked the question, and I got an answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:56Z",
        "message": "Super clear. Let's zoom in on that moment. What was it about ChatGPT that made you reach for it? First, you were unsure if what you saw was real or misleading."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:06.540000Z",
        "message": "Because Google sends binge you around in a circle and never gives you a clear answer on anything."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:16.709000Z",
        "message": "That's really interesting. So with Google, it sounds like you end up clicking through lots of links and still don't feel you get a straight answer. When you use ChatGee"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:25.990000Z",
        "message": "Exactly."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:29.920000Z",
        "message": "when you got the answer from ChatGPT, how did you feel about it? Did it give you what you needed, or did you still have any doubts or frustrations?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:37.040000Z",
        "message": "It gave me what I needed."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:41.390000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Was there anything about ChatGPT's response? Maybe the way it explained things, the tone, or how fast it answered? That stood out as especially helpful to you."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:52.539000Z",
        "message": "It was very quick, and it gave me lots of links and information."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:58.460000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like speed and getting a bunch of sources made a big difference. For you. When you saw all those links and info, did you end up clicking through to to check them yourself for verification? Or did you mostly trust what ChatGPT gave you right away?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:13.830000Z",
        "message": "I mostly trusted what they gave me right away."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:22.489000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful to know. Thinking about other answer engines? Like Perplexity, Gemini, or or even Google's AI summaries, have you ever tried them for the same kind of question? If so,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:34.530000Z",
        "message": "Nope. I'm not a fan of them."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:40.040000Z",
        "message": "got it. What is it about those other engines Perplexity, Gemini, Google AI summaries, that makes you steer clear of them, Is it something about the experience? The trust factor, or just habit?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:51.720000Z",
        "message": "I just don't think they're as good. Or reliable."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:58.440000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense when you think about ChatGPT compared to those other engines. What words or qualities come to mind for ChatGPT and for Google, if any? Just whatever pops up first."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:09.360000Z",
        "message": "That CPT is more direct and more easy to use. Google is just a pain, and I feel like it sends you around in the"
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:23.050000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for putting that into words. ChatGPT feels direct and easy to use. While Google seems to send you in circles. If you imagine each engine as a person at a party, what kind of vibe would ChatGPT have? And what about Google? How would they act? Are you still there? Feel free to ask me any questions."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:19.329000Z",
        "message": "I have no questions."
      },
      {
        "callId": "9b0006bbd35847b5a506e6bf6",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:22.240000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for letting me know. That covers everything on my end. Um, thanks for sharing your thoughts and stories. Super helpful. You can end the call whenever you'd like."
      }
