        "message": "ChatGPT, like I said, is very satisfying. It's very 10 out of 10 for me."
      },
      {
        "callId": "76c38231a74a46f295289d4be",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:32.998000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. So ChatGPT stands out as satisfying for you. A 10 out of 10 experience, especially when you need answers, a certain format. Does that ever make looking back, has anything changed about how you search for answers online, say, in the past year? Any new habits or tools, even small shifts?"
