        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:27:01.228000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So your habits have stayed pretty steady. If you imagine in the future, what would make you want to use ChatGPT more often? Than Google or Safari? Or even switch over completely? Is there anything ChatGPT could could add or change that would tip tip the balance for you?"
