        "message": "Glad to hear it. So when you need answers online, say, you're curious about something, or need quick info, what's the very first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:30.966000Z",
        "message": "Search it up on Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:34.176000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Can you walk me through what that process looks like for you step by step? For example, how do do you decide what to what to type in? What do you do once the results come up?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:47.386000Z",
        "message": "I figure out what question I wanna ask. Then I search it up, and then I click whatever link gives the best answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:58.126000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for breaking that down. Um, thinking about your most recent search, what was the topic, and how did you go about picking which link to click?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:08.555000Z",
        "message": "It was about president Trump and I clicked the most recent link."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:15.706000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So for you, freshness matters when you're looking for an answer. When you click to that recent link, what stood out about it or what made it feel like it would give you the answer you needed?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:27.096000Z",
        "message": "The headline."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:29.896000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Headlines can be pretty telling. When you read through the answer on that page, did you feel confident about what you found? Or was there anything that made you question, double check, or look for more sources?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:43.096000Z",
        "message": "I feel confident."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:47.836000Z",
        "message": "Good to know. Um, so for quick answers like this, Google's your usual go to. Are there ever times you reach for a different tool or site like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or anything else? Instead of Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:59.466000Z",
        "message": "Sometimes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:04.106000Z",
        "message": "Can you think of a time when you chose something other than Google? What was going on, and what made you switch tools for that?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:10.786000Z",
        "message": "I was trying to find a grocery budget list for 20 dollars."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:15.815000Z",
        "message": "Great example. Which tool did you use for that, and what pushed you to choose it instead of Google for that particular task?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:22.425000Z",
        "message": "Check GPT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:25.956000Z",
        "message": "Nice. So when you use ChatGPT for your grocery budget list, what felt different about that experience compared to using Google, maybe in how the answer was presented or how it helped you get what you needed."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:37.446000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. It just it easily gives you a grocery list for your budget. It's quick."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:43.996000Z",
        "message": "That sounds pretty straightforward. Thinking about that, process, was there anything about, uh, using ChatGPT that felt especially helpful? Or even annoying? Any part of the experience that stood out to you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:57.166000Z",
        "message": "No."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:00.886000Z",
        "message": "Alright. If you hadn't used ChatGPT for that grocery budget task, what do you think you would have done instead?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:06.246000Z",
        "message": "Oh god."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:11.036000Z",
        "message": "Take your time. If ChatGPT hadn't been around, what would your backup plan have looked like? Would you have searched"
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:15.626000Z",
        "message": "Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:19.176000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for that. To recap, Google's usually your first stop, but for something like a budget grocery list, you turned to ChatGPT because it was quick and direct. Thinking about"
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:28.335000Z",
        "message": "Yes. I'm here."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:32.156000Z",
        "message": "perfect. Let's dig a little deeper. I'm curious about how you compare the answers you get from different tools. For instance, you've used Google versus ChatGPT for similar questions, does anything stand out about how the results feel? Like, the depth of information, confidence you get, or maybe questions?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:51.666000Z",
        "message": "Using ChatGPT is because you just get your answer right there. You don't have to click on any links."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:57.446000Z",
        "message": "That's a really clear difference. It comes to the kind of answers you trust, does 1 engine feel more credible to you or does it depend on what you're looking up?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:06.036000Z",
        "message": "It depends on what I'm looking at."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:09.656000Z",
        "message": "I hear you. Thinking back, when you want to quote or share an answer with someone else, are you more likely to send them a a Google link or copy something from ChatGPT? What influences that choice?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:20.496000Z",
        "message": "A Google link."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:24.216000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So Google feels right for sharing What is it about those links or the answers from Google that make them your pick? When you're passing info to someone else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:35.066000Z",
        "message": "It's just easier to send a link."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:38.066000Z",
        "message": "That's straightforward. Less effort. Looking back over the past year or so, has anything changed in how often you use Google? Versus tools like ChatGPT? Any shift in which 1 is your default for certain kinds of questions?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:51.256000Z",
        "message": "No. I still use Google the same."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:55.976000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for being clear. Last thing, do friends or coworkers ever recommend a specific answer engine to you? Like ChatGPT or Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:03.236000Z",
        "message": "No."
      },
      {
        "callId": "595f863c56684d128a55800b0",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:05.296000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful to know. Thanks for walking me through your habits. I learned a lot. How was this AI interview experience for you? You can end the call whenever you'd like."
      }
