        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot. Your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:16:57.210000Z",
        "message": "Hello? It's going fine."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:16:59.090000Z",
        "message": "Hello. I'm here and ready. Glad to hear it. I'm here to learn more about how you find answers online."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:04.180000Z",
        "message": "I hear you."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:05.570000Z",
        "message": "No right or wrong ways. Just your own style. To start, when you need to look something up or get an answer online, what's what's the very first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:17.390000Z",
        "message": "Well, I look for, um, normal keywords and type in Google or, um, through AI Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:25.340000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you start by coming up with keywords and then you type them into Google or use AI Google. Can you tell me a bit more about what you mean by AI Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:32.410000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:34.400000Z",
        "message": "Do you mean Google's AI generated answers? That show up? The Gemini search or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:38.280000Z",
        "message": "Yes. Gemini."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:45.710000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for clearing that up. So when you're searching, do you usually use regular Google search results? Or do you pay more attention to the Gemini AI generated answers? Up top?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:58.010000Z",
        "message": "No. The Gemini AI AI animated answers."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:03.210000Z",
        "message": "So you mostly on Gemini's AI generated answers when searching, Can you walk me through the last time you used it? What were you looking for? And what happened from start to finish?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:12.480000Z",
        "message": "I was looking where yeah. It was just it was yesterday, and I was looking for a specific item of clothing."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:21.310000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing. So yesterday, you searched for a specific item of clothing using Gemini's AI Answers. Can you walk me through what you typed in, what kind of answer you got, and what you did next?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:33.230000Z",
        "message": "I typed in ASOS, and I found the website of course, and there are different deals and all that or whatnot."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:43.430000Z",
        "message": "So you typed ASOS into Gemini, got to the website, and saw different deals. Did Gemini's AI Answer give you anything besides just the link? Like summaries, suggestions, or highlights? How did the Gemini result feel compared to a normal Google search result?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:59.640000Z",
        "message": "They were great. And also, they gave me multiple like accessories, machines, belts. And stuff like that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:13.570000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like Gemini's AI answer felt more helpful. Pulling together accessories and options beyond just giving you a link. What part of that experience stood out to you the most or felt the most useful?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:27.490000Z",
        "message": "Well, it broke it down into into areas that I really needed to know and right before I would, you know, go shopping on the website."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:40.229000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. So it gave you organized info you needed before you even went to shop. Was there anything about the Gemini AI result that felt confusing or didn't work the way you wanted?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:54.660000Z",
        "message": "It's it's a string with big hip. Other than, you know, just or just going to the website. Do and, like, not knowing how to navigate through every through the nooks and crannies of it all. But yeah."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:12.770000Z",
        "message": "So sounds like the Gemini answer made things easier by pointing out specific areas helping you avoid getting lost or overwhelmed on the site itself. Did you find yourself relying on any other engines or tools, like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or regular Google. For the same task, or did Gemini cover it all for you that time?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:35.360000Z",
        "message": "No. Gemini covered all of most of it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:39.670000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So Gemini pretty much did the job for you. If you hadn't used Gemini's AI Answers, what would you have done instead to find what you needed?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:48.630000Z",
        "message": "I just would've went straight to the website or did a simple way of search."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:20:54.440000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Uh, so before using Gemini, you just go to the ASOS site or type a basic search in Google. When you compare that old way with using Gemini's AI Answers, how does it feel different for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:09.549000Z",
        "message": "It feels like a big help. It it simplify it simplifies everything. That I'm trying to do, um, with the website or my search."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:18.820000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate you sharing that. The simplicity factor seems pretty important for you. Uh, could you tell me about any moments where Gemini's answer felt less helpful? Maybe it missed something you wanted or you needed to ask a follow-up."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:34.130000Z",
        "message": "Well, no. Um, I didn't I didn't feel that way at all. It it answered all or most of my questions."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:42.070000Z",
        "message": "That's good to hear. Sounds like Gemini, um, met most of your needs in that search. Thinking about other engines for a moment, have you ever tried ChatGPT, Perplexity, or regular Google results for similar searches? What was that experience like?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:21:59.449000Z",
        "message": "Well, I had never tried for just searching or making for a different task It depends on what I'm doing, but not for that specific search."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:09.200000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. You pick your tool depending on what you're trying to do. Can you think of a time when you chose a different engine? Like ChatGPT or Perplexity for another kind of task? What was the situation? And why did you use something other than Gemini or Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:25.910000Z",
        "message": "Well, I use it I use it for work to, you know, do a project."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:32.540000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So you use a different engine for work projects. Could you share the last time you used say, ChatGPT or Perplexity for that kind of task? What were you working on, and how did the experience compare to Gemini's AI"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:44.410000Z",
        "message": "Probably a week ago. It was about a week ago. Um, it it's"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:48.510000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. What"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:22:51.150000Z",
        "message": "kinda it's it's kinda similar, but, um, yeah, um, I would rather do Gemini 6. It's, you know, more simple."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:00.330000Z",
        "message": "So for work tasks, you've tried other engines like ChatGPT or Perplexity, but you still prefer Gemini because it feels simpler. Is there something specific about Gemini that makes it easier for you when you're working compared to those other tools?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:16.360000Z",
        "message": "Well, the options are automatically listed. So that's that's easy as it gets. After you search."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:24.440000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Having options listed right after searching, makes things straightforward for you. If you think about chat GPT or perplexity,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:31.079000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 43,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:32.380000Z",
        "message": "is there anything they do that you wish Gemini could do? Or something you miss from those tools even if you mostly use Gemini?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:42.110000Z",
        "message": "Well, no. Not at all. Everything seems fine. I prefer Gemini over all the most."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 45,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:23:50.370000Z",
        "message": "Understood. It sounds like Gemini is your clear favorite right now. When you think about Gemini, Google, or ChatGPT as brands or personalities, if each was a person at a party, who are they and how would they act?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 46,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:07.770000Z",
        "message": "1."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 47,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:11.770000Z",
        "message": "Let's start with Gemini."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 48,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:12.660000Z",
        "message": "Could you repeat that?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 49,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:15.320000Z",
        "message": "Sure. So if Gemini, Google, and ChatGPT were each a person at a party, who would Gemini be? How would they act or interact with people?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 50,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:25.790000Z",
        "message": "I would say Gemini will be my girlfriend and Complexity will be a friend."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 51,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:31.750000Z",
        "message": "That's a fun way of putting it. So Gemini feels close and familiar, like someone you trust and spend a lot of time Perplexity is more like a friend, maybe helpful, but not as central for you. If you imagine Google or ChatGPT at the same party, what roles or vibes do they have?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 52,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:24:49.720000Z",
        "message": "Both of them will probably have good vibes. All 3 of us will hit it all in all day. But but being being with Google, I'm probably wouldn't know. Make me feel more comfortable and familiar with everything I'm trying to do."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 53,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:07.030000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. Sounds like Google brings a sense of comfort and familiarity of like a dependable person you've known for a while, would you say there's a difference how much you trust or rely? On the answers from Gemini versus Google or Chat 2 p t, or do they all feel about the same in that way?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 54,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:27.930000Z",
        "message": "Well, Google Gemini is the best. The others are a little bit behind, but they are pretty good their self. I would trust Google Gemini way better or first and foremost than others."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 55,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:25:44.760000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Sounds like Gemini is is where your trust goes first. With Google and the others trailing, but still solid. Thinking back a year ago, has anything changed about how you look things up online? Any shifts in which tools you reach for or how often you use Gemini versus the others?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 56,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:04.710000Z",
        "message": "Oh, no. I think everything is fine. I think we cleared up everything."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 57,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:12.110000Z",
        "message": "Great. I really appreciate you taking the time to share your experiences and how you think about these answer engines. For chatting with me. You can end the call whenever you'd like."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ae0f49d63c88415ea70e0932f",
        "index": 58,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:26:24.240000Z",
        "message": "Thank you very much."
      },
