        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:45.651000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:53.211000Z",
        "message": "Good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:56.331000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. Get us started, when you need answers online, whether it's something quick or a bit more in-depth, what's what's the very first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:06.071000Z",
        "message": "Better Bigel."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:10.471000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. You mentioned Better Biggle. Can you walk me through what that is and what led you to choose it? You're searching for answers online?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:18.281000Z",
        "message": "Google, quick search."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:22.071000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So, usually, your first move is a quick Google search. Can you walk me through what that process looks like for you step by step? From the moment you think of your question all the way to finding your answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:37.131000Z",
        "message": "Google what's most concerning or interested. And it's a quick search, and it gives me everything I need to know."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:48.541000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. About the last time you used, uh, Google for a search, what was the topic or question you were looking into, and what made that search stand out?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:02.421000Z",
        "message": "I was googling the top 100 songs for the week, so I can update my playlist on Spotify."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:12.731000Z",
        "message": "Great example. Starting from when you decided to update your Spotify playlist, Can you walk me through every step you took in that Google search? What you typed? What results showed up? How you decided which info to trust? Just tell me the full story."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:27.841000Z",
        "message": "I typed in the top 100 songs for the week. Then it took me to like, the billboard music list, And then I got to play a sample of each song, and then I downloaded this song."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:46.981000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful. Thinking back on that experience, what part of it felt most helpful to you? Uh, was there anything about the process that was annoying or or slowed you down? Feel free to ask me any questions."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:09.400000Z",
        "message": "Questions?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:12.251000Z",
        "message": "Sure. I'm here for your questions too. But before I flip it around, just 1 more on your billboard search. Uh, was there anything in that process you wish was quicker or easier, like getting, like, the song files, browsing the list, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:27.121000Z",
        "message": "No."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:29.191000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for clarifying. When you're looking for answers, do you ever use other tools or sites? Besides Google? Like ChatGPT, Perplexity, Gemini, or something else? If so, can you share a story about when you switch to a different tool and what the task was?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:45.821000Z",
        "message": "Chat GPT. You can talk into it. And it gives you answers almost immediately, sometimes quicker than Google itself."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:01.071000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. Um, can you share the story of the last time you used ChatGPT for something instead of Google? What question did you ask and what was different about that experience for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:12.881000Z",
        "message": "I asked about a recipe for cookies, and it gave me a basic recipe and how to make it and then asked me if I had any of the following ingredients. And I said I didn't have all the ingredients and then it simplified their recipe. So accommodate all the ingredients I did have. And it was a quick response."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:39.741000Z",
        "message": "That's a pretty hands on use case. Thinking about that cookie recipe experience, what stood out to you as most helpful about using ChatGPT versus Google? Anything that surprised you or felt especially useful?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:53.370000Z",
        "message": "It was able to, um, come up with a quick rest recipe. Using the ingredients I already had in my kitchen. And I didn't have to reask the same question. And it just kept asking me, like, what it could do different or what I needed or didn't need in that recipe."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:14.631000Z",
        "message": "That sounds super convenient. When ChatGPT adapted the recipe like that, how did you feel about the response compared to what you usually get? From a Google search? Any particular emotions or impressions that stuck with you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:23.910000Z",
        "message": "Alright. I really enjoyed it because, it didn't, like, try to drag me in a different direction or use something I didn't have. And it's accommodated everything I was looking for. Then a quick response."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:45.241000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Um, if you think about how ChatGPT and Google each answer your questions, how do their responses feel different to you? Maybe in terms of depth the way they talk to you, or even trust. Anything that stands out?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:59.571000Z",
        "message": "Chad GBT was more in-depth than, like, was, like, a more personalized experience. Where Google would give just, like, basic information and different, links to click on them. It didn't really answer my full question to where ChatGPT did."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:15:19.711000Z",
        "message": "Really clear comparison. Thanks. You had to line up Google and ChatGPT from most to least helpful, for you personally, which comes first? And what's what's the main reason for your choice?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:15:30.761000Z",
        "message": "Oh, ChatGPT because it's more personalized than easier to understand, and you don't have to click through a bunch of links to find what you're exactly looking for."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:15:43.571000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Now thinking about how you see these tools as brands, if you had to imagine Google and ChatGPT as people at a party, who would they be? How would each act?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:15:55.031000Z",
        "message": "I would chat with Jack GPT. I don't understand the question."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:16:04.001000Z",
        "message": "No worries. Basically, if you think about Google and ChatGPT, like, they each have their own personality or vibe. Words come to mind for each? For example, Google feels like. The ChatGPT feels like"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:16:17.071000Z",
        "message": "Chat GPT feels more personalized and like, understanding of what you're trying to ask to where"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:16:27.671000Z",
        "message": "Nice. Sounds like ChatGPT comes across as more understanding maybe even helpful. What about Google? If you had to put it into a word or 2, what's what's the vibe or feeling that comes to mind? Are you still there?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:16:47.991000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:16:50.221000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for confirming. So how would you describe Google's vibe or feeling when you use it? Maybe words like informative, straightforward, impersonal, or something else come to mind?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:01.871000Z",
        "message": "It's very impersonal and just basic."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:06.791000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate that. When you get an answer and wanna share it with someone, like texting a friend or posting online, is there a certain engine's answer you feel more comfortable quoting? Why do you think that is?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:20.991000Z",
        "message": "I I don't understand the question. I'm sorry."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:25.891000Z",
        "message": "No problem at all. If you're helping someone else, say, sending them a link or some info, do you ever prefer to share a Google result? Or a ChatGPT answer? Does 1 feel more trustworthy or credible to to share? Or not really? Thanks. That's clear. Got it. So chat GPT feels more trustworthy for sharing answers with others. Thinking about the past year, has anything changed about how often you use Google versus ChatGPT? Maybe you find yourself reaching for ChatGPT more often or something triggered a shift."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:03.970000Z",
        "message": "I tend to use ChadGPT more often, um, just out of time, like, from in a hurry trying to look for something or an answer or whatever. I'll go there instead of Google because I feel like with Google, I have to sit there for a while and just try to come up with the best answer that I'm looking for."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:24.681000Z",
        "message": "That's a helpful shift to hear about. Was there a specific moment you remember when you started reaching for CHAT GPT first? Instead of Google, or has it just kinda happened gradually over time?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:35.481000Z",
        "message": "When I first heard about it, I downloaded it and was just kinda messing around with it to see what it was about. And then I just felt more comfortable using that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:47.240000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like discovering it and trying it out led to a switch pretty naturally."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 43,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:49.911000Z",
        "message": "Yeah."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:51.411000Z",
        "message": "Do you ever hear friends or coworkers recommending ChatGPT or other engines"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 45,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:51.961000Z",
        "message": "Yeah."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:55.971000Z",
        "message": "for certain types of searches? Or is it more something you stumbled on yourself?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 47,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:02.170000Z",
        "message": "I heard about it on a podcast. And then then I was interested about it and downloaded it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 48,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:10.221000Z",
        "message": "That's really clear. Thanks for walking me through your whole journey. We wrap up, is there anything you wish these Answer Tools could do that they don't today? Any features or improvements on your personal wish list?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 49,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:22.501000Z",
        "message": "No. Not right now. I can't think of any."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 50,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:19:25.920000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. Totally fair. Sometimes it's working just fine as is. Thanks so much for sharing your experiences and stories with me."
      },
      {
        "callId": "41973863b08b4da4a94398d8b",
        "index": 51,
