        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:54.863000Z",
        "message": "speed really made a difference for you. Can you say more about how Gemini's answers felt compared to something like Google search or another engine? What's what's the difference for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:06.913000Z",
        "message": "Well, to me, it's a lot faster than just a search. And you get more you know, you get better answers out of Gemini. And that that's my preferred way of shopping and you know, asking questions about different, uh, things."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:26.183000Z",
        "message": "You mentioned Better Answers. Can you describe what makes Gemini's responses better for you? Is it the detail, how it phrases things, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:35.213000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. It's more in-depth. It it explains better than searches on Google or any other search engine. And it's got in-depth pictures, you know, videos. Just everything to me is better."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:51.883000Z",
        "message": "So you get richer descriptions, plus photos, and videos all in 1 spot. When you read those answers, how do you usually feel? For example, confident"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:00.503000Z",
        "message": "Off. Yeah. I I feel great. I mean, it it is such a big help."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:09.783000Z",
        "message": "It sounds Gemini leaves you feeling positive and and supported. Is there anything about the experience that ever frustrates or annoys you? Even small things?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:20.752000Z",
        "message": "Actually, no. I've never had no problems with it. And, I never will. And I think, you know, in time, it will become much better."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:33.003000Z",
        "message": "You sound pretty confident in it. If Gemini hadn't been available, what do you think you would have done to find the gift for your fiance?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:41.503000Z",
        "message": "Well, I didn't get I would actually use my Alexa, you know, speaker or something like that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:50.082000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. So Alexa might be your backup. How do you feel the answers from Alexa compare with what you get"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:53.723000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:57.093000Z",
        "message": "from Gemini?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:59.483000Z",
        "message": "I like Gemini better. It's just it has more in-depth ways of explaining what I'm buying or what I'm looking up. It's just to me, it's a better a better way to find things."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:14.263000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So for you, Gemini stands out for its depth and explanations. Thinking back, can you remember a time you used a different tool? Maybe Google or ChatGPT instead of Gemini for a task? What was that like? And why did you switch?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:29.152000Z",
        "message": "I used to Google everything or, you know, I would use Windows and all that. And it's just once that I started learning the new AI and all the meta stuff and, you know, Gemini, it's just it's helped me a great deal, and it it just explains better to me than just, you know, search engines."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:50.753000Z",
        "message": "So it sounds like switching to Gemini and other AI tools changed how you look things up. Can you tell me about a moment when you first noticed yourself? Choosing Gemini or an AI engine first? Instead of Google, what led you to make that change?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:15:05.343000Z",
        "message": "Well, I was just I got frustrated with all the Google searches coming up with no answers. So I said, you know what? I would I'm gonna try this Gemini. And I have a I have been using it ever since. I I fell in love with it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:15:24.433000Z",
        "message": "That frustration with Google, no clear answer showing up. Pushed you to try Gemini. Uh, can you tell me about how you felt first time Gemini actually gave you what you needed compared to old experience with Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:15:37.983000Z",
        "message": "Oh, I was very happy. I thought Google was the best thing known to man, but once I use Gemini, I rarely even use Google search anymore. I'm My first pick is born to Gemini."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:15:55.423000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like Gemini quickly won you over. If you were telling a friend or coworker about Gemini, versus Google, um, what words would you use to describe Gemini? And what about Google? What kind of words come to mind there?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:16:10.293000Z",
        "message": "Well, Google is used to be my go to way of finding things. But, yes, I would tell a friend or family member or whoever, hey. If you think Google's great, you have to try Gemini because, you know, you get answers quicker. You get videos, pictures. Everything's just faster."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:16:31.043000Z",
        "message": "And when you share an answer with someone else, maybe texting a link or telling them what you found, which engine's response feels most credible to mention or quote. Why do you say that?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:16:44.533000Z",
        "message": "Gemini. It's and I use a lot. I use Facebook Messenger a lot."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:16:52.863000Z",
        "message": "When you send something from Gemini over Messenger or elsewhere, makes you feel confident it's worth sharing? Is it the detail How quickly you got it or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:04.323000Z",
        "message": "Well, it's very fast. It is. And it's clear. It's quicker. Everything that I do with the Internet, it seems like it's better."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:09.793000Z",
        "message": "So speed and clarity really matter to you. Let's say, Gemini suddenly disappeared for a week. What would you do Would you switch to another tool, go back to Google, or try something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 43,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:26.693000Z",
        "message": "Well, I'd actually go back to Google, but I would still wait until Jim and I came back. It's I'm love Gemini."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:37.723000Z",
        "message": "You'd switch back to Google in a pinch, but you'd be ready to return, uh, to Gemini right away. If you could change or improve anything about Gemini, even just a little, what would you wish for?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 45,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:17:53.313000Z",
        "message": "Actually, could not answer that. It everything that I need all in 1. That's that's a I wouldn't change anything."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:04.473000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like Gemini is ticking all the boxes for you. Uh, before we wrap up, how did it feel talking about your Answer Engine habits? Me today? Anything surprise you about the chat?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 47,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:16.293000Z",
        "message": "No. This is a very nice chat, and it's yeah. It's like I'm talking to a friend. It's very fun."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5f7ba1345f3e49498011cdbda",
        "index": 48,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:18:24.733000Z",
