      },
      {
        "callId": "87cf4017b1014a13b8b275eaa",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:51.723000Z",
        "message": "sorry for the confusion. If you compare Google's AI Answers to what you imagine you might get from something like ChatGPT or Perplexity, what differences do you think you'd notice?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "87cf4017b1014a13b8b275eaa",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:03.323000Z",
        "message": "I have no idea. They're probably about the same."
      },
      {
        "callId": "87cf4017b1014a13b8b275eaa",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:07.373000Z",
        "message": "Fair enough. You hear the names Google, ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity, is there anything you associate with each 1? Words, feelings, or impressions that pop into your head?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "87cf4017b1014a13b8b275eaa",
        "index": 43,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:19.063000Z",
        "message": "No. Not really. The Owl chats faster."
      },
      {
        "callId": "87cf4017b1014a13b8b275eaa",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:24.743000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. Owl chats faster. Is that perplexity you're thinking of? Or something else? Tell me more about makes you say that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "87cf4017b1014a13b8b275eaa",
        "index": 45,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:33.023000Z",
        "message": "I'm not sure. They're probably all the same."
      },
      {
        "callId": "87cf4017b1014a13b8b275eaa",
        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:36.643000Z",
        "message": "Got it. For you, they blend together. No big differences stand out. Thinking back, has anything changed about the way you look things up? Online compared to a year ago, or is"
      },
      {
        "callId": "87cf4017b1014a13b8b275eaa",
        "index": 47,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:46.353000Z",
        "message": "No. Yes. It's a lot faster now for sure."
      },
      {
        "callId": "87cf4017b1014a13b8b275eaa",
        "index": 48,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:53.242000Z",
        "message": "That jump in speed, do you remember when you first noticed things getting a lot faster? Any moment or change that sticks out?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "87cf4017b1014a13b8b275eaa",
        "index": 49,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:01.293000Z",
        "message": "And it's probably about 6 months ago when things started speeding up with it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "87cf4017b1014a13b8b275eaa",
        "index": 50,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:06.243000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful. 6 months sounds like when Google's AI summaries kicked in for you. Have you ever heard friends or coworkers mention using other answer engines? Or is it mostly Google in your circles too?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "87cf4017b1014a13b8b275eaa",
        "index": 51,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:18.583000Z",
        "message": "It's message."
      },
      {
        "callId": "87cf4017b1014a13b8b275eaa",
        "index": 52,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:22.423000Z",
        "message": "Are you saying most people in your circle just message for help? Instead of using search engines, or did you mean something else? Tell me a bit more."
      },
      {
        "callId": "87cf4017b1014a13b8b275eaa",
        "index": 53,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:30.533000Z",
        "message": "Thank you, Christine. Like, they just mostly use Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "87cf4017b1014a13b8b275eaa",
        "index": 54,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:35.233000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for clearing that up. So it's mostly Google for you and the people you know. Before we wrap up, is there anything you wish Google's AI Answers could do that it doesn't today? Any features or options you'd love to see added?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "87cf4017b1014a13b8b275eaa",
        "index": 55,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:50.383000Z",
        "message": "No. I think it's perfect the way it is."
      },
      {
        "callId": "87cf4017b1014a13b8b275eaa",
        "index": 56,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:54.272000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Last quick thing. How was chatting with an AI moderator today? Anything that stood out to you about this kind of interview experience?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "87cf4017b1014a13b8b275eaa",
        "index": 57,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:15:05.423000Z",
        "message": "No."
      },
      {
        "callId": "87cf4017b1014a13b8b275eaa",
        "index": 58,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:15:07.883000Z",
        "message": "Thank you for calling."
      }
