  {
    "id": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
    "responseId": "49e08ea2c4114bc9bec14e16e",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:08:38.329000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:08:46.938000Z",
        "message": "It is good. Thank you."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:08:51.579000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. Let's start with something simple. When you need answers online, what's what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:08:59.679000Z",
        "message": "I go to Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:03.599000Z",
        "message": "Walk me through what that looks like for you Start from the moment you realize you need an answer. What's the next step you take?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:10.759000Z",
        "message": "I'll go to Google and I type in what I the the question I have, and I did not click search."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:19.199000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So once you type your question, into Google, what do you do next? Do you read through the results? Look for something specific? Or does something else happen?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:28.489000Z",
        "message": "Look through the results. And see which 1 gives me the best information I think is good to me."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:39.699000Z",
        "message": "Got it. When you're browsing those Google results, what catches your eye first? Now, is it the headlines, the domain names, snippets, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:49.449000Z",
        "message": "It's usually the headlines. If the headlines usually pertains to the question I'm asking, I'll go with those."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:57.329000Z",
        "message": "And when you click into 1 of those results, what do you look for to decide if the answer is trustworthy or helpful for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:06.019000Z",
        "message": "How does it how it sounds? Where the source is coming from, and basically, like, though who said it or something like that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:16.079000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. Thinking back, can you tell me about the last time you used Google for a quick answer? What was your question, and how did the whole process go for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:27.509000Z",
        "message": "I looked up, uh, when a little Kim song came out so I just typed in when did Lil' Kim make, a song a certain song I was looking forward to. And they told me what year it came out in."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:43.029000Z",
        "message": "Once you saw the answer to your low chem search, was there anything about that experience? That especially helpful or maybe a bit annoying?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:52.038000Z",
        "message": "The experience was regular. As soon as I typed in the question, the answer came up right away. So"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:02.449000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like it was pretty smooth. If you hadn't used Google for that, is there another tool or site you might have tried instead? For that kind of question?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:12.019000Z",
        "message": "I could use, like, chat GPT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:15.889000Z",
        "message": "Have you used ChatGPT for questions like that before? If so, how did the experience feel different from Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:24.839000Z",
        "message": "I used the I used chat with DBT for certain questions and for them to help me edit my pictures. Like, Google doesn't do that. Doesn't help you edit pictures, give you certain question. Answers to certain questions, or just give you, like, ideas of how to help help you do certain stuff. So I like chat GPT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:48.019000Z",
        "message": "Seems like ChatGPT does some unique jobs for you. Can you tell me about a specific time you used ChatGPT, maybe for editing pictures or getting creative help. What did you ask, and how did it go?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:59.389000Z",
        "message": "I asked them to help me turn 1 of my pictures into, like, an anime picture for a album cover."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:09.579000Z",
        "message": "That's a cool project. When you asked ChatGPT to to help turn your picture, into an anime album cover, how did it guide you? What kind of steps or suggestions did it give you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:21.719000Z",
        "message": "It just gave me, like, what I what kind of anime I do I like, what kind of style do I want. Basically, with, like, emotion or something to do if I want something dark. Funny. Or depending on what enemies do I like, Dragon Ball z or something."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:44.379000Z",
        "message": "When ChatGPT asked you those questions, like about your favorite style or mood, how did that feel compared to searching on Google for ideas or inspiration?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:53.909000Z",
        "message": "Because they asked me what I want, and they gave me some choices and all that. Like, I didn't know what I really wanted. Like, I I kind of knew, but not sure. But when it gave me some more choices and everything, it helped me narrow down my options."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:10.688000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like ChatGPT helped you shape your ideas not just answer a fixed question. How did you feel during that process? Any moments of surprise? Frustration, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:22.309000Z",
        "message": "No. Everything was good. I was happy. It did that because it made it easier for me."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:29.879000Z",
        "message": "Nice. Sounds like you felt supported. Thinking about both Google and ChatGPT, is there anything either 1 does that frustrates you or feels like it could be improved?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:43.229000Z",
        "message": "Uh, not really yet. Google's usually alright. Like, it helps me with certain other stuff, certain questions that I think Google might answer. But I'd rather use ChatGPT for a lot of stuff."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:00.279000Z",
        "message": "When you decide between Google and ChatGPT, what's what's the main thing that tips the scales for you? Is it the type of question how fast you get an answer or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:11.859000Z",
        "message": "Is that how fast I can get the answer? And all the editing stuff for pictures? That's what Google doesn't do. ChatGPT does that. And I I usually do that a lot."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:24.099000Z",
        "message": "If you think about other answer engines out there, like Perplexity or Gemini, have you ever used them? If yes, what was that like? If not, have you heard anything about them from friends or online?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:36.379000Z",
        "message": "I never used them. I just seen a couple commercials for Gemini and stuff. It looks alright, but I already used ChapGBT. So"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:48.759000Z",
        "message": "If you lined up Google, ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Gemini, just based on what you know or have seen, how would you rank them from most to least helpful for you? What leads to that order?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:59.699000Z",
        "message": "Yo."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:15:02.359000Z",
        "message": "I hear you. Would you like to keep going or wrap up for today? If you'd like, you can end the call whenever you'd like."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:15:10.839000Z",
        "message": "I wanna keep going."
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:15:14.248000Z",
        "message": "Great. Let's dig a bit deeper. If each of these engines, Google, ChatGPT, Gemini, were people at a party, what kind of person would each 1 be? How would they act"
      },
      {
        "callId": "73e76b2979494665b70d08ca0",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:15:27.449000Z",
        "message": "I think Chad GPT would just be a know it all. Everybody would like, oh, we'll go to that person for questions or if they need something. Google is just probably someone that thinks they know"
      }
