  {
    "id": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
    "responseId": "c69a2720a88b47b5a5c26931d",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:19.501000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:27.461000Z",
        "message": "It's good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:30.150000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. Let's jump in. When you need answers online, what's what's the first thing you you you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:37.301000Z",
        "message": "I go to Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:42.441000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Can you walk me through your typical process when you look something up on Google? From the moment you have a question all the way to getting your answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:54.140000Z",
        "message": "I type in what I'm looking for, and I go through several different web pages until I'm find the exact answer that I need."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:08:05.251000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Thinking about the last time you did this, what was the question you were trying to answer? And you tell me the full story from start to finish?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:08:15.141000Z",
        "message": "I was in the process of cooking dinner, and there was 1 thing I did not know how to make, which was gravy. And so I looked up how to make homemade gravy and then looked through several web pages and found the best recipe for me."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:08:33.360000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for walking through that. What stood out as especially helpful during that experience? And was there anything frustrating or or annoying about it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:08:44.471000Z",
        "message": "The web pages that were helpful were the ones that you can just jump straight to the recipe. The frustrating part is the web pages that you have to read a whole bunch of stuff before they actually get you to the rest or there was a whole bunch of ads that pop up on that web page."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:03.751000Z",
        "message": "That sounds familiar to a lot of people. In that moment, did you ever consider using something besides Google? Like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Google's own AI summaries? Or did you stick with just regular Google search?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:18.011000Z",
        "message": "I stuck with just regular Google search because I'm not too familiar familiar with the AI the chat bots, or all that new stuff. But coming around and I'm trying to learn it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:33.391000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful to know. When you hear about tools like ChatGPT or Gemini, is there anything in particular that comes to mind? Any feelings, ideas, or even worries?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:44.841000Z",
        "message": "No worries. It's just a little high-tech for me, and I it's take me a little bit to get to learn it and I'm just gonna have to use it more I guess, instead of using the regular Google search."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:01.541000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. It can feel like a lot at first when something is brand new. If you were to imagine trying out 1 of these AI answer engines for the first time, what would make you want to give it a shot instead of just using Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:18.041000Z",
        "message": "I guess the fact that I don't have to sit there and type everything in or maybe I'll get better information through the new technology."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:29.711000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So less typing and possibly more useful answers. Are draws for you. If you did switch away from Google for looking up recipes or other things, what would you need from a new tool to feel confident and comfortable using it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:45.741000Z",
        "message": "I would just need to know that I'm getting accurate information."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:53.111000Z",
        "message": "That's key. When you think about sharing answers, or recipes with others, do you feel more comfortable quoting something you found on Google? Or would you trust something from an AI engine just as much? Me a bit about your thinking there."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:11.500000Z",
        "message": "Well, Google sometimes can sway you away and into false information. As it has in the past. I feel that AI is more innovative, and I'll probably get more trustworthy information from there."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:27.481000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. You think of a specific time when Google gave you info that turned out to be wrong or unreliable? What happened and how did you figure it out?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:38.931000Z",
        "message": "When I had common cold symptoms and I looked up my symptoms and tried to tell me I had cancer and this and this and that, and so it just it overexaggerates information."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:54.401000Z",
        "message": "That's a good example. How did that make you feel about trusting Google's answers for health related questions after that happened?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:06.151000Z",
        "message": "Just that Google wasn't too trustworthy in giving false information like that can really affect somebody's life."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:17.391000Z",
        "message": "I hear you. If you imagine using something like ChatGPT or Gemini, for a health question in the future, what would signal to you that you could trust their answer more than Google? Is there anything specific you'd look for?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:33.631000Z",
        "message": "I would look for information based on these symptoms that I gave them, not a broad wide information that's just, like, tells me I got everything wrong with me in the book, but that they focus on 1 thing."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:51.621000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. You'd want the answer to be focused based on what you actually describe not just a worst case scenario list. About all these tools, Google, ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity, if you line them up from most helpful to least helpful for your needs right now, based on what you know and have used, what order would you put them in?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:16.141000Z",
        "message": "I'm not really sure because I've only used Gemini, and I was only a couple times."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:24.131000Z",
        "message": "Got it. When you that's helpful. When you did use Gemini, those couple of times, what were you trying to find out? And how did the experience feel compared to Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:40.230000Z",
        "message": "I was trying to find out the admission price to my son's away football game at that school. Because I couldn't find it on regular Google. And they pretty much told me they had mission price. For the away team, and it was straightforward."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:03.641000Z",
        "message": "That's a neat example. What about that Gemini experience felt especially helpful or different from your usual Google search? Any little details stand out?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:14.790000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. How straightforward it was, and I didn't have to search through 5 different web pages just to find 1 simple answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:23.621000Z",
        "message": "Sounds like saving time and hassle was key for you there. Looking back over the past year, do you notice any changes in how often or when you use Google versus these AI engines like Gemini? If just a little bit?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:37.521000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. It's just like you said, more time saving, more convenient"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:46.961000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate that. Last thing, if you imagine telling a friend about Gemini, or another AI answer engine, what words or feelings do you think you'd use to describe it to"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:58.441000Z",
        "message": "I would just let them know that you waste more time using the regular Google and that is more convenient"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:15:16.181000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing all that. Before we wrap up, how did this AI interview feel for you? Any feedback about the experience and you're free to end the call whenever you'd like."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:15:31.061000Z",
        "message": "It was nice not to have to type in stuff when I'm getting asked questions, but obviously save time. Especially on these surveys. You know, you waste a lot of time when you gotta type in all kinds of stuff, but it's easier just to speak to somebody rather than having to write everything out."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8f9da538f9034f948f20e23e7",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:15:53.941000Z",
        "message": "That's really helpful feedback. Thanks for sharing. Um, I enjoyed hearing your stories. You're all set here. So you can end the call whenever you'd like."
      }
    ],
