  {
    "id": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
    "responseId": "2e366496a44948aeb7b0a782a",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:15.291000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:23.811000Z",
        "message": "Alright."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:26.990000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for share"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:27.321000Z",
        "message": "Can you hear"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:31.771000Z",
        "message": "I can't hear in the traditional sense, but I can read and respond to anything you type here. Just let me know what's on your mind. Or if you have any questions before we get started."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:43.371000Z",
        "message": "No questions."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:45.611000Z",
        "message": "Great. Thanks for letting me know. So to kick things off, when you need answers, online, what's what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:54.321000Z",
        "message": "Go to Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:57.001000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Google is your starting point. Can you walk me through what that usually looks like step by step, uh, when you're searching for something."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:08:06.041000Z",
        "message": "Just click the space bar, and then type in what I'm looking for and click search."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:08:11.821000Z",
        "message": "Nice and straightforward. After you hit search, what do you typically look for on the results page? For example, do you go for the first link, check summaries, scroll for something specific? Walk me through what happens next."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:08:30.771000Z",
        "message": "Something specific."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:08:33.551000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you're scanning for a particular result. Can you tell me a bit more about"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:08:37.321000Z",
        "message": "Correct."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:08:39.301000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for confirming. Thinking back to your most recent search, can you tell me the full story? What were you looking for? And how did you go about finding your answer?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:08:50.651000Z",
        "message": "I was looking for a answer to a a a problem I was having. So I went I went to the AR generator department."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:00.351000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Just to make sure I understand, you were having a problem, and you went to the AR generator department was that part of your Google search or was it a specific website you found through Google? Can you walk me through exactly"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:13.311000Z",
        "message": "No. When you go to Google in the in the left hand corner,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:16.441000Z",
        "message": "thanks for"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:19.771000Z",
        "message": "it it say AI, and I click AI."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:25.161000Z",
        "message": "That helps clarify things. Appreciate you clarifying. So after you type your question, into Google, you notice an AI option in the left hand corner? And you click that. When you do that"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:38.991000Z",
        "message": "Correct."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:41.201000Z",
        "message": "thanks for confirming. After you click that AI option on Google, what happens next? How does the answer show up for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:47.571000Z",
        "message": "It gives you a rundown. AI give you a rundown to answer the wrong person. Yeah."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:09:50.411000Z",
        "message": "Got it. A quick rundown. Interesting. So the AI gives you a rundown, but sometimes it feels like the answer is aimed at the wrong person. Can you tell me more about what you mean by that? Maybe an example or how that feels when you see the response?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:10.331000Z",
        "message": "So far, AI had been pretty much on point."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:15.590000Z",
        "message": "That's good to hear. When the AI is on point, what stands out to you as the most helpful part of those answers? Is it the speed, the detail, the way it explains things, or something else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:27.931000Z",
        "message": "The speed and detail."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:31.381000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Speed and detail matter most to you. On the flip side, uh, has anything ever frustrated you or felt annoying? When using the AI feature in Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:42.321000Z",
        "message": "No."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:45.491000Z",
        "message": "Alright. Good to know. If you hadn't used Google's AI feature, just imagining for a moment, what would you have done instead? Get your answer?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:55.361000Z",
        "message": "The traditional Google search."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:10:58.881000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. So if the AI feature wasn't there, you just use regular Google search as your backup. Thinking about other answer engines, like ChatGee"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:06.561000Z",
        "message": "Correct."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:08.671000Z",
        "message": "thanks for confirming. Now thinking about other answer engines, like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Gemini, Have you ever used 1 of those instead of Google's AI? If so, can you tell me about a specific time and what led you to pick a different tool?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:25.741000Z",
        "message": "I believe AI to Google is Gemini, if I'm not mistaken. Or if I'm not mistaken, I believe it says Gemini in corner."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:36.851000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful. The AI option on Google you use, likely Gemini. Thanks for pointing that out. Have you ever tried any other answer engines? Like ChatGPT or Perplexity?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:47.111000Z",
        "message": "No."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:11:50.501000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So for you, it's mostly Google and the Gemini AI feature. If you think about the way Gemini answers your questions, how would you describe its strengths? Makes it stand out to you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:03.021000Z",
        "message": "As is pretty much it gets straight to the point."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:07.301000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate your take. Getting straight to the point is key for you. When you see an answer from Gemini, do you ever feel the need to double check its or do you mostly trust what it gives you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:20.391000Z",
        "message": "I trust you."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:24.391000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing. That's helpful. If you picture Gemini as as a person at a party, what kind of personality would it have? How would it act with people?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 43,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:35.940000Z",
        "message": "Intelligent and proper."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:39.441000Z",
        "message": "That's a clear image. Intelligent and proper. How about traditional Google search if that were a person at a party? What would they be like?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 45,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:51.021000Z",
        "message": "Quiet, but but full of information."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:12:55.391000Z",
        "message": "Love that. Quiet, but packed with info. If you ever need to share an answer with someone else, say, texting a friend or telling a coworker, which answer feels more credible to pass along, Geminis or traditional Googles, or do you treat them about the same?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 47,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:11.361000Z",
        "message": "Both the same."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 48,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:15.440000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing. Looking back, say, a year ago, has anything changed in how you search for answers? Online? Or it pretty much feel the same as before?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 49,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:27.660000Z",
        "message": "No. It's fast."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 50,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:30.621000Z",
        "message": "Got it. No real change, and speed is still the big thing for you. Do you ever hear friends or coworkers talk about using different answer engines, or do most people, you know, stick with Google too?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 51,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:44.391000Z",
        "message": "Mostly Google. But what I or yeah. Mostly Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 52,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:13:50.190000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. So Google really is the go to among people you know. Before we wrap up, is there anything you wish these Answer Engines, Google, Gemini, or any others could do better or offer that would make your experience even smoother?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 53,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:06.421000Z",
        "message": "No. It's it's it's working perfectly."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 54,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:10.161000Z",
        "message": "Good to hear it's doing the job for you. Thanks for sharing your search stories. With me today. It's really helpful. Um, if you have any last thoughts or questions, about doing an AI interview, let me know. Otherwise, you're all set and can end the call whenever you'd like."
      },
      {
        "callId": "5509837259334db99d3694239",
        "index": 55,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:14:27.271000Z",
        "message": "Okay. Thank you."
      }
