  {
    "id": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
    "responseId": "d5808c02b68646129c624d053",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:01:46.703000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:01:54.583000Z",
        "message": "It's going well."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:01:57.413000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. Let's start with something simple. When you need to look something up or get an answer online, what's the very first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:02:07.093000Z",
        "message": "Go to Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:02:09.343000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So when you head to Google for answers, can you walk me through your typical process? Step by step, starting from when you decide to search,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:02:20.763000Z",
        "message": "It's something peak my curiosity or I want an immediate answer or a variety of answers, I go straight to Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:02:29.813000Z",
        "message": "So it's often about satisfying your curiosity or getting quick info. And Google is your first stop. When you're actually on Google, what do you usually do next? Do you type a specific kind of question? Or keyword, and how do you decide which result to click on?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:02:44.803000Z",
        "message": "It depends. Sometimes I do a a quick question or sometimes just a word."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:02:51.263000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Once you see the search results, how do you pick which 1 to click first? Is there anything you look for like, certain sites, snippets, or features"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:03:00.863000Z",
        "message": "Usually, the first 1 has the most details."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:03:06.223000Z",
        "message": "So the top result tends to catch your eye, especially if it's detailed. Can you tell me the full story of the last time you looked something up on Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:03:10.383000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:03:15.033000Z",
        "message": "Starting with what you needed and how it all went?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:03:17.513000Z",
        "message": "I looked up the MLB schedule and who was ahead in the numbers."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:03:25.303000Z",
        "message": "Great example. So you searched for the MLB schedule and team standings. What did you see at the top? Was it a special result, a website, or something else? And what made you choose where to click or read? Feel free to ask me any questions."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:03:55.613000Z",
        "message": "I'm fine."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:03:58.193000Z",
        "message": "Alright. Thinking back to that MLB search, what part of the Google experience felt most helpful? Was there anything frustrating or annoying about it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:04:07.602000Z",
        "message": "No. Google's always helpful. Top notch."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:04:13.703000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Um, if for some reason you couldn't use Google for a search like that, what would you do instead? Is there another tool"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:04:20.813000Z",
        "message": "Hi, Greg. Probably check AI."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:04:27.873000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So if Google wasn't an option, you turn to AI. Can you tell me about a time you actually used an AI tool? Like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Gemini, to look up something instead of Google? What did you need, and how did it go?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:04:41.603000Z",
        "message": "I can't recall anything specific. I've only used it a couple of times."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:04:47.633000Z",
        "message": "That's totally fine. From those couple of times using AI tools, even if it's just a general impression, how did the answers you got feel different from what Google gives you? Anything stand"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:04:59.743000Z",
        "message": "They just felt they felt more scattered and more impersonal."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:05:06.412000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. Scattered and impersonal. Can you tell me a bit more about what made them feel that way? Was it the way"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:05:13.523000Z",
        "message": "Well, AI specifically, that's you know that its answers may or may not be accurate."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:05:20.493000Z",
        "message": "Absolutely. So with AI tools, there's a bit of uncertainty about accuracy. When you see an answer from Google versus 1 from an AI, like, ChatGPT or Perplexity, how does your level of trust or confidence compare?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:05:34.053000Z",
        "message": "Oh, so far, I I still trust Google more."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:05:39.673000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. If you think about, like, sharing answers with someone else and maybe copying a link or recommending a tool, do you feel more comfortable quoting Google? What makes you feel that way?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:05:49.923000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. I'm just more used to it. It's a more reputable resource. For me personally."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:06:02.893000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Familiarity and give Google the edge for you. Thinking about brands for a second. If Google and AI engines like ChatGPT or Perplexity were people at a party, who would they be? How would each act?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:06:17.483000Z",
        "message": "Google would be the popular older guy, and the AI or ChatGPT would be the new up and coming person with all the new information."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:06:28.743000Z",
        "message": "Love that image. Google as the popular veteran and AI as the intriguing newcomer full of fresh info. When you think of words or feelings tied to Google Answers, versus chat GPT or perplexity, comes to mind for each? Just whatever pops into your head."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:06:45.043000Z",
        "message": "For Google Secure Answers, good, strong answers, answers I trust, For chat GPT, it's a little iffy yet, but more interesting. Items come up."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:02.913000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. That's super clear. Uh, looking back, say, a year ago, has anything shifted in how you look things up? Are you checking out AI engines more often? Or does Google still hold steady as your go to?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:14.453000Z",
        "message": "Well, a year ago, I wasn't using AI at all. So a year ago, it was only Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:22.223000Z",
        "message": "That's a good point. AI is a pretty new option. In your lineup. Um, was there a particular moment or or reason that made you try AI tools? For the first time? Or"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:31.173000Z",
        "message": "I just started I started seeing it pop up more. When I would scroll."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:39.543000Z",
        "message": "So seeing AI show up more often got you curious enough to try it out. Have any friends or coworkers ever suggested using AI tools instead of Google? Share their own experiences with them?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:51.083000Z",
        "message": "No. Not so far."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:07:55.553000Z",
        "message": "Alright. Last question. If you imagine a situation that might make you switch from Google to to using an AI engine more as your default? What would need to change or improve for you."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:08:08.813000Z",
        "message": "I would have to have a more personalized AI on an individual app, and I would have to trust it or feel like it was more sentient and connected to me."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:08:19.363000Z",
        "message": "That's really interesting. A highly personalized AI with your favorite apps and feeling more connected or almost sentient Thanks for sharing all that. Um, just to wrap up, how was this AI interview experience for you? Anything you want to mention?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 43,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:08:34.563000Z",
        "message": "This was great. No. This was great. I like it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b68024f296a3404c97bb152ec",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:08:39.053000Z",
        "message": "I'm really glad to hear that. Thanks again for your time and and openness. Um, you can end the call whenever you'd like. Have a great rest of your day."
      }
