  {
    "id": "ef4e8ed1ec624cd99d4b32eb4",
    "responseId": "f9b71b19a29b4d6e8dd223637",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "ef4e8ed1ec624cd99d4b32eb4",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:01:38.627000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ef4e8ed1ec624cd99d4b32eb4",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:01:46.267000Z",
        "message": "Good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ef4e8ed1ec624cd99d4b32eb4",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:01:48.546000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. Let's start with something simple. When you need answers online, what's what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ef4e8ed1ec624cd99d4b32eb4",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:02:03.697000Z",
        "message": "Use Google."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ef4e8ed1ec624cd99d4b32eb4",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:02:06.157000Z",
        "message": "Got it. You reached for Google first. Can you walk me through your typical process for looking something up on Google? Start from the moment you realize you need an answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ef4e8ed1ec624cd99d4b32eb4",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:02:19.167000Z",
        "message": "I just type in the question and into the Google search thing."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ef4e8ed1ec624cd99d4b32eb4",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:02:26.617000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. After you type your question into Google and hit enter, what's the next thing you do, uh, once you see the results?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ef4e8ed1ec624cd99d4b32eb4",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:02:36.687000Z",
        "message": "See the results, study them, decide whether I got cancer I needed or not."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ef4e8ed1ec624cd99d4b32eb4",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:02:44.547000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate the walk through. When you say you study them, what does that look like? Do you click into multiple links, read summaries, or something else? Tell me more about your approach there."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ef4e8ed1ec624cd99d4b32eb4",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:02:56.027000Z",
        "message": "Often, I will click on multiple links till I find the answer I'm looking for."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ef4e8ed1ec624cd99d4b32eb4",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:03:02.166000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. Thinking about the last time you searched for something on Google, can you walk me through that particular experience? What did you need, and what steps did you take from start to finish?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ef4e8ed1ec624cd99d4b32eb4",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:03:14.706000Z",
        "message": "No. I don't remember."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ef4e8ed1ec624cd99d4b32eb4",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:03:18.987000Z",
        "message": "No worries at all. Let's stick with general habits for now. Sometimes people use other tools, um, besides Google. Like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Gemini, especially for quick answers. Have you tried any of those yet?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ef4e8ed1ec624cd99d4b32eb4",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:03:32.467000Z",
        "message": "Yes. In fact, I used Meta AI yesterday."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ef4e8ed1ec624cd99d4b32eb4",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:03:37.746000Z",
        "message": "Oh, interesting. Tell me the story of that moment. What did you need? And walk me through everything you did with Meta AI, start to finish."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ef4e8ed1ec624cd99d4b32eb4",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:03:48.147000Z",
        "message": "I started the app, and then I was showing my daughter what it could do. How it could answer questions and stuff."
      },
      {
        "callId": "ef4e8ed1ec624cd99d4b32eb4",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:03:54.077000Z",
        "message": "That sounds fun. That sounds like a cool way to explore it together. What kind of questions did you and your daughter ask Meta AI? And how did it respond?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "ef4e8ed1ec624cd99d4b32eb4",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
