  {
    "id": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
    "responseId": "6f869eb4dc8146f985ed17c58",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:59:01.072000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:59:09.092000Z",
        "message": "Good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:59:11.851000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. Let's start simple. When you need to find an answer online, what's usually the first thing you do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:59:19.462000Z",
        "message": "Do a Google search."
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:59:22.352000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Can you walk me through your usual steps when you do a Google search? Start"
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:59:26.362000Z",
        "message": "I open up I open up Chrome, type in Google dot com, and then go to the search in search window."
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:59:36.302000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for painting that picture. After you type in your question or or keywords in Google, what's what's the next thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:59:44.302000Z",
        "message": "Hit enter."
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:59:48.562000Z",
        "message": "After you hit enter, what do you look at first? On the results page?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:59:53.012000Z",
        "message": "The first thing that the thing at the top, the most relevant"
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:00:01.242000Z",
        "message": "And when you say the thing at the top, can you describe what that usually looks like to you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:00:06.932000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. There's a few things that ask you what you wanna look at in either AI mode or all mode. And I look for the answer that's right underneath that."
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:00:17.052000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. When you see that choice between AI mode and all mode, which 1 are you more likely to pick? Tell me about"
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:00:23.822000Z",
        "message": "I got a it's always like"
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:00:24.342000Z",
        "message": "what goes through your"
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:00:26.302000Z",
        "message": "always on all mode, but I go to AI mode after I read all mode."
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:00:33.102000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful. So you start with all mode, then check out AI mode after. What's your thought process for switching to AI mode?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:00:38.572000Z",
        "message": "Yes."
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:00:41.682000Z",
        "message": "What are you hoping to see or solve that you don't get in all mode?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:00:45.672000Z",
        "message": "Because all mode sometimes doesn't have it. It's the answers aren't clear, then AI mode summarizes it a lot better in clearer English."
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:00:55.002000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. Thinking about the last time you did this, can you tell me the story? What question were you looking up, and how did you move between all mode and AI mode?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:01:05.392000Z",
        "message": "I was looking up something personal, and I just went from AI mode to all mode by clicking with the mouse."
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:01:13.772000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. In that moment, part of the experience felt most useful to you? And was there anything that annoyed you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:01:22.682000Z",
        "message": "There was nothing about and that annoyed me. What felt most useful was that I could understand."
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:01:30.531000Z",
        "message": "It sounds like Clarity is a big deal for you. When the answer makes sense right away, how does that make you feel?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:01:37.812000Z",
        "message": "Good. This is stupid."
      },
      {
        "callId": "07a322c1483b4f8c957de91e3",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:01:42.362000Z",
        "message": "Totally get it. These questions can feel repetitive. I'm here just to listen. And, um, learn from your own take, so feel free to cut me off anytime. Switching gears a bit."
      }
    ],
