  {
    "id": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
    "responseId": "37c273883b384194a350fc644",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:56:45.632000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:56:53.972000Z",
        "message": "My day is going good."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:56:57.602000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it. When you need to look something up online, or get an answer quickly, what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:57:05.862000Z",
        "message": "I usually go on Safari and look up whatever I'm thinking about."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:57:11.381000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you start by opening Safari. From there, do you have a go to search method or engine you use? Like Google or something else, Or does it depend on what you're looking up?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:57:23.552000Z",
        "message": "It depends on what I'm looking up."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:57:26.792000Z",
        "message": "That makes sense. Can you walk me through the last time you looked something up starting with what you needed and then each step you took to find your answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:57:35.712000Z",
        "message": "I was trying to find out how much these jeans cost. So I looked up the jeans, and I looked at the prices."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:57:43.181000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. When you searched for the genes, did you use a specific website or did you just type the style into a search engine? What happened next after you saw the results?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:57:53.922000Z",
        "message": "I just typed this dial, and I found out the price, and I bought them."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:57:58.791000Z",
        "message": "Sounds pretty straightforward. Was there anything about that search experience that felt especially helpful or maybe frustrating at any point?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:58:07.262000Z",
        "message": "No."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:58:10.442000Z",
        "message": "Alright. For quick answers like that, do you usually stick with the same search method? Or are there times when you use something like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or any AI powered answer engine instead?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:58:23.332000Z",
        "message": "Sometimes I check Chekibati if I can't find the right thing on Safari."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:58:28.952000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So Checkerbody comes into play if Safari doesn't give you what you want. Can you remember a specific time when you use Checkibody for a search? What was the situation, and how did that experience go for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:58:41.612000Z",
        "message": "I was trying to find out how much this shirt was, but the shirt wasn't popping up on Safari, so I went to chat GBT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:58:48.992000Z",
        "message": "That's a good example. When you switch to ChatGPT for that shirt search, you walk me through exactly what you did? Starting with your question and then how ChatGPT responded."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:59:02.002000Z",
        "message": "I typed in the shirt and what I was looking for, and they told me how much approximately it would be."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:59:11.942000Z",
        "message": "Got it. When ChatGPT gave you that approximate price, how did that answer feel compared to what you might get from a regular search engine or website? Anything stand out about the way it responded?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:59:22.772000Z",
        "message": "The answer felt great and no."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:59:27.892000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing. When you use ChatGPT like that, do you find yourself double checking its answers elsewhere? Or do you usually just go with what it tells you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:59:37.732000Z",
        "message": "I usually just go with what it tells me."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:59:42.802000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful to know. If you think about chat and Safari as tools you use for answers, how would you describe the different strengths or weaknesses between them?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:59:52.272000Z",
        "message": "I would describe it very helpful."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:59:56.402000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for that. When you hear Safari or ChatGPT, do any specific feelings, words, or associations come to mind for each?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:00:05.252000Z",
        "message": "No. Nothing comes to mind."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:00:08.852000Z",
        "message": "Fair enough. Let's look back over the past year. Do you notice any changes in how often you use Safari versus ChatGPT for looking things up, or is it about the same as before?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:00:18.672000Z",
        "message": "It's about the same as before."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:00:23.232000Z",
        "message": "Thanks. That's clear. Friends or family talk about finding answers online, do they ever mention ChatGPT or other AI tools? If so, what do they say or recommend?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:00:32.762000Z",
        "message": "Now nobody else uses it by me. That I know."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:00:40.042000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So in your circle, you're the only 1 using tools like ChatGPT. Before we wrap up, is there anything you wish these answer engines could do better for you? Any any features or ways they could make your searches even smoother?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:00:52.632000Z",
        "message": "No. They're just fine."
      },
      {
        "callId": "b1fd8a6635d244c7a94ec91ce",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T23:00:56.032000Z",
        "message": "Alright. Thanks for being so thanks for answering all my questions. And for sharing your honest experience. If you ever wanna revisit this topic or have feedback about these tools, I'm all ears. Can end the call whenever you'd like."
      }
    ],
