  {
    "id": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
    "responseId": "6a942353036b4f7a841a9c3dc",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:55:19.609000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:55:27.939000Z",
        "message": "My day is going great. How are you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:55:31.219000Z",
        "message": "I'm glad to hear it. I'm doing well too. Thanks for asking. Let's jump in. When you need answers online, what's what's the first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:55:40.789000Z",
        "message": "The first thing I usually do is I kind of research on Google or chat GPT."
      },
      {
        "callId": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:55:49.419000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So you switch between Google and ChatGPT when you're looking for answers. Can you walk me through what makes you pick 1 over the other? For example, what usually decides if you start with Google or with ChatGPT?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:56:03.209000Z",
        "message": "It depends on how vast or difficult the what I'm looking for is so that depends which 1 I I go for."
      },
      {
        "callId": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:56:15.489000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. Tell me more about"
      },
      {
        "callId": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:56:15.909000Z",
        "message": "Because yes, because Charge GPT tends to, like, give a more detailed information. So"
      },
      {
        "callId": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:56:32.209000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Can you walk me through the full story of the last time you used ChatGPT? Start with what you needed, and then tell me every step you remember. How you asked, what kind of answer you got, and what you did next."
      },
      {
        "callId": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:56:47.479000Z",
        "message": "Okay. Yeah. So I was looking to file I was looking to send a package to to the USCIS lockbox. And I kind of, like, try to get the address, but I couldn't, like, find the exact address that I was looking for. So I asked chat GPT, and yeah. I got it. And I was able to mail my package, like, successfully."
      },
      {
        "callId": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:57:20.099000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that story. When you ask ChatGPT for the address, what was most helpful about its answer for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:57:29.748000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. It give me, like, the as the exact address that I was looking for."
      },
      {
        "callId": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:57:36.879000Z",
        "message": "Did anything about that experience"
      },
      {
        "callId": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:57:40.709000Z",
        "message": "Sorry?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:57:43.479000Z",
        "message": "No worries. I was just curious. Was there anything about using ChatGPT for that task? That felt annoying or less helpful? Or did it go smoothly?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:57:53.939000Z",
        "message": "It went smoothly."
      },
      {
        "callId": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:57:58.629000Z",
        "message": "Nice. After you got the address from Chad GPT, did you double check it anywhere else? Or did you feel confident enough to go ahead and use it right away?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:58:08.739000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. I double checked with my friends too. And, yeah, that was the exact same address that they were mailing their stuff to. So it was correct."
      },
      {
        "callId": "db246297239d405ba8782573e",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:58:22.049000Z",
        "message": "Very thorough. Thinking about Google now, if you had tried searching there instead, what do you think would have happened? How is that process different for you?"
