        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:59:59.119000Z",
        "message": "That's really vivid. A friendly vibe and emotional support. If you line up, uh, the tools you've used, you know, ChatGPT, Google, maybe others, like Perplexity or Gemini, from most helpful to least helpful, how would you rank them? And what sticks out about your top pick?"
