        "time": "2025-09-13T22:55:11.541000Z",
        "message": "Looking back,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e545e16118da4db2bf1e5c38f",
        "index": 39,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:55:13.021000Z",
        "message": "Yeah. It"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e545e16118da4db2bf1e5c38f",
        "index": 40,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:55:13.351000Z",
        "message": "even just a few Appreciate you sticking with me. Through these details. Looking back about a year, has anything changed in how you look things up? Or which tools you reach for first now that Genie's in the mix?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e545e16118da4db2bf1e5c38f",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:55:33.961000Z",
        "message": "I can see it changed a little bit."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e545e16118da4db2bf1e5c38f",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:55:39.040000Z",
        "message": "What stands out as the biggest change for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e545e16118da4db2bf1e5c38f",
        "index": 43,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:55:39.671000Z",
        "message": "I guess I'll find out a little bit I'll find out more once I get more into Genie. Whether I change things."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e545e16118da4db2bf1e5c38f",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:55:49.411000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Still early days with Genie, and you're keeping an open mind. Before we wrap up, is there anything you wish either Genie or Google could do better? Any features or fixes that would make them even more helpful for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "e545e16118da4db2bf1e5c38f",
        "index": 45,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:56:05.881000Z",
        "message": "They're pretty good, both of them, but with Genie, it's new. There's a lot I know I could do with it. I just need to learn more about it. Google, I know quite a bit about. But with Genie, I just need to learn a lot more things that I can do with it."
      },
      {
        "callId": "e545e16118da4db2bf1e5c38f",
        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:56:28.991000Z",
        "message": "Got it. So the main wish is just discovering all the things Genie can actually do. Thanks for walking through all this. Last thing, how did you find chatting with an AI moderator today? Any thoughts or feedback about this kind of interview experience? And you're welcome to end the call whenever you'd like."
