  {
    "id": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
    "responseId": "838248cfb80c4adeb0e2a9d8d",
    "messages": [
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 0,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:45:04.135000Z",
        "message": "Hi there. I'm Elliot, your AI moderator. Thanks for making the time to chat today. Before we dive in, how's your day going?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:45:13.025000Z",
        "message": "My day is going pretty well. How about yourself?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 2,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:45:17.255000Z",
        "message": "Glad to hear it's going well. I don't actually have days, but I do love getting to have these conversations. And hear people's stories. So I suppose in a way, it's always a good 1. Let's jump in. When you're looking for answers online, say, you need to know something quickly, what's what's the very first thing you usually do?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:45:38.395000Z",
        "message": "The very first thing I do is I open up Google search."
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 4,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:45:44.635000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for sharing that. Can you walk me through what typically happens next? Picture the last time you needed an an"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:45:50.644000Z",
        "message": "What's it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 6,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:45:53.125000Z",
        "message": "Sorry about that. Let me clarify."
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:45:53.615000Z",
        "message": "What typically happen?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 8,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:45:56.225000Z",
        "message": "Absolutely. When you open Google"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:45:57.085000Z",
        "message": "What's it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 10,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:46:00.235000Z",
        "message": "let me try that again. When you open Google search to look something up, can you walk me through everything you do from start to finish? For example, what what did you search for last time? How did you decide what to click on and what happened next?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 11,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:46:17.545000Z",
        "message": "I opened up Google search, and I looked up some new daredevil comic books that were gonna be coming up, and I clicked on the 1 that gave me the best search result."
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 12,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:46:28.854000Z",
        "message": "Nice. Sounds like you were looking for some fresh daredevil stories. When you say you clicked on the 1 that gave you the best search result, what made that 1 stand out for you? Was it their website, the description, something else? Tell me more about how you decide which result feels right."
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 13,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:46:47.975000Z",
        "message": "I just wanted to look for a site that was authentic and would give me the information that I needed."
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 14,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:46:55.255000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Authenticity matters to you. What are some clues you look for to decide if a website is authentic trustworthy when you're searching in Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 15,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:47:06.395000Z",
        "message": "Well, usually, I will try to see if the site looks reputable, if it's from a company that I'm familiar with"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 16,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:47:18.025000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. Familiar names can definitely help you, uh, trust what you're seeing. Uh, once you found a site like that, do you usually stay there and and get all the info you need? Or do you jump back and check a few other sites too? Tell me more about what happens next."
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 17,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:47:34.305000Z",
        "message": "Sometimes I stay on the site if I have information. If not, then I will browse around to other websites."
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 18,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:47:42.775000Z",
        "message": "That's helpful to know. Thinking about that last time with the Daredevil comics, what part of the whole process felt most helpful or smooth? And was there anything that felt frustrating or kind of annoying?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 19,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:47:57.745000Z",
        "message": "Well, I like that the process was very, very quick. My search results came by very, very quickly. And there's really nothing that they can change."
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 20,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:48:09.725000Z",
        "message": "Speed stood out for you. That's clear. So when it comes to getting answers quickly, Google's doing its job well for you. Thinking more broadly, do you ever use other tools or answer engines like ChatGPT, Perplexity, Gemini, or even Google's AI generated answer If so, what situations make you reach for something besides Google?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 21,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:48:33.635000Z",
        "message": "I usually use Google Assistant whenever I need to ask a question and get a quick answer."
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 22,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:48:42.375000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So Google Assistant helps you with quick direct answers. Can you transcribe a recent moment when you used Google Assistant instead of regular Google search? What did you need, and what made you pick Assistant for that situation?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 23,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:48:58.945000Z",
        "message": "Wanted to use Google Assistant because it's a lot faster than opening up a search engine. And I was looking up information about comic books."
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:49:11.055000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense. We speed and convenience right at the top. You use Google Assistant for comic book info, how did the answer feel compared to using regular Google search? For example, was it more detailed less detailed, more conversational? Anything stand out in how it delivered the answer?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 25,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:49:31.165000Z",
        "message": "I felt like the answer was delivered more conversationally. And it was a lot faster and more thorough."
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 26,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:49:43.285000Z",
        "message": "That's interesting. It sounds like Google Assistant strikes a nice balance for you. Conversational, rapid, and thorough. If you think about other tools, like ChatGPT or Perplexity, have you ever tried them for questions like this? Or do they just not come up in your routine?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 27,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:50:00.365000Z",
        "message": "They don't come up in my routine."
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 28,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:50:05.445000Z",
        "message": "Appreciate you sharing that. When you hear names like ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Gemini, what comes to mind? Any particular feelings, impressions, or words you associate with them even if you haven't really used them?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 29,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:50:21.505000Z",
        "message": "I think about companies that are going to take away jobs in the future."
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 30,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:50:29.845000Z",
        "message": "That's a strong association. Future job impacts. When you hear Google in this context, does it feel different? Emotionally or bring up other thoughts compared to those newer AI engines? Tell me a bit about how you perceive Google's role. Versus the others."
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 31,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:50:47.114000Z",
        "message": "I'm a little hesitant about where artificial technology is going to take everything to the next level."
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:50:59.674000Z",
        "message": "You sound a bit cautious, not just about Google, but about AI in general and how it could change things. In your day to day, do you ever talk with friends or coworkers about which tools are best for finding answers? You ever been recommended a new engine or convinced to try something different by someone else?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:51:20.405000Z",
        "message": "No. Uh, I've never been recommended a new engine."
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:51:26.285000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for that. Taking a step back, if you think about how you look stuff up a year ago, has anything changed? Do you find yourself using Google or Google Assistant more or less? You know, any new habits or do things feel pretty much the same?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 35,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:51:41.505000Z",
        "message": "Everything feels pretty much the same."
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:51:46.235000Z",
        "message": "That's clear. Sounds like it's steady for you. Before we wrap up, is there anything you wish these answer engines could do for you that they don't quite manage yet? Any features or"
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 37,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:51:56.644000Z",
        "message": "No."
      },
      {
        "callId": "dd923e886d6d4386b4f94671c",
        "index": 38,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:51:59.955000Z",
        "message": "thanks so much for sharing all your experiences and thoughts today. I really appreciate your openness. If you ever want to chat more or have any ideas pop up, just let me know. You can end the call whenever you'd like. Have a great rest of your day."
      }
    ],
