        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 24,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:35:43.539000Z",
        "message": "Interesting. So did Gemini already have your question ready? Or was there something about how you interact with it that made it faster? Can you tell me a bit more about how it worked?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
