      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 32,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:36:47.138000Z",
        "message": "So you took Gemini"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 33,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:36:49.549000Z",
        "message": "yeah. Because it was in a sentence, and it showed what it was related to."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 34,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:36:58.999000Z",
        "message": "That's super clear. So seeing the acronym in a full sentence, with context helps you trust answer right away. Now, thinking about other times you've needed an answer,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
