        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:37:06.409000Z",
        "message": "Yeah."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 36,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:37:09.288000Z",
        "message": "can you remember a time when you used a different tool? Like Google, ChatGPT, or Perplexity, instead of Gemini? Well, what was the task and what made you switch?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
