        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 41,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:38:21.279000Z",
        "message": "Not really. It's just there's all the browsers have different even though they're inanimate objects, the browser's seem to have different views. Each browser is different. On the research you're doing."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
