        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:38:40.709000Z",
        "message": "That's a neat observation. Really intriguing. So even the browser you use changes how your research feels, or what answers you see. Can you tell me more about that? What differences do you do you notice from browser to browser when you're looking things up?"
