        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 44,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:39:15.698000Z",
        "message": "So depending on the browser, you get different types of, uh, context or ways your results are framed. Can you think of a browser that tends to give you answers you like better or feels more trustworthy for your research? What's what stands out about it for you?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 45,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:39:29.889000Z",
        "message": "None of them I I really don't trust any of the browsers. But I use Brave a lot. Because it's to me, it's it's more how can I say it?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 46,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:39:45.419000Z",
        "message": "Take your time. Um, what is it about Brave?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 47,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:39:46.589000Z",
        "message": "It looks yeah. It look it looks at things without bias. More than the other browsers. Google is uses Google use to me, opinionated"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 48,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:40:10.179000Z",
        "message": "That's really insightful."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 49,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:40:10.179000Z",
        "message": "opinions. Well, I don't know about that. It depends on how you look at things."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 50,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:40:23.569000Z",
        "message": "Fair enough. Um, sounds like you see, uh, subtle differences, but it's not 1 size fits all. When you get an answer, you feel good about a clear, complete, unbiased response from any engine or browser, how does that make you feel?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 51,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:40:41.469000Z",
        "message": "It's hard to believe."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 52,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:40:45.869000Z",
        "message": "You sound a bit skeptical. What is it that makes it hard to believe even when answers look unbiased and clear? Can you talk more about that?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 53,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:40:55.989000Z",
        "message": "Because of the info there's so much information out It's like information warfare. And you have to have some kind of background knowledge in what you're researching. To see what is true."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 54,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:41:22.218000Z",
        "message": "That's a strong point. So for you, it sounds like trusting an answer relies a lot on your own background knowledge. Not just what the engine or a browser shows. I'm curious. When you share an answer you found with someone else,"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 55,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:41:32.989000Z",
        "message": "Right."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 56,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:41:35.869000Z",
        "message": "is there 1 source, Gemini Google Search. Brave, anything else, that you feel more comfortable citing, or are they all pretty equal in your mind?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 57,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:41:47.278000Z",
        "message": "They're all pretty equal."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 58,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:41:51.109000Z",
        "message": "Makes sense? Thinking back over the last year or so, has has anything changed about the way you look things up online? New habits, tools, or little things that feel different."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 59,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:42:03.009000Z",
        "message": "The only new habit would be the AI."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 60,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:42:09.369000Z",
        "message": "That's a good shift to notice. Can you tell me a bit more about how AI, like Gemini, has changed your habits? What's different in your routine or experience now compared to a year ago?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 61,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:42:25.289000Z",
        "message": "I if I don't feel like typing it in, I can just ask the AI"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 62,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:42:38.449000Z",
        "message": "So voice input"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 63,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:42:39.359000Z",
        "message": "So for Conferior, go ahead."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 64,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:42:46.279000Z",
        "message": "Thanks for being so open. Uh, wrapping up here, how did it feel talking with an AI about your AnswerEngine habits today? Anything unexpected or any last thoughts you'd like to share?"
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 65,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:42:58.059000Z",
        "message": "No. Not really. The AI you've done a really good job. You sound exactly like a human, and if it was that bad, I wouldn't be talking to you right now."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 66,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:43:13.619000Z",
        "message": "I appreciate that a lot. Thanks for your time and honesty today. That's everything I needed. So you're welcome to end the call whenever you'd like. I hope you get to enjoy a bit more of that sunny day."
      },
      {
        "callId": "8cb7f8d3802644cbae2e32fff",
        "index": 67,
        "role": "user",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:43:27.179000Z",
        "message": "You too. Thank you, AI."
      }
    ],
