        "time": "2025-09-13T22:41:06.961000Z",
        "message": "It's just the general idea. Nothing specific, really."
      },
      {
        "callId": "06c76ec3fcbd45ac92f4d9a3d",
        "index": 42,
        "role": "bot",
        "time": "2025-09-13T22:41:12.201000Z",
        "message": "Got it. Just wanting things to run smoothly in general. Makes sense. Thanks for being so open and sharing your experiences and thoughts today. Before we finish up, how did you find chatting with an AI interviewer like me? You know, anything you'd change or any last thoughts?"
